{"id": "29409", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29409", "title": "Consortium of European Research Libraries", "text": "O Consortium of European Research Libraries (CERL) o l'\u00e9 'n cons\u00f2r\u00e7io de bibliot\u00eache de ri\u00e7\u00e8rca, scito\u00e6 sorviat\u00f9tto in Eor\u00f6pa, ch'o fa\u00e7\u00eclita e ri\u00e7\u00e8rche di st\u00f2richi co-\u00een inter\u00e8sse in sci\u00e2 st\u00f6ia de 'n l\u00ecbbro, public\u00e0ndo de viv\u00e0gne in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 che incl\u00f9ddan l'Heritage of the Printed Book Database (HPB), o CERL Thesaurus e o CERL Portal. L'\u00f2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n a t\u00eagne \u00e0nche di semen\u00e2i e di lou\u00eai e, a part\u00ee da-o 1998, a p\u00f9blica 'n peri\u00f2dico ch'o l'\u00e9 ciam\u00f2u \"CERL Papers\". A l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta cre\u00e2 into 1992 e, da-o 1994, a l'\u00e9 registr\u00e2 into R\u00e9gno Un\u00eeo c\u00f3mme 'na socj\u00eat\u00e6 a responsabilit\u00e6 limit\u00e2 da garan\u00e7\u00eea, con s\u00eade a L\u00f3ndra. L'asenbl\u00eaa soci\u00e2le a se t\u00eagne anoalm\u00e9nte into m\u00e9ize de nov\u00e9nbre e o s\u00f2 \u00f2rgano aministrat\u00eevo o l'\u00e9 form\u00f2u da 'n cons\u00e9ggio d'aministra\u00e7i\u00f3n e da 'n comit\u00e2to esecut\u00eevo. O s\u00f2 prescid\u00e9nte o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to Elmar Mittler, 'n profes\u00f4 em\u00earito in biblioteconom\u00eea, sc\u00ecnn-a-o nov\u00e9nbre do 2011, qu\u00e0nde o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to sostito\u00eeo da Ulf G\u00f6ranson, ecs-c\u00e0ppo bibliotec\u00e2io de l'Universcit\u00e6 de Uppsala. \nHeritage of the Printed Book Database.\nL'Heritage of the Printed Book Database, into pas\u00f2u ciam\u00f2u Hand Press Book Database, a-o frev\u00e2 2014 o contegn\u00eeva squ\u00e6xi 5 milio\u00een de sch\u00eade in sce di l\u00ecbbri st\u00e0np\u00e6 inte l'\u00e9poca da st\u00e0npa a m\u00e0n, a part\u00ee d\u00f3nca da l'introdu\u00e7i\u00f3n da tecnolog\u00eea da st\u00e0npa in Eor\u00f6pa, ci\u00f9 \u00f2 m\u00eano into 1450, a-a meit\u00e6 do XIX s\u00e9colo, con de descri\u00e7io\u00een che fa\u00e7\u00eclitan o parag\u00f3n tra e v\u00e0rie verscio\u00een. In qu\u00e9llo mom\u00e9nto, 41 institu\u00e7io\u00een contribo\u00eevan con d\u00e6ti e sch\u00eade, e qu\u00e6 s\u00f3n inc\u00e9ntr\u00e6 sorviat\u00f9tto in sce l'an\u00e0lixi de l'\u00f2g\u00e8tto ciuf\u00eeto che in sci\u00e2 retroconversci\u00f3n de v\u00f4xe bibliogr\u00e0fiche prexist\u00e9nti. A b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti a l'\u00e9 de l\u00f3ngo agiorn\u00e2, sp\u00e9cce da-e institu\u00e7io\u00een parte\u00e7ip\u00e0nti.\nA b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti HPB a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta \u00f2spit\u00e2 da l'americ\u00e0nn-a OCLC da-o set\u00e9nbre 2007 a-o 2013 e a l'ad\u00eauvia i software FirstSearch e Connexion de l'OCLC. A part\u00ee da-o set\u00e9nbre 2013, a l'\u00e9 \u00f2spit\u00e2 da-a ted\u00e9sca Gemeinsamer Bibliotheksverbund. L'intr\u00e2 a l'\u00e9 limit\u00e2 a-e institu\u00e7io\u00een parte\u00e7ip\u00e0nti a-o CERL e a-i licensat\u00e2i.\nCERL Thesaurus.\nO CERL Thesaurus, gest\u00eeo da-o Data Conversion Group de G\u00f6ttingen, o l'in\u00e0ndia l\u00eaughi, stanpo\u00e9i, edito\u00ee e aoto\u00ee pe trav\u00e0ggi st\u00e0np\u00e6 tra o 1450 e o 1850, e qu\u00e9sto o s\u00e8rve d\u00f3nca, ins\u00e9mme con l'integr\u00f2u contr\u00f2llo d'outorit\u00e6 (o Gemeinsame Normdatei), pe incrox\u00e2 i n\u00f3mmi de vari\u00e0nte inte st\u00e0npe e inti cat\u00e0loghi.\nO v\u00eagne agiorn\u00f2u outomaticam\u00e9nte co-a b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti Material Evidence in Incunabula e o l'\u00f2fre di colegam\u00e9nti a-e informa\u00e7io\u00een in sci\u00e2 proveni\u00e9nsa forn\u00eee da-e institu\u00e7io\u00een parte\u00e7ip\u00e0nti a-o CERL, che rapr\u00e9zentan de cole\u00e7io\u00een \u00f2ua spantegh\u00e6, e o l'incl\u00f9dde \u00e0nche do materi\u00e2le digitaliz\u00f2u c\u00f3mme inm\u00e0gine de m\u00e0rche tipogr\u00e0fiche m\u00ecsse ins\u00e9mme da Vindel, Ronald McKerrow e Philippe Renouard e de f\u00ee de gr\u00e0nn-e. A v\u00ecxita a-o thesaurus a l'\u00e9 de b\u00e0dda.\nCERL Portal.\nO CERL Portal o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to svilup\u00f2u da l'Electronic Publishing Centre da Bibliot\u00eaca de l'Universcit\u00e6 de Uppsala d\u00f2ppo o conplet\u00e2se do CERL Manuscripts Project. O perm\u00e9tte de ri\u00e7\u00e8rche conbin\u00e6 s\u00e9gge da manoscr\u00eeti che da l\u00ecbbri st\u00e0np\u00e6, in de b\u00e0nche d\u00e6ti de manoscr\u00eeti, c\u00f3mme l'HPB e \u00e2tre b\u00e0nche d\u00e6ti adi\u00e7ion\u00e2li in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 c\u00f3mme l'English Short-Title Catalogue e b\u00e0nche d\u00e6ti de fotograf\u00eee. L'intr\u00e2 a-o port\u00e2 a l'\u00e9 de b\u00e0dda.\nMaterial Evidence in Incunabula.\nMaterial Evidence in Incunabula a l'\u00e9 'na b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti de st\u00e0npe e incon\u00e0boli do XV s\u00e9colo ch'a p\u00ecggia da l'Incunabula Short Title Catalogue da British Library e e m\u00e9tte ins\u00e9mme con d\u00e6ti in sce de s\u00e9ncie c\u00f2pie. O s\u00f2 svil\u00f9ppo o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to ini\u00e7ialm\u00e9nte finan\u00e7i\u00f2u da-a British Academy. A v\u00ecxita a-a b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti a l'\u00e9 de b\u00e0dda.\nInstitu\u00e7io\u00een parte\u00e7ip\u00e0nti.\nA-o nov\u00e9nbre do 2021, o cons\u00f2r\u00e7io o cont\u00e2va de 293 m\u00e9nbri, sorviat\u00f9tto da l'Eor\u00f6pa ma \u00e0nche da-e Am\u00e9riche. De qu\u00e9sti, i s\u00e9nci m\u00e9nbri (a qu\u00f6ta intr\u00eaga) e i m\u00e9nbri speci\u00e2li (i qu\u00e6 p\u00e0gan 'na qu\u00f6ta ci\u00f9 b\u00e0ssa) \u00e0n 'n v\u00f4to a l'asenbl\u00eaa soci\u00e2le ano\u00e2le; gr\u00f9ppi de no ci\u00f9 de 16 bibliot\u00eache condiv\u00ecddan 'n v\u00f4to e gr\u00f9ppi de m\u00e9nbri asoci\u00e6 inte 'n s\u00f4lo sog\u00e8tto pori\u00e9ivan \u00e0nche no vot\u00e2."}
{"id": "29411", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29411", "title": "Union List of Artist Names", "text": "L'Union List of Artist Names (ULAN) o l'\u00e9 'na b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti de b\u00e0dda in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6, gest\u00eea da-o Getty Research Institute d\u00eauvi\u00e0ndo 'n vocabol\u00e2io control\u00f2u, o qu\u00e6, into 2018, o conprend\u00e9iva ci\u00f9 de 300.000 art\u00ecsti e 720.000 n\u00f3mmi pe qu\u00e9sti, cosc\u00ec c\u00f3mme \u00e2tre informa\u00e7io\u00een in sc\u00ee m\u00e6ximi art\u00ecsti. I n\u00f3mmi ULAN p\u00eauan \u00ease n\u00f3mmi pr\u00f2ppi, cogn\u00f3mmi, n\u00f3mmi f\u00e2si, vari\u00e0nte \u00f2rtogr\u00e0fiche, n\u00f3mmi in v\u00e0rie l\u00e9ngoe e n\u00f3mmi che s\u00f3n c\u00e0ngi\u00e6 co-o t\u00e9npo, prez\u00e9npio n\u00f3mmi da mai\u00e9zzo. Tra qu\u00e9sti n\u00f3mmi, de s\u00f2lito ghe n'\u00e9 un ch'o v\u00eagne indic\u00f2u c\u00f3mme o prefer\u00eeo.\nScib\u00e9n ch'o l'\u00e9 raprezent\u00f2u c\u00f3mme 'na l\u00ecsta, l'ULAN o l'\u00e9 strutur\u00f2u ci\u00f9 c\u00f3mme 'n thesaurus, in ac\u00f2rdo co-i st\u00e0ndard ISO e NISO pi-\u00e2 costru\u00e7i\u00f3n de 'ste b\u00e0nche d\u00e6ti chi; o cont\u00eagne def\u00e6ti de rela\u00e7io\u00een ger\u00e0rchiche, de equival\u00e9nsa e asociat\u00eeve.\nL'\u00f2biet\u00eevo de \u00f2gni elem\u00e9nto ULAN o l'\u00e9 'n art\u00ecsta, Inta b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti, \u00f2gni elem\u00e9nto art\u00ecsta (ciam\u00f2u sog\u00e8tto asc\u00ec) o l'\u00e9 indentific\u00f2u da 'n ID num\u00e9rico \u00f9nico. A l'\u00e9 indic\u00e2 a na\u00e7ionalit\u00e6 de qu\u00e9sto art\u00ecsta e i l\u00eaughi e e d\u00e6te de n\u00e0scita e de m\u00f2rte (se conosci\u00fbe). Ligh\u00e6 a \u00f2gni elem\u00e9nto de art\u00ecsta gh'\u00e9 i n\u00f3mmi, i art\u00ecsti corel\u00e6, e f\u00f3nte di d\u00e6ti e de n\u00f2tte. A covert\u00fba into t\u00e9npo de l'ULAN a va da l'antighit\u00e6 a-o prez\u00e9nte e o s\u00f2 \u00e0nbito gi\u00f6gr\u00e0fico o l'\u00e9 glob\u00e2le.\nI art\u00ecsti p\u00eauan \u00ease s\u00e9gge di indiv\u00ecdoi (pers\u00f3nn-e) che di gr\u00f9ppi de indiv\u00ecdoi che trav\u00e0ggian ins\u00e9mme, prez\u00e9npio \u00f2rgani socjet\u00e2i. I art\u00ecsti inte l'ULAN rapr\u00e9zentan generalm\u00e9nte i creato\u00ee coinv\u00f2lti inte l'idea\u00e7i\u00f3n \u00f2 a produ\u00e7i\u00f3n de \u00e0rte vix\u00eeve e de architet\u00fbe. S\u00f3n asc\u00ec incl\u00fbzi \u00e7\u00e8rti art\u00ecsti do spet\u00e0colo (ma de s\u00f2lito no ato\u00ee, baler\u00ecn \u00f2 \u00e2tri art\u00ecsti sc\u00ecmili). S\u00f3n conpr\u00e9ixi \u00e0nche i archiv\u00ecsti e di donato\u00ee.\nSt\u00f6ia.\nO svil\u00f9ppo de l'ULAN o l'\u00e9 incomens\u00f2u into 1984 da p\u00e0rte do J. Paul Getty Trust. O Trust, o qu\u00e6 o gest\u00eeva za l\"'Art and Architecture Thesaurus\" (AAT), o l'\u00e0 avi\u00f2u o prog\u00e8tto in risp\u00f2sta a-e necescit\u00e6 di \u00e2tri prog\u00e8tti Getty pe vocabol\u00e2i control\u00e6 di n\u00f3mmi di art\u00ecsti. L'ULAN o cr\u00e9sce e o c\u00e0ngia gr\u00e0\u00e7ie a-i contrib\u00fbti da comunit\u00e6 di ut\u00e9nti e a-o trav\u00e0ggio editori\u00e2le do \"Getty Vocabulary Program\".\nScib\u00e9n che \u00f2riginaiam\u00e9nte o l'\u00eaa destin\u00f2u a l'\u00fbzo s\u00f4lo da p\u00e0rte di prog\u00e8tti Getty, a ci\u00f9 \u00e0npia comunit\u00e6 de informa\u00e7io\u00een art\u00ecstiche de f\u00eaua do Getty a l'\u00e0 espr\u00e8sso a necescit\u00e6 de d\u00eauvi\u00e2 l'ULAN pe cataloga\u00e7i\u00f3n e rec\u00f9pero d\u00e6ti. O Getty o l'\u00e0 d\u00f3nca distribo\u00eeo l'ULAN pe 'n \u00fbzo ci\u00f9 \u00e0npio seg\u00f3ndo i prin\u00e7\u00ecppi precedentem\u00e9nte stabil\u00eei pi-\u00e2 costru\u00e7i\u00f3n e o mantegnim\u00e9nto de l\"'Art and Architecture Thesaurus\": o s\u00f2 trav\u00e0ggio o l'incl\u00f9dde i n\u00f3mmi neces\u00e2i pe catalog\u00e2 e ricuper\u00e2 informa\u00e7io\u00een in sc\u00ea \u00e0rte vix\u00eeve e l'architet\u00fba. O l'\u00e9 baz\u00f2u in sce 'na terminolog\u00eea cor\u00e9nte, garant\u00eea pe l'\u00fbzo de f\u00f3nte leter\u00e2ie de c\u00f3nto e convalid\u00e6 da l'\u00fbzo inta comunit\u00e6 scent\u00ecfica de l'\u00e0rte e da st\u00f6ia de l'architet\u00fba; o l'\u00e9 conpil\u00f2u e modific\u00f2u in risp\u00f2sta a-e ezig\u00e9nse da comunit\u00e6 di ut\u00e9nti.\n\u00d2riginaiam\u00e9nte costr\u00fbto c\u00f3mme 'na s\u00e9nplice \"union list\" in \u00f3rdine arfab\u00e9tico de n\u00f3mmi di art\u00ecsti e de biograf\u00eee, de m\u00f2ddo da r\u00e9ndelo coer\u00e9nte con l'AAT e o \"Getty Thesaurus of Geographic Names\", a-a f\u00ecn di \u00e0nni nov\u00e0nta l'ULAN o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to r\u00e9izo conf\u00f3rme a-i st\u00e0ndard na\u00e7ion\u00e2li e interna\u00e7ion\u00e2li pi-\u00e2 costru\u00e7i\u00f3n do thesaurus. O s\u00f2 \u00e0nbito o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to anpli\u00f2u pe incl\u00f9dde \u00e9nti c\u00f3mme st\u00f9ddi de architet\u00fba e dep\u00f2xiti d'\u00e0rte, i qu\u00e6 p\u00eauan \u00ease disp\u00f2sti seg\u00f3ndo di liv\u00e9lli ger\u00e0rchichi.\nL'ULAN o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to fond\u00f2u s\u00f3tt'a-a dire\u00e7i\u00f3n de Eleanor Fink, a qu\u00e6 a l'\u00eaa c\u00e0ppo de qu\u00e9llo ch'o l'\u00e9 p\u00f6i st\u00e6to ciam\u00f2u \"Vocabulary Coordination Group\", p\u00f6i divent\u00e2 diret\u00f4 de l\"'Art History Information Program\", ci\u00f9 av\u00e0nti rinomin\u00f2u \"Getty Information Institute\". L'ULAN o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to costr\u00fbto co-o pas\u00e2 di \u00e0nni da numer\u00f4zi m\u00e9nbri da comunit\u00e6 di ut\u00e9nti e da 'n gr\u00f9ppo de edito\u00ee dedic\u00e6, s\u00f3tt'a-a supervix\u00f3n de div\u00e8rsci gesto\u00ee. L'ULAN o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to public\u00f2u into 1994 s\u00e9gge c\u00f3mme di pap\u00ea (Union List of Artist Names, diret\u00f4 do prog\u00e8tto: James M. Bower, edit\u00f4 c\u00e0ppo: Murtha Baca, N\u00eauva York, G.K. Hall, 1994) che con di file leg\u00ecbili da-a m\u00e0china. D\u00e6ta a dimensci\u00f3n de l\u00f3ngo ci\u00f9 gr\u00e0nde e a frequ\u00e9nsa de mod\u00ecfiche e de az\u00f3nte a l'ULAN, into 1997 o l'\u00eaa divent\u00f2u ci\u00e6o che a publica\u00e7i\u00f3n in sce c\u00e0rta a l'\u00eaa 'n scist\u00eama inpratic\u00e0bile. \u00d2ua o l'\u00e9 def\u00e6ti public\u00f2u s\u00f4lo in di form\u00e2ti outomatiz\u00e6, s\u00e9gge inte 'n'interf\u00e0ccia in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 da-a qu\u00e6 se p\u00eauan f\u00e2 de ri\u00e7\u00e8rche, che in di file de d\u00e6ti dispon\u00ecbili pi-\u00e2 lic\u00e9nsa. I d\u00e6ti pe ULAN s\u00f3n conpil\u00e6 e mod\u00ecfic\u00e6 inte 'n scist\u00eama editori\u00e2le cre\u00f2u sci\u00f9 mez\u00fba da-o person\u00e2 t\u00e9cnico de Getty pe sodisf\u00e2 i requix\u00eeti \u00f9nichi de conpila\u00e7i\u00f3n de d\u00e6ti da t\u00e0nti contriboto\u00ee, fuxo\u00een, spostam\u00e9nti e publica\u00e7i\u00f3n in v\u00e0rri form\u00e2ti. O contr\u00f2llo editori\u00e2le fin\u00e2le de l'ULAN o l'\u00e9 f\u00e6to da-o \"Getty Vocabulary Program\", d\u00eauvi\u00e0ndo de r\u00e9gole editori\u00e2li cons\u00f2lid\u00e6. I ato\u00e2li aministrato\u00ee de l'ULAN s\u00f3n Patricia Harpring, edit\u00f4 manageri\u00e2le, e Murtha Baca, diret\u00f4 do \"Vocabulary Program\" e do \"Digital Resource Management\".\nCarater\u00ecstiche.\nScib\u00e9n che a s\u00f2 strut\u00fba a l'\u00e9 relativam\u00e9nte ci\u00e0tta, l'ULAN o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to realiz\u00f2u c\u00f3mme 'na b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti ger\u00e0rchica ch'a se dir\u00e0mma da 'na r\u00e9ixe ciam\u00e2 \"Top of the ULAN hierarchies\" (Subject_ID: 500000001); a l'\u00e0 atoalm\u00e9nte do\u00ee t\u00eepi de elem\u00e9nti p\u00f9blic\u00e6: Pers\u00f3nn-a e \u00c9nte. Entit\u00e6 da tipolog\u00eea Pers\u00f3nn-a de s\u00f2lito no \u00e0n \u00e2tri elem\u00e9nti a l\u00f4 l\u00ecgh\u00e6. E entit\u00e6 de t\u00eepo \u00e9nte p\u00eauan pe c\u00f3ntra diram\u00e2se in di \u00e8rbi de elem\u00e9nti. P\u00eauan \u00easighe m\u00f9ltipli cont\u00e8sti ci\u00f9 \u00e0npi, rend\u00e9ndo a strut\u00fba de l'ULAN de t\u00eepo poliger\u00e0rchico. \u00d3ltre a-e rela\u00e7io\u00een ger\u00e0rchiche, l'ULAN o conpr\u00e9nde de rela\u00e7io\u00een de equival\u00e9nsa e asociat\u00eeve asc\u00ec."}
{"id": "29415", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29415", "title": "Bibliot\u00eaca da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n", "text": "A Bibliot\u00eaca da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n (\"National Diet Library\", NDL, in giapon\u00e9ize \u56fd\u7acb\u56fd\u4f1a\u56f3\u66f8\u9928, \"Kokuritsu Kokkai Toshokan\") a l'\u00e9 a bibliot\u00eaca na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n e unn-a de ci\u00f9 gr\u00e9nde bibliot\u00eache a-o m\u00f3ndo. A l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta cre\u00e2 into 1948 con l'\u00f2biet\u00eevo de asc\u00ecste i m\u00e9nbri da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n (\u56fd\u4f1a, \"Kokkai\") inta ri\u00e7\u00e8rca de questio\u00een de inter\u00e8sse p\u00f9blico. Qu\u00e9sta bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00e9 sc\u00ecmile pe \u00f2biet\u00eevi a-a Bibliot\u00eaca do Congr\u00e8sso di St\u00e2ti Un\u00eei.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 form\u00e2 da d\u00f4e strut\u00fbe prin\u00e7ip\u00e6 che se tr\u00eauvan a T\u00f2kyo e a Ky\u00f2to, e da 'na s\u00e9rie de \u00e2tre bibliot\u00eache second\u00e2ie spantegh\u00e6 pe t\u00f9tto o Giap\u00f3n.\nSt\u00f6ia.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 o suces\u00f4 de tr\u00e6 div\u00e8rse bibliot\u00eache: qu\u00e9lla da C\u00e0mia di P\u00e2ri, a bibliot\u00eaca da C\u00e0mia di Raprezent\u00e0nti, t\u00f9tte d\u00f4e instito\u00eee a-a crea\u00e7i\u00f3n da Di\u00eata Inperi\u00e2le Giapon\u00e9ize into 1890, e a Bibliot\u00eaca Inperi\u00e2le, a qu\u00e6 a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta costito\u00eea into 1872 s\u00f3tt'a-a giurisdi\u00e7i\u00f3n do Minist\u00earo da P\u00f9blica Instru\u00e7i\u00f3n.\nO pot\u00eare da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n pr\u00ecmma da go\u00e6ra o l'\u00eaa limit\u00f2u e o s\u00f2 bez\u00e9ugno de informa\u00e7io\u00een o l'\u00eaa de consego\u00e9nsa as\u00e6 pic\u00ecn. E \u00f2rigin\u00e2ie bibliot\u00eache da Di\u00eata \"no \u00e0n m\u00e2i svilup\u00f2u ne e arecug\u00e9ite ne i serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i che avi\u00e9ivan posci\u00fbo r\u00e9ndele 'n conplem\u00e9nto vit\u00e2le de 'n'ativit\u00e6 legislat\u00eeva pe dindav\u00e9i respons\u00e0bile\". Sc\u00ecnn-a-a sconf\u00ectta do Giap\u00f3n, pe de ci\u00f9, l'esecut\u00eevo o l'av\u00e9iva control\u00f2u t\u00f9tti i pap\u00ea pol\u00ectichi, priv\u00e0ndo a popola\u00e7i\u00f3n e a Di\u00eata de v\u00e0rie informa\u00e7io\u00een as\u00e6 inport\u00e0nti. E f\u00f2rse de \u00f2cupa\u00e7i\u00f3n americ\u00e0nn-e s\u00f3tt'a-o gener\u00e2le Douglas MacArthur \u00e0n d\u00f3nca ritegn\u00fbo che a rif\u00f3rma do scist\u00eama bibliotec\u00e2io da Di\u00eata a fo\u00eese 'na p\u00e0rte inport\u00e0nte da democratiza\u00e7i\u00f3n do Giap\u00f3n d\u00f2ppo a s\u00f2 sconf\u00ectta inta seg\u00f3nda go\u00e6ra mondi\u00e2le.\nInto 1946, \u00f2gni c\u00e0mia da Di\u00eata a l'\u00e0 form\u00f2u o pr\u00f2pio comit\u00e2to perman\u00e9nte inta Bibliot\u00eaca da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n. Hani Goro, st\u00f2rico marx\u00ecsta ch'o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to inprexon\u00f2u inta go\u00e6ra pe di cr\u00ecmini de pensc\u00eao e ch'o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to elez\u00fbo a-a C\u00e0mia di Conseg\u00ea (o suces\u00f4 de l'abol\u00eea C\u00e0mia di P\u00e2ri) d\u00f2ppo a go\u00e6ra, goid\u00e0ndo i sf\u00f2rsi de rif\u00f3rma. L'Hani o l'\u00e0 inmagin\u00f2u o n\u00eauvo c\u00f2rpo c\u00f3mme \"s\u00e9gge 'na \u00e7itad\u00e9lla da sovranit\u00e6 popol\u00e2re\", s\u00e9gge o m\u00e9zzo pe realiz\u00e2 'na \"rivolu\u00e7i\u00f3n pac\u00ecfica\". I ofi\u00e7i\u00e6 de l'\u00f2cupa\u00e7i\u00f3n respons\u00e0bili da supervix\u00f3n de rif\u00f3rme de bibliot\u00eache \u00e0n rifer\u00eeo che, scib\u00e9n che l'\u00f2cupa\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00eaa 'n catalizat\u00f4 pe-o cangiam\u00e9nto, l'ini\u00e7iat\u00eeva loc\u00e2le a prexist\u00e9iva a l'\u00f2cupa\u00e7i\u00f3n e e rif\u00f3rme ari\u00easc\u00eee \u00eaan dov\u00fbe a di giapon\u00e9ixi div\u00f6ti c\u00f3mme l'Hani.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta av\u00e8rta into z\u00f9gno do 1948 inte l'ato\u00e2le C\u00e2 di Invit\u00e6 de St\u00e2to (l'ecs pal\u00e0sso destac\u00f2u de Akasaka) co-ina cole\u00e7i\u00f3n ini\u00e7i\u00e2le de 100.000 vol\u00f9mmi. O pr\u00ecmmo bibliotec\u00e2io da Bibliot\u00eaca da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to o pol\u00ectico Tokujir\u014d Kanamori, afianc\u00f2u da-o fil\u00f2zofo Masakazu Nakai c\u00f3mme pr\u00ecmmo v\u00eece-bibliotec\u00e2io. Into 1949, a NDL a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta un\u00eea a-a Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le (ini\u00e7ialm\u00e9nte ciam\u00e2 Bibliot\u00eaca Inperi\u00e2le), divent\u00e0ndo a s\u00f4la bibliot\u00eaca na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n. Inte 'sto m\u00f2ddo chi, a s\u00f2 cole\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 aoment\u00e2 de 'n mili\u00f3n de vol\u00f9mmi de ci\u00f9 che \u00eaan sc\u00ecnn-a qu\u00e9llo mom\u00e9nto \u00f2spit\u00e6 inte l'ecs Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de Ueno.\nInto 1961, a NDL a s'\u00e9 trasfer\u00eea inta s\u00f2 s\u00eade ato\u00e2le a Nagatach\u014d, da-ar\u00e9nte a-a Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le. Into 1986 o conpl\u00e8sso da NDL o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to conplet\u00f2u pe arech\u00e9ugge 'n tot\u00e2le de 12 milio\u00een de l\u00ecbbri e de peri\u00f2dichi. O Kansai-kan (a Bibliot\u00eaca do Kansai), a l'\u00e0 av\u00e8rto inte l'\u00f2t\u00f4bre do 2002 inta Kansai Science City (\u00e7it\u00e6 de Seika, distr\u00e9ito de S\u014draku, prefet\u00fba de Ky\u00f2to), a qu\u00e6 a l'\u00e0 'na cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de 6 milio\u00een de elem\u00e9nti. Into m\u00e0zzo do 2002, a NDL a l'\u00e0 av\u00e9rto 'na n\u00eauva s\u00eade, \u00f6 s\u00e6 a Bibliot\u00eaca Interna\u00e7ion\u00e2le de Letiat\u00fba pe Figeu, inte l'ecs pal\u00e0sso da Bibliot\u00eaca Inperi\u00e2le de Ueno. Qu\u00e9sto r\u00e0mmo o cont\u00eagne ci\u00f9 de 400.000 art\u00eccoli de letiat\u00fba pe figeu che v\u00eagnan da t\u00f9tto o m\u00f3ndo.\nScib\u00e9n che o mand\u00e2to \u00f2rigin\u00e2le da NDL o l'\u00eaa qu\u00e9llo d'\u00ease 'na bibliot\u00eaca de ri\u00e7\u00e8rca pi-\u00e2 Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le, o p\u00f9blico in gener\u00e2le o l'\u00e9 o ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte consumat\u00f4 di serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i da bibliot\u00eaca. Prez\u00e9npio, inte l'\u00e0nno fisc\u00e2le termin\u00f2u into m\u00e0rso do 2004 a bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00e0 av\u00fbo ci\u00f9 de 250.000 dom\u00e0nde de refer\u00e9nse da-o p\u00f9blico; pe c\u00f3ntra s\u00f3n st\u00e6te registr\u00e6 s\u00f4lo 32.000 dom\u00e0nde da p\u00e0rte de m\u00e9nbri da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le.\nPe risp\u00f3nde a-a pandem\u00eea de COVID-19, a NDL a l'\u00e0 sosp\u00e9izo i serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i bibliotec\u00e2i a-o p\u00f9blico da-i 5 de m\u00e0rso do 2020; arv\u00ecndo t\u00f3rna a-o p\u00f9blico a-i 11 de z\u00f9gno do 2020 pe 'n m\u00e0scimo de 200 vixitato\u00ee a-o gi\u00f3rno in sci\u00e2 b\u00e2ze de 'n'estra\u00e7i\u00f3n sc\u00ecmile a 'na loter\u00eea, co-i poten\u00e7i\u00e2li vixitato\u00ee tegn\u00fbi a registr\u00e2se in ant\u00ec\u00e7ipo pe av\u00e9i a poscibilit\u00e6 de \u00ease sele\u00e7ion\u00e6.\nCole\u00e7io\u00een.\nCole\u00e7i\u00f3n prin\u00e7ip\u00e2.\nC\u00f3mme bibliot\u00eaca na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n, a NDL a l'arech\u00e9ugge de c\u00f2pie de t\u00f9tte e publica\u00e7io\u00een st\u00e0np\u00e6 into P\u00e0ize. Pe de ci\u00f9, zach\u00e9 a NDL a l'\u00e9 'na bibliot\u00eaca de ri\u00e7\u00e8rca pe-i m\u00e9nbri da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le, o s\u00f2 person\u00e2, \u00f3ltre che pe-o p\u00f9blico in gener\u00e2le, o mant\u00eagne 'na gr\u00e0nde cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de materi\u00e2le scr\u00eeto in l\u00e9ngoe for\u00e8ste in sce 'n'\u00e0npia g\u00e0mma de argom\u00e9nti.\n\u00c2tre cole\u00e7io\u00een.\nA NDL a l'\u00e0 \u00e0nche \u00e9utto cole\u00e7io\u00een specializ\u00e6 in sce: Mod\u00e8rna St\u00f6ia Pol\u00ectica e Costitu\u00e7ion\u00e2le, Materi\u00e2li in sce l'\u00d2cupa\u00e7i\u00f3n do Giap\u00f3n d\u00f2ppo a Go\u00e6ra, L\u00e9zze e \u00c0tti Prelimin\u00e2ri, Sc\u00e9nsa e Tecnolog\u00eea, M\u00e0ppe, M\u00fbxica, L\u00ecbbri d'\u00e2tri p\u00e0ixi in sci\u00f4 Giap\u00f3n e L\u00ecbbri R\u00e2ri.\nA cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de Mod\u00e8rna St\u00f6ia Pol\u00ectica e Costitu\u00e7ion\u00e2le a conpr\u00e9nde ci\u00f9 \u00f2 m\u00eano 300.000 \u00f2g\u00e8tti corel\u00e6 a-a moderniza\u00e7i\u00f3n pol\u00ectica e leg\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n into XIX s\u00e9colo, incl\u00fbzi i arch\u00ecvi de pap\u00ea \u00f2rigin\u00e2li in sce di inport\u00e0nti \u00f2mmi pol\u00ectichi giapon\u00e9ixi da seg\u00f3nda meit\u00e6 do XIX s\u00e9colo e do prin\u00e7\u00ecpio do XX, c\u00f3mme It\u014d Hirobumi, Iwakura Tomomi, Sanj\u014d Sanetomi, Mutsu Munemitsu, Terauchi Masatake e \u00e2tre fig\u00fbe as\u00e6 inflo\u00e9nti di per\u00eeodi Meiji (1868-1912) e Taish\u014d (1912-1926).\nA NDL a l'\u00e0 'n'est\u00e9iza cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de microform pe 'n tot\u00e2le de ci\u00f9 \u00f2 m\u00eano 30 milio\u00een de p\u00e0gine de pap\u00ea relat\u00eevi a l'\u00d2cupa\u00e7i\u00f3n do Giap\u00f3n d\u00f2ppo a s\u00f2 sconf\u00ectta inta seg\u00f3nda go\u00e6ra mondi\u00e2le. Qu\u00e9sta cole\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'incl\u00f9dde di pap\u00ea prepar\u00e6 da-o Com\u00e0ndo gener\u00e2le (\"General Headquarters\", GHQ), da-o Comand\u00e0nte supr\u00eamo de f\u00f2rse ale\u00e6 (\"Supreme Commander of the Allied Powers\", SCAP), da-a Comisci\u00f3n pe l'estr\u00eamo lev\u00e0nte (Far Eastern Commission, FEC) e da l\"'United States Strategic Bombing Survey Team\" (e c\u00f2pie \u00f2rigin\u00e2li de 'sti pap\u00ea chi s\u00f3n per\u00f2 de propi\u00eat\u00e6 de l'Arch\u00ecvio de St\u00e2to di St\u00e2ti Un\u00eei).\nA cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de L\u00e9zze e \u00c0tti Prelimin\u00e2ri a l'\u00e9 form\u00e2 da ci\u00f9 \u00f2 m\u00eano 170.000 pap\u00ea in giapon\u00e9ize e 200.000 in \u00e2tre l\u00e9ngoe in sce l'ativit\u00e6 da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le e di \u00f2rgani legislat\u00eevi de ci\u00f9 de 70 \u00e2tri p\u00e0ixi, \u00f3ltre che e gaz\u00e9tte ofi\u00e7i\u00e6, i stat\u00fbti, i pa\u00e9i giudi\u00e7i\u00e2i e i trat\u00e2ti interna\u00e7ion\u00e2li de ci\u00f9 de 150 na\u00e7io\u00een.\nA NDL a mant\u00eagne 'na cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de ci\u00f9 de 530.000 l\u00ecbbri e libr\u00e9tti e 2 milio\u00een de microform in sce di argom\u00e9nti ligh\u00e6 a-e sc\u00e9nse. Qu\u00e9sti materi\u00e2li incl\u00f9ddan, tra e \u00e2tre c\u00f6se, t\u00eaxi de dotor\u00e2to for\u00e8ste inte 'n \u00e0nbito scent\u00ecfico, \u00e0tti e rela\u00e7io\u00een de socj\u00eat\u00e6 acad\u00e9miche, cat\u00e0loghi de st\u00e0ndard t\u00e9cnichi, etc.\nA NDL a l'\u00e0 'na cole\u00e7io\u00ec\u00f3n de ci\u00f9 \u00f2 m\u00eano 400.000 m\u00e0ppe do Giap\u00f3n e de \u00e2tri p\u00e0ixi, incl\u00fbze de m\u00e0ppe topogr\u00e0fiche, geol\u00f2giche e idrol\u00f2giche, c\u00e0rte che rem\u00f3ntan a-o per\u00eeodo Meiji (1868-1912) e m\u00e0ppe topogr\u00e0fiche de \u00e2tri p\u00e0ixi.\nA NDL a l'arech\u00e9ugge t\u00f9tti i t\u00eepi de registra\u00e7io\u00een fonogr\u00e0fiche f\u00e6te in Giap\u00f3n e, a-a giorn\u00e2 d'ancheu, a l'\u00e0 'na cole\u00e7i\u00f3n form\u00e2 da 300.000 vin\u00eeli e 200.000 CD.\nAnd\u00e0ndo apr\u00eauvo a 'na tradi\u00e7i\u00f3n ch'a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta incomens\u00e2 da-a Bibliot\u00eaca Inperi\u00e2le, a NDL a cole\u00e7i\u00f3nn-a l\u00ecbbri de \u00e2tri p\u00e0ixi in sci\u00f4 Giap\u00f3n, i qu\u00e6 incl\u00f9ddan r\u00e2ri e ant\u00eeghi pap\u00ea, c\u00f3mme de rela\u00e7io\u00een di miscion\u00e2i eorop\u00eai ch'\u00e0n vixit\u00f2u o Giap\u00f3n into XVI s\u00e9colo.\nA NDL a l'\u00f2spita a cole\u00e7i\u00f3n da v\u00eagia Bibliot\u00eaca Inperi\u00e2le de materi\u00e2li in l\u00e9ngoa giapon\u00e9ize do per\u00eeodo Edo (1603-1867) e de qu\u00e9lli ci\u00f9 ant\u00eeghi. I ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nti cat\u00e0loghi inte 'sta cole\u00e7i\u00f3n chi incl\u00f9ddan:\nKansai-kan.\nO Kansai-Kan (\u00f6 s\u00e6 a Bibliot\u00eaca do Kansai), ch'o l'\u00e0 av\u00e9rto inta prefet\u00fba de Ky\u00f2to into 2002, o l'\u00e9 a seg\u00f3nda strut\u00fba da NDL.\nA NDL a l'\u00e0 stramu\u00f2u into Kansai-kan e cole\u00e7io\u00een de rev\u00ecste \u00f2cident\u00e2li, l\u00ecbbri e \u00e2tri materi\u00e2li scr\u00eeti in de l\u00e9ngoe azi\u00e0tiche desp\u00e6gie da-o giapon\u00e9ize, \u00e7\u00e8rti materi\u00e2li scent\u00ecfichi e tecnol\u00f2gichi (c\u00f3mme rela\u00e7io\u00een t\u00e9cniche, pap\u00ea de socj\u00eat\u00e6 acad\u00e9miche for\u00e8ste, cat\u00e0loghi de st\u00e0ndard t\u00e9cnichi giapon\u00e9ixi e de \u00e2tri p\u00e0ixi, t\u00eaxi de dotor\u00e2to da \u00e2tri p\u00e0ixi e \u00e0tti de conv\u00eagni in l\u00e9ngoe \u00f2cident\u00e2li), rela\u00e7io\u00een de ri\u00e7\u00e8rche scent\u00ecfiche c\u00f3npil\u00e6 con de conven\u00e7io\u00een co-o Minist\u00earo de l'Instru\u00e7i\u00f3n, Colt\u00fba, Sp\u00f2rt, Sc\u00e9nsa e Tecnolog\u00eea, t\u00eaxi de dotor\u00e2to in giapon\u00e9ize e l\u00ecbbri in sce n\u00e0stri.\nViv\u00e0gne digit\u00e2li.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Giap\u00f3n a l'\u00e0, inti \u00f9rtimi \u00e0nni, conpil\u00f2u 'n sc\u00eeto d'Intern\u00e9tte as\u00e6 detagi\u00f2u, scr\u00eeto in giapon\u00e9ize e in ingl\u00e9ize. A s\u00f2 b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 a consc\u00ecste into \"National Diet Library Online Public Access Catalog\" (NDL-OPAC), e \"National Diet Library Digital Collections\" e o \"Minutes of the Imperial Diet and National Diet\".\nA NDL a forn\u00ecsce 'n OPAC (\"On-line public access catalogue\") co-o qu\u00e6 i ut\u00e9nti p\u00eauan f\u00e2 de ri\u00e7\u00e8rche inte t\u00f9tte e cole\u00e7io\u00een da bibliot\u00eaca da \u00f2gni p\u00e0rte do m\u00f3ndo, s\u00e9gge in giapon\u00e9ize che in ingl\u00e9ize. D\u00eauvi\u00e0ndo l'OPAC pe identific\u00e2 viv\u00e0gne e n\u00f9meri de cat\u00e0logo, i ut\u00e9nti da \u00e2tri p\u00e0ixi p\u00eauan \u00f2tegn\u00ee \u00e7\u00e8rti materi\u00e2li da-a NDL gr\u00e0\u00e7ie a-o pr\u00e9stito interbibliotec\u00e2io. Pe de ci\u00f9, a NDL a forn\u00ecsce 'n serv\u00ec\u00e7io a pagam\u00e9nto de riprodu\u00e7i\u00f3n di file pe-i studi\u00f4zi rescid\u00e9nti a l'\u00e8stero. Da-o z\u00f9gno do 2017 a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta pianific\u00e2 a f\u00ecn do serv\u00ec\u00e7io NDL-OPAC pe-o dex\u00e9nbre do m\u00e6ximo \u00e0nno apr\u00eauvo a-o sl\u00e0nso de 'n n\u00eauvo scist\u00eama in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6.\nE cole\u00e7io\u00een digit\u00e2li da NDL (\"NDL Digital Collections\") forn\u00ecscian v\u00e0rri materi\u00e2li digit\u00e2li c\u00f3mme l\u00ecbbri r\u00e2ri, file \u00f2udiovix\u00eevi e materi\u00e2li o qu\u00e6 dir\u00ectto d'aot\u00f4 o l'\u00e9 sch\u00e9ito. I contegn\u00fbi che f\u00f3rman a Bibliot\u00eaca Digit\u00e2le do per\u00eeodo Meiji e a b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti de inm\u00e0gine de l\u00ecbbri r\u00e2ri (v\u00e9dde ci\u00f9 in b\u00e0sso) s\u00f3n \u00f2ua dispon\u00ecbili in sc\u00ea cole\u00e7io\u00een digit\u00e2li da NDL, arch\u00ecvio ch'o l'\u00eaa ciam\u00f2u \"NDL Digitalized Contents\" sc\u00ecnn-a-o 2014.\nUnn-a de fon\u00e7ionalit\u00e6 ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nti do sc\u00eeto d'Intern\u00e9tte da NDL a l'\u00e9 a Bibliot\u00eaca Digit\u00e2le do Per\u00eeodo Meiji (\u8fd1\u4ee3\u30c7\u30b8\u30bf\u30eb\u30e9\u30a4\u30d6\u30e9\u30ea- \"Kindai dejitaru raiburarii\", leteralm\u00e9nte \"Bibliot\u00eaca Digit\u00e2le de l'Et\u00e6 Rec\u00e9nte\". A Bibliot\u00eaca Digit\u00e2le a l'\u00e9 l'evolu\u00e7i\u00f3n in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 do \"Maruzen Meiji Microfilm\", o prod\u00fbto de l'anbi\u00e7i\u00f4zo prog\u00e8tto de inser\u00ee in di microfilm t\u00f9tta a cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de l\u00ecbbri do per\u00eeodo Meiji, a qu\u00e6 a l'\u00e9 form\u00e2 da ci\u00f9 de 60.000 vol\u00f9mmi. A Bibliot\u00eaca Digit\u00e2le a cont\u00eagne de inm\u00e0gine de 'sti trav\u00e0ggi chi, i qu\u00e6 s\u00f3n spart\u00eei in tr\u00e6 categor\u00eee prin\u00e7ip\u00e6 in sci\u00e2 b\u00e2ze da \"Nippon Decimal Classification\" (NDC): 0 - Gener\u00e2le (\u7dcf\u8a18, \"s\u014dki\"); 1 - Filozof\u00eea (\u54f2\u5b66, \"tetsugaku\"); 2 - St\u00f6ia (\u6b74\u53f2, \"rekishi\"); 3 - Sc\u00e9nse soci\u00e2li (\u793e\u4f1a\u79d1\u5b66, \"shakai kagaku\"); 4 - Sc\u00e9nse natur\u00e2li (\u81ea\u7136\u79d1\u5b66, \"shizen kagaku\"); 5 - Ingegner\u00eea e manifat\u00fba (\u5de5\u5b66\u30fb\u5de5\u696d, \"k\u014dgaku/k\u014dgy\u014d\"); 6 - Ind\u00f9stria (\u7523\u696d, \"sangy\u014d\"); 7 - \u00c0rte e atl\u00e9tica (\u82b8\u8853\u30fb\u4f53\u80b2, \"geijutsu/taiiku\"); 8 - Lengo\u00e0ggi (\u8a9e\u5b66, \"gogaku\") e 9 - Letiat\u00fba (\u6587\u5b66, \"bungaku\").\nE inm\u00e0gine no s\u00f3n codifich\u00e6, e d\u00f3nca a no l'\u00e9 posc\u00ecbile efeto\u00e2 de ri\u00e7\u00e8rche pe t\u00e8sto; a \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo a ri\u00e7\u00e8rca in Giapon\u00e9ize pe t\u00ectolo, aot\u00f4, edit\u00f4, sog\u00e8tto e som\u00e2io di trav\u00e0ggi inta b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti a l'\u00e9 posc\u00ecbile. I peri\u00f2dichi do per\u00eeodo Meiji no s\u00f3n incl\u00fbzi inte 'sta cole\u00e7i\u00f3n chi. A Bibliot\u00eaca Digit\u00e2le de l'\u00e9poca Meiji a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta un\u00eea inte Cole\u00e7io\u00een digit\u00e2li da Bibliot\u00eaca da NDL into 2015.\nO sc\u00eeto da NDL o cont\u00eagne a b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti de inm\u00e0gine de l\u00ecbbri r\u00e2ri (\u8cb4\u91cd\u66f8\u753b\u50cf\u30c7\u30fc\u30bf\u30d9\u30fc\u30b9, \"kich\u014dsho gaz\u014d d\u0113tab\u0113su\") asc\u00ec, 'na cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de inm\u00e0gine digit\u00e2li de 37.000 l\u00ecbbri con ilustra\u00e7io\u00een p\u00f9blich\u00e6 pr\u00ecmma do per\u00eeodo Edo. \u00c0nche a ri\u00e7\u00e8rca in giapon\u00e9ize pe t\u00ectolo, aot\u00f4 e n\u00f9mero de elem\u00e9nto a l'\u00e9 posc\u00ecbile inte 'sta b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti chi. A b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti de inm\u00e0gine de l\u00ecbbri r\u00e2ri a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta integr\u00e2 inti \"NDL Digitalized Contents\", d'ancheu Cole\u00e7io\u00een digit\u00e2li da NDL, into 2012.\nA NDL a forn\u00ecsce 'na b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti di verb\u00e2li, s\u00e9gge da Di\u00eata Inperi\u00e2le che da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le, i s\u00f4li inta b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 da NDL inti qu\u00e6 a ri\u00e7\u00e8rca pe t\u00e8sto a fon\u00e7i\u00f3nnn-a pe t\u00f9tto o pap\u00ea. T\u00f9tti i verb\u00e2li da-a crea\u00e7i\u00f3n da Di\u00eata Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le a-a giorn\u00e2 d'ancheu s\u00f3n dispon\u00ecbili inta b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti; pe c\u00f3ntra i s\u00f4li verb\u00e2li aotoalm\u00e9nte dispon\u00ecbili da Di\u00eata Inperi\u00e2le s\u00f3n qu\u00e9lli de s\u00f2 \u00f9rtime d\u00f4e sescio\u00een, \u00f6 s\u00e6 qu\u00e9lle da-o nov\u00e9nbre do 1946 a-o m\u00e0zzo do 1947."}
{"id": "29416", "revid": "1211", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29416", "title": "Bailo", "text": "Un bailo (pr. /'bajlu/) \u00f2 b\u0153\u00fclo (pr. /'b\u00f8jlu/) \u00f2 bavullo\n \u00f2 asc\u00ed b\u00e6ulo (ciu antigamente baullo - da-o spagnollo \"\") o l'\u00e8 'n tipo de capiente cascia da vi\u00e6gio, de legno, c\u0153uio, carton \u00f2 atro materi\u00e2, soventi co-i canti, i spighi e i bordi rinfor\u00e7\u00e6 de metallo e l'interno fodrao de pap\u00ea, pe contegn\u00ee do vestiaio e atra roba.\nDescri\u00e7ion.\nO coercio into lao de d'ato o l'\u00e9 pe-o ciu convesso e o s'arve \u00e0 reb\u00e2sa, saiv'\u00e0 d\u00ee ch'o ven sciu gjando insce-e mappe atac\u00e6 a-o lao de der\u00ea, mentre insci-o lao davanti o p\u0153u aveighe un \u00f2 ciu caina\u00e7\u00e7i \u00f2 s\u00e6 de lengoette co' ina fissua vertic\u00e2 pe ser\u00e2 o bailo co-o luchetto (caina\u00e7\u00e7i da luchetto) \u00f2 munii de 'n nazetto, \u00f2 acricao, che quande vegnan zu o va \u00e0 infi\u00e2se inta fissua da ciav\u0153\u00fca. \nInsci-i doi loei curti de sollito gh'\u00e8 'na maneggia pe-o transporto. I baili ciu picin a maneggia p\u0153uan aveighela insci-o coercio.\n\u00c0 l'interno, atac\u00e6 a-o fondo, ghe p\u0153u ese un p\u00e2 de \u00e7enge, \u00f2 corezze, da strenze con de stecche pe tegn\u00ee ferma a roba.\nAtri scignific\u00e6.\nInta segonda edi\u00e7ion do vocabolaio Caza\u00e7\u00e7a do 1876, a pag. 130, tra-i scignific\u00e6 de \"b\u0153\u00fclo\" (scrito \"be\u00fblo\") gh'\u00e8 quello de \"coverta\" \u00f2 s\u00e6 a covertua de pria di paapeti, foscia pi-a forma convessa ch'a-a f\u00e2 assumegi\u00e2 \u00e0 'n coercio de bailo; gh'\u00e8 asc\u00ec quello de \"burello\", ch'a sai\u00e6 a \"caviggia da inciongi\u00e2\" do vocabolaio Caza\u00e7\u00e7a do 1851 e o \"cavigiotto\" do di\u00e7ionaio de l'Oiv\u00ea do 1851, \u00f2 s\u00e6 o \"borrello\" che-o Nobiasco into so di\u00e7ionaio do 1934 a p. 21 o traduxe con \"bielo\" (scrito \"by\u0113lu\"), saiv'\u00e0 d\u00ee in t\u00f2cco de legno cilindrico ch'o serve a un\u00ee doi cavi (i doi cavi se fan fin\u00ee con do\u00ee \u0153uggi, s'infia un cavo inte l'\u0153uggio de l'atro e o tocco de legno inte l'\u0153uggio do primmo): primma de ipotiz\u00e2 che in zeneize existesse 'na forma \"berullo\" alternativa a \"burello\" da-a qu\u00e6 pori\u00e6 ese derivao questo \"be\u00fblo\", l'\u00e8 o caxo de conscider\u00e2 a poscibilit\u00e6 che ch\u00ec o Caza\u00e7\u00e7a o no se segge sbaliao \u00e0 leze i so aponti e o l'agge pigiao \"b\u00fb\u00eblo\" pe \"be\u00fblo\" (dif\u00e6ti subbito doppo gh'\u00e8 in atro er\u00f4: invece de \"\"cavo\" gh'\u00e8 scrito \"carro\"\"), e comonque segge \"b\u00fb\u00eblo\" che \"be\u00fblo\" inte sta segonda a\u00e7e\u00e7ion o l'avi\u00e6 dovuo ese un lemma \u00e0 parte."}
{"id": "29419", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29419", "title": "National Diet Library", "text": ""}
{"id": "29420", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29420", "title": "Europeana", "text": "Europeana a l'\u00e9 'n port\u00e2 d'Intern\u00e9tte cre\u00f2u da l'Uni\u00f3n Eorop\u00eaa ch'o cont\u00eagne e cole\u00e7io\u00ecn digitaliz\u00e6 do patrim\u00f2nio coltur\u00e2le de ci\u00f9 de 3.000 institu\u00e7io\u00ecn de t\u00f9tta Eor\u00f6pa. O l'incl\u00f9dde e registra\u00e7io\u00ecn de ci\u00f9 de 50 milio\u00ecn de artef\u00e6ti coltur\u00e2li e scent\u00ecfichi, m\u00ecssi ins\u00e9mme inte 'na s\u00f4la piataf\u00f3rma e prezent\u00e6 inte 'na gr\u00e0nde vari\u00eat\u00e6 de m\u00f2ddi pe-i ut\u00e9nti mod\u00e8rni. O prot\u00f2tipo de Europeana o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to o European Digital Library Network (EDLnet), cre\u00f2u into 2008. \nA \"Europeana Foundation\" a l'\u00e9 l'\u00f2rgano de gov\u00e8rno de l'\u00e9nte, o qu\u00e6 o l'\u00e9 costito\u00eeo seg\u00f3ndo a l\u00e9zze oland\u00e9ize c\u00f3mme Stichting Europeana. \nSt\u00f6ia.\nEuropeana a l'\u00e0 av\u00fbo in\u00ec\u00e7io apr\u00eauvo a 'na l\u00e9tia spedi\u00e2 conzontam\u00e9nte inte l'arv\u00ee do 2005 da Jacques Chirac, Prescid\u00e9nte da Rep\u00f9brica Fran\u00e7\u00e9ize, e i pr\u00ecmmi min\u00ecstri de Germ\u00e0nia, Sp\u00e0gna, It\u00e0lia, Pol\u00f2nia e Ungher\u00eea a-o Prescid\u00e9nte da Comisci\u00f3n Eorop\u00eaa, Jos\u00e9 Manuel Dur\u00e3o Barroso. Inte 'sta l\u00e9tia chi a l'\u00eaa sponci\u00e2 a crea\u00e7i\u00f3n de 'na bibliot\u00eaca virto\u00e2le eorop\u00eaa de m\u00f2ddo da r\u00e9nde o patrim\u00f2nio coltur\u00e2le do V\u00eagio Contin\u00e9nte ci\u00f9 acesc\u00ecbile a t\u00f9tti.\nQu\u00e9sta l\u00e9tia a l'\u00e0 contribo\u00eeo a d\u00e2 'n ar\u00e9nbo in ci\u00f9 a-o trav\u00e0ggio che a Dire\u00e7i\u00f3n Gener\u00e2le de Socj\u00eat\u00e6 de Informa\u00e7i\u00f3n e di Media da Comisci\u00f3n Eorop\u00eaa a l'av\u00e9iva za f\u00e6to inti \u00f9rtimi d\u00eax'\u00e0nni, cosc\u00ec c\u00f3mme o prog\u00e8tto \"Telematics for Libraries\". A l'\u00e0 \u00e0nche d\u00e6to 'n f\u00f2rte ar\u00e9nbo de t\u00eepo pol\u00ectico a-a strateg\u00eea da Dire\u00e7i\u00f3n (i2010: comunica\u00e7i\u00f3n in sce bibliot\u00eache digit\u00e2li), public\u00e2 into set\u00e9nbre do 2005. Qu\u00e9sto o l'\u00e0 m\u00ecsso in ci\u00e6o l'inten\u00e7i\u00f3n de cre\u00e2 e sostegn\u00ee 'na bibliot\u00eaca digit\u00e2le eorop\u00eaa, ch'a \u00f2pera inte t\u00f9tta l'Uni\u00f3n Eorop\u00eaa de m\u00f2ddo da incorag\u00ee a cresci\u00e0nsa de socj\u00eat\u00e6 de informa\u00e7i\u00f3n e de ind\u00f9strie di Media corel\u00e6.\nO pr\u00ecmmo prog\u00e8tto ch'o l'\u00e0 inandi\u00f2u a costru\u00e7i\u00f3n de Europeana o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to o \"European Digital Library Network\" (EDLnet), o qu\u00e6 r\u00f2llo o l'\u00eaa qu\u00e9llo de stabil\u00ee 'n mod\u00e9llo de prot\u00f2tipo de 'n serv\u00ec\u00e7io incentr\u00f2u in sce l'ut\u00e9nte, in gr\u00e0ddo de fon\u00e7ion\u00e2 f\u00eaua di conf\u00ecn na\u00e7ion\u00e2li e in v\u00e0rri dom\u00ecnni d'Intern\u00e9tte. A Comisci\u00f3n Eorop\u00eaa a l'\u00e0 finan\u00e7i\u00f2u EDLnet pe m\u00e9zzo do s\u00f2 progr\u00e0mma eContentplus.\nO prot\u00f2tipo do \"European Digital Library Network\" o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to avi\u00f2u a-i 20 de nov\u00e9nbre do 2008. Ini\u00e7ialm\u00e9nte o permett\u00e9iva a v\u00ecxita de 4,5 milio\u00ecn de elem\u00e9nti digit\u00e2li, quantit\u00e6 d\u00f3ggia do prev\u00ecsto, e o l'\u00e0 ri\u00e7ev\u00fbo di contrib\u00fbti in d\u00e6ti da ci\u00f9 de 'n migi\u00e2 de difer\u00e9nti \u00f2rganiza\u00e7io\u00ecn, incl\u00fbze bibliot\u00eache, galer\u00eee e cole\u00e7io\u00ecn de mus\u00eai de f\u00e0mma interna\u00e7ion\u00e2le scito\u00e6 inta v\u00e0rie capit\u00e2li eorop\u00eae.\nO suces\u00f4 de EDLnet, \u00f6 s\u00e6 Europeana versci\u00f3n 1.0, o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to cre\u00f2u into frev\u00e2 do 2009. O l'\u00e9 rest\u00f2u at\u00eevo pe do\u00ee \u00e0nni e m\u00eazo e, into 2010, o prot\u00f2tipo ini\u00e7i\u00e2le o l'\u00eaa \u00f2rm\u00e2i do t\u00f9tto svilup\u00f2u, d\u00e0ndo a poscibilit\u00e6 de v\u00e9dde ci\u00f9 de 10 milio\u00ecn de elem\u00e9nti digit\u00e2li de \u00f2pere coltur\u00e2li. N\u00eauve fon\u00e7ionalit\u00e6 s\u00f3n st\u00e6te az\u00f3nte into 2011, c\u00f3mme 'n scist\u00eama de tradu\u00e7i\u00f3n e 'na fon\u00e7i\u00f3n ch'a perm\u00e9tte d'est\u00e9nde e ri\u00e7\u00e8rche in sce de \u00e2tre piataf\u00f3rme asc\u00ec, Wikipedia incl\u00fbza.\nFon\u00e7io\u00ecn e descri\u00e7i\u00f3n.\nEuropeana a cont\u00eagne de cole\u00e7io\u00ecn de mus\u00eai digitaliz\u00e6 a m\u00ecsse in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6.\nEuropeana a perm\u00e9tte a v\u00ecxita a v\u00e0rri t\u00eepi de contegn\u00fbi, i qu\u00e6 v\u00eagnan da desp\u00e6gie tipolog\u00eee de institu\u00e7io\u00ecn coltur\u00e2li. I \u00f2g\u00e8tti digit\u00e2li che i ut\u00e9nti p\u00eauan trov\u00e2 in sce Europeana no s\u00f3n arch\u00ecvi\u00e6 inte 'na b\u00e0nca d\u00e6ti centraliz\u00e2 ma bensc\u00ec r\u00e8stan inte relat\u00eeve institu\u00e7io\u00ecn coltur\u00e2li, \u00f2spit\u00e6 inti s\u00f2 \"network\". Europeana a l'arech\u00e9ugge de informa\u00e7io\u00ecn d\u00eete metad\u00e6ti in sc\u00ee v\u00e0rri \u00f2g\u00e8tti, \u00f3ltre che 'n'inm\u00e0gine pic\u00ecnn-a de qu\u00e9sti. I ut\u00e9nti \u00e7\u00e8rcan 'ste informa\u00e7io\u00een chi e, qu\u00e0nde \u00e0n trov\u00f2u qu\u00e9lle de pr\u00f2pio inter\u00e8sse, se v\u00eauan v\u00e9dde t\u00f9tti i d\u00e6ti in sce qu\u00e9lla \u00f2pera, d\u00eavan sciac\u00e2 in sci\u00f4 colegam\u00e9nto a-o sc\u00eeto \u00f2rigin\u00e2le da-o qu\u00e6 v\u00eagnan e informa\u00e7io\u00een.\nV\u00e0rie tipolog\u00eee de \u00f2rganiza\u00e7io\u00ecn coltur\u00e2li, c\u00f3mme bibliot\u00eache, mus\u00eai, arch\u00ecvi e cole\u00e7io\u00ecn \u00f2udiovix\u00eeve, in\u00e0ndian o pr\u00f2pio contegn\u00fbo in m\u00f2ddi desp\u00e6gi e seg\u00f3ndo st\u00e0ndard difer\u00e9nti, con di proc\u00eade che p\u00eauan cangi\u00e2 tra-i v\u00e0rri p\u00e0ixi. Pe r\u00e9nde ci\u00f9 f\u00e0\u00e7ile a ri\u00e7\u00e8rca de informa\u00e7io\u00ecn, qu\u00e9ste d\u00eavan \u00ease m\u00e0p\u00e6 inte 'n \u00f9nico st\u00e0ndard com\u00f9n, ciam\u00f2u \"Europeana Semantic Elements\" e baz\u00f2u in sce \"Dublin Core\". Qu\u00e9sto st\u00e0ndard pe-i metad\u00e6ti o l'ad\u00eauvia 'n proc\u00eade a-o m\u00ecnimo com\u00f9n denominat\u00f4 pe l'integra\u00e7i\u00f3n de v\u00e0rri t\u00eepi de contegn\u00fbo digit\u00e2le. Into 2010 o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to introd\u00fbto o Europeana Data Model, 'n stand\u00e0rd pe-i metad\u00e6ti ci\u00f9 r\u00eccco, de m\u00f2ddo da agiut\u00e2 a forn\u00ee a-i ut\u00e9nti informa\u00e7io\u00ecn in ci\u00f9.\nEuropeana a l'ac\u00e9tta i metad\u00e6ti in sc\u00ee \u00f2g\u00e8tti digit\u00e2li, s\u00e9nsa pigi\u00e2 nisci\u00f9nn-a decix\u00f3n in sci\u00e2 digitaliza\u00e7i\u00f3n. Def\u00e6ti, t\u00f9tte e decixo\u00ecn in sce qu\u00e6 \u00f2g\u00e8tti d\u00eavan \u00ease digitaliz\u00e6 s\u00f3n pigi\u00e6 da l'\u00f2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n propi\u00eat\u00e2ia do materi\u00e2le.\nCi\u00f9 de 3.000 institu\u00e7io\u00ecn de t\u00f9tta Eor\u00f6pa \u00e0n contribo\u00eeo a Europeana, incl\u00fbzo o Rijksmuseum, a British Library e o Louvre. D\u00e6ti in sce ci\u00f9 de 10 milio\u00ecn de artef\u00e6ti coltur\u00e2li e scent\u00ecfichi s\u00f3n st\u00e6ti m\u00ecssi ins\u00e9mme in sci\u00e2 piataf\u00f3rma de Europeana, prez\u00e9nt\u00e6 inte di m\u00f2ddi div\u00e8rsci pe-i v\u00e0rri ut\u00e9nti, da-i smartphone a-e API.\nStrateg\u00eee.\nInto s\u00f2 ci\u00e0n strat\u00e9gico pe-o per\u00eeodo 2011-2015, public\u00f2u into zen\u00e2 do 2011, Europeana a l'\u00e0 sotolini\u00f2u i qu\u00e0ttro \u00f2biet\u00eevi strat\u00e9gichi seg\u00f3ndo i qu\u00e6 model\u00e2 o s\u00f2 fut\u00fbro svil\u00f9ppo:\nO suces\u00eevo ci\u00e0n strat\u00e9gico o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to svilup\u00f2u in sci\u00f4 per\u00eeodo 2015-2020.\n\u00d2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n.\nA \"Europeana Foundation\" (Fonda\u00e7i\u00f3n Europeana) a l'\u00e9 l'\u00f2rgano de gov\u00e8rno do serv\u00ec\u00e7io Europeana. I s\u00f2 m\u00e9nbri s\u00f3n i prescid\u00e9nti e i direto\u00ee de v\u00e0rie asocia\u00e7io\u00ecn pe-o patrim\u00f2nio coltur\u00e2le e asocia\u00e7io\u00ecn de informa\u00e7i\u00f3n. A Fonda\u00e7i\u00f3n a prom\u00eauve a colabora\u00e7i\u00f3n tra i mus\u00eai, i arch\u00ecvi, e cole\u00e7io\u00ecn \u00f2udiovix\u00eeve e e bibliot\u00eache, de m\u00f2ddo che i ut\u00e9nti de qu\u00e9ste institu\u00e7io\u00ecn po\u00easan av\u00e9i 'n'intr\u00e2 a-i pr\u00f2ppi contegn\u00fbi incl\u00fbza pe m\u00e9zzo de Europeana e de \u00e2tri serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i.\nA Fonda\u00e7i\u00f3n l'\u00e9 costito\u00eea seg\u00f3ndo o dir\u00ectto oland\u00e9ize c\u00f3mme Stichting Europeana e a l'\u00e0 a s\u00f2 s\u00eade inta Koninklijke Bibliotheek (Bibliot\u00eaca Re\u00e2 di P\u00e0ixi B\u00e0sci), a bibliot\u00eaca na\u00e7ion\u00e2le di P\u00e0ixi B\u00e0sci. A forn\u00ecsce 'n qu\u00e0ddro giur\u00ecdico pi-\u00e2 governance de Europeana, inpieg\u00e0ndo o person\u00e2, fax\u00e9ndo de \u00f2f\u00e8rte pe finan\u00e7iam\u00e9nti e permett\u00e9ndo a sostegnibilit\u00e6 do serv\u00ec\u00e7io.\nL'ato\u00e2le diret\u00f4 esecut\u00eevo da Fonda\u00e7i\u00f3n Europeana a l'\u00e9 Harry Verwayen.\nProg\u00e8tti Europeana.\nA gh'\u00e9 v\u00e0rri prog\u00e8tti, o cosc\u00ec d\u00eeto gr\u00f9ppo Europeana (\"Europeana Group\"), che stan d\u00e0ndo solu\u00e7io\u00ecn tecnol\u00f2giche e contegn\u00fbi a Europeana. Qu\u00e9sto s\u00f3n gest\u00eei da v\u00e0rie institu\u00e7io\u00ecn do patrim\u00f2nio coltur\u00e2le e s\u00f3n in p\u00e0rte finan\u00e7i\u00e6 da-o progr\u00e0mma eContentplus da Comisci\u00f3n Eorop\u00eaa e da-o progr\u00e0mma de sup\u00f2rto a l\"'Information and Communications Technologies Policy Support Programme\" (ICT PSP).\nI prog\u00e8tti do gr\u00f9ppo Europeana s\u00f3n:\nFinan\u00e7iam\u00e9nti.\nEuropeana e i \u00e2tri prog\u00e8tti che forn\u00ecscian contegn\u00fbi a Europeana.eu s\u00f3n st\u00e6ti finan\u00e7i\u00e6 da-a Comisci\u00f3n Eorop\u00eaa s\u00f3tt'a-o progr\u00e0mma eContentplus, l\"'Information and Communications Technologies Policy Support Programme\" (ICT PSP) e \u00e2tri progr\u00e0mmi sc\u00ecmili. Pe parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 inte 'na s\u00e9rie cosc\u00ec \u00e0npia de prog\u00e8tti, i qu\u00e6 ri\u00e7\u00e9ivan f\u00f3ndi da-a Comisci\u00f3n pe 'n tot\u00e2le do 50-100% di pr\u00f2ppi c\u00f3sti, da-i qu\u00e6 s\u00f3n per\u00f2 escl\u00fbze e sp\u00e9ize gener\u00e2li, Europeana a fa 'n scignificat\u00eevo afidam\u00e9nto in sc\u00ee finan\u00e7iam\u00e9nti proveni\u00e9nti da-i minist\u00eari de colt\u00fba e deduca\u00e7i\u00f3n di P\u00e0ixi m\u00e9nbri."}
{"id": "29422", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29422", "title": "Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de Oustr\u00e0lia", "text": "A Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de Oustr\u00e0lia (in ingl\u00e9ize \"National Library of Australia\", NLA), precedentem\u00e9nte conosci\u00fba c\u00f3mme \"Commonwealth National Library\" e \"Commonwealth Parliament Library\", a l'\u00e9 a ci\u00f9 gr\u00e0nde bibliot\u00eaca de refer\u00e9nse d'Oustr\u00e0lia e a respons\u00e0bile, s\u00f3tt'a-i t\u00e8rmini do \"National Library Act 1960\", do \"mantegnim\u00e9nto e do svil\u00f9ppo de 'na cole\u00e7i\u00f3n na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de materi\u00e2le libr\u00e2io, incl\u00fbza 'na cole\u00e7i\u00f3n conpl\u00eata de scr\u00eeti in sce l'Oustr\u00e0lia e i \u00e7itad\u00ecn oustrali\u00e9n\", d\u00f3nca fon\u00e7ion\u00e0ndo c\u00f3mme 'na bibliot\u00eaca na\u00e7ion\u00e2le asc\u00ec. A s\u00f2 s\u00eade centr\u00e2le a l'\u00e9 a Parkes, Canberra, into Terit\u00f6io da Capit\u00e2le Oustrali\u00e0nn-a. \nCre\u00e2 into 1960 co-o \"National Library Act\", a-a f\u00ecn do z\u00f9gno do 2019 a s\u00f2 cole\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00eaa form\u00e2 da 7.717.579 \u00f2g\u00e8tti, co-i s\u00f2 manoscr\u00eeti che \u00f2cup\u00e2van 17.950 m\u00eatri qu\u00e0ddri de sp\u00e0\u00e7io in sc\u00ea sganz\u00eee. A NLA a l'\u00f2spita e gest\u00ecsce \u00e0nche l'avox\u00f2u serv\u00ec\u00e7io de scov\u00e8rta do patrim\u00f2nio coltur\u00e2le Trove, o qu\u00e6 o l'incl\u00f9dde l'intr\u00e2 inte l\"'Australian Web Archive\" e into \"National edeposit\" (NED), 'na gr\u00e0nde cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de giorn\u00e2li, pap\u00ea ofi\u00e7i\u00e6, manoscr\u00eeti e inm\u00e0gine digitaliz\u00e6, cosc\u00ec c\u00f3mme di materi\u00e2li \"born-digital\". \nSt\u00f6ia.\nInto 1901 a Bibliot\u00eaca Parlament\u00e2re do Commonwealth (\"Commonwealth Parliament Library\") a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta cre\u00e2 pe serv\u00ee l'ap\u00e9nn-a form\u00f2u Parlam\u00e9nto Feder\u00e2le de l'Oustr\u00e0lia. Da-a s\u00f2 crea\u00e7i\u00f3n a Bibliot\u00eaca Parlament\u00e2re do Commonwealth a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta svilup\u00e2 de m\u00f2ddo d'av\u00e9i 'n'inport\u00e0nte cole\u00e7i\u00f3n a b\u00e2ze na\u00e7ion\u00e2le. Into 1907 a Comisci\u00f3n Parlament\u00e2re Un\u00eea de Bibliot\u00eache s\u00f3tt'a-a dire\u00e7i\u00f3n do s\u00f2 Prescid\u00e9nte, Sir Frederick William Holder, a l'\u00e0 defin\u00eeo l'\u00f2biet\u00eevo da Bibliot\u00eaca Parlament\u00e2re do Commonwealth con 'ste par\u00f2lle chi:\nDa-o 1923, do\u00ee n\u00f3mmi s\u00f3n st\u00e6ti comunem\u00e9nte d\u00eauvi\u00e6: Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le do Commonwealths (\"Commonwealth National Library\") e Bibliot\u00eaca Parlament\u00e2re do Commonwealth (\"Commonwealth Parliament Library\") pe indic\u00e2, rispetivam\u00e9nte, a cole\u00e7i\u00f3n Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le e qu\u00e9lla Parlament\u00e2re.\nInto 1960 a Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de Oustr\u00e0lia a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta cre\u00e2 co-o \"National Library Act 1960\", e e d\u00f4e bibliot\u00eache s\u00f3n divent\u00e6 de institu\u00e7io\u00een separ\u00e6.\nS\u00eade.\nL'ato\u00e2le pal\u00e0sso da bibliot\u00eaca o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to av\u00e8rto a-i 15 de ag\u00f3sto do 1968 da-o Pr\u00ecmmo Min\u00ecstro John Gorton. O pal\u00e0sso o l'\u00e9 'n prog\u00e8tto do st\u00f9dio de architet\u00fba Bunning and Madden, realiz\u00f2u into st\u00eele cl\u00e0scico despugi\u00f2u t\u00ecpico da f\u00ecn do XX s\u00e9colo. O p\u00f2rtego o l'\u00e9 decor\u00f2u co-o m\u00e0rmo, e vedr\u00e2te s\u00f3n 'n'\u00f2pera de Leonard French e i tr\u00e9i ar\u00e0ssi de Mathieu Mat\u00e9got. O pal\u00e0sso o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to inser\u00eeo inta Commonwealth Heritage List oustrali\u00e0nn-a a-i 22 de z\u00f9gno do 2004.\nS\u00e2le de let\u00fba.\nA gr\u00e0nde costru\u00e7i\u00f3n da Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le a l'\u00f2spita v\u00e0rie s\u00e2le de let\u00fba e cole\u00e7io\u00een. A-o ci\u00e0n ter\u00e9n a gh'\u00e9 a s\u00e2la de let\u00fba prin\u00e7ip\u00e2, d\u00f3nde a gh'\u00e9 a ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte di termin\u00e2li pe coleg\u00e2se a-a R\u00e6 da Bibliot\u00eaca e d\u00f3nde o l'\u00e9 dispon\u00ecbile o colegam\u00e9nto wireless a l'Intern\u00e9tte asc\u00ec. V\u00e0rri serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i s\u00f3n forn\u00eei \u00e0nche inta bibliot\u00eaca da-a z\u00f6na Giorn\u00e2li e St\u00f6ia Famili\u00e2re a-o ci\u00e0n ter\u00e9n, da-a S\u00e2la Let\u00fbe de Cole\u00e7io\u00een Speci\u00e2li a-o pr\u00ecmmo ci\u00e0n e da-e cole\u00e7io\u00een azi\u00e0tiche a-o liv\u00e9llo 3.\nCole\u00e7io\u00een.\nCole\u00e7i\u00f3n gener\u00e2le e oustrali\u00e0nn-a.\nA bibliot\u00eaca a l'arech\u00e9ugge materi\u00e2li prod\u00fbti da \u00e7itad\u00ecn oustr\u00e0li\u00e9n, pe-i oustrali\u00e9n \u00f2 in sce l'Oustr\u00e0lia, realiz\u00e6 inte t\u00f9tti i form\u00e2ti, no s\u00f4lo de \u00f2pere st\u00e0np\u00e6 c\u00f3mme l\u00ecbbri, st\u00f6ie a pont\u00e6, giorn\u00e2li, m\u00e0ppe, manif\u00e8sti, m\u00fbxiche e ephemera st\u00e0np\u00e6, ma \u00e0nche publica\u00e7io\u00een in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 e \u00f2pere no p\u00f9blic\u00e6 c\u00f3mme manoscr\u00eeti, inm\u00e0gine e st\u00f6ie cont\u00e6. Into 1957, Hazel de Berg a l'\u00e0 incomens\u00f2u a registr\u00e2 scrito\u00ee, art\u00ecsti, muxic\u00ecsti e \u00e2tri oustrali\u00e9n lig\u00e6 a l'\u00e0rte, ariv\u00e0ndo a f\u00e2 squ\u00e6xi 1.300 interv\u00ecste. Ins\u00e9mme co-a Bibliot\u00eaca, a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta 'n pioni\u00eare into s\u00f2 c\u00e0npo in Oustr\u00e0lia, travagi\u00e0ndo con l'institu\u00e7i\u00f3n pe vintis\u00e8tte \u00e0nni.\n'N'inport\u00e0nte cole\u00e7i\u00f3n do t\u00eepo \"Australiana\" a l'\u00e9 qu\u00e9lla de John A. Ferguson. A Bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00e0 de particol\u00e6 ecel\u00e9nse inte s\u00f2 cole\u00e7io\u00een, sp\u00e9cce into r\u00e0mmo de \u00e0rte do spet\u00e0colo, b\u00e0llo incl\u00fbzo.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca a cont\u00eagne 'na cole\u00e7i\u00f3n conscider\u00e9vole de materi\u00e2le libr\u00e2io gener\u00e2le e r\u00e2ro, \u00f3ltre che cole\u00e7io\u00een azi\u00e0tiche e da z\u00f6na do Pac\u00ecfico de liv\u00e9llo mondi\u00e2le che van a aoment\u00e2 e cole\u00e7io\u00een in sci\u00e2 colt\u00fba oustrali\u00e0nn-a. Pe de ci\u00f9, e cole\u00e7io\u00een de st\u00e0npe s\u00f3n s\u00f9port\u00e6 da gr\u00e9nde arecug\u00e9ite de microform. A Bibliot\u00eaca a cons\u00e8rva a Cole\u00e7i\u00f3n Braille da Ris\u00e8rva Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le asc\u00ec.\nC\u00f3mme 'na bibliot\u00eaca na\u00e7ion\u00e2le, a NLA in sci\u00e2 b\u00e2ze de dispoxi\u00e7ion contegn\u00fbe into \"Copyright Act 1968\" a l'arech\u00e9ugge seg\u00f3ndo o dep\u00f2xito leg\u00e2le 'na c\u00f2pia de \u00f2gni publica\u00e7i\u00f3n oustrali\u00e0nn-a, i qu\u00e6 edito\u00ee d\u00eavan prezent\u00e2la a-o mom\u00e9nto da s\u00f2 publica\u00e7i\u00f3n.\nA-a f\u00ecn de l'\u00e0nno finan\u00e7i\u00e2io oustrali\u00e0n 2018-2019, a cole\u00e7i\u00f3n da Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le a l'\u00eaa form\u00e2 da 7.717.579 \u00f2g\u00e8tti, ci\u00f9 \u00e2tri 17.950 m\u00eatri de f\u00e9uggi scr\u00eeti a m\u00e0n. E cole\u00e7io\u00een da colt\u00fba oustrali\u00e0nn-a da Bibliot\u00eaca se s\u00f3n svil\u00f9p\u00e6 inta s\u00e9ncia ci\u00f9 gr\u00e0nde arecug\u00e9ita de materi\u00e2li in sci\u00f4 patrim\u00f2nio coltur\u00e2le oustrali\u00e0n de t\u00f9tta a na\u00e7i\u00f3n. Scrito\u00ee, edito\u00ee e ilustrato\u00ee oustrali\u00e9n s\u00f3n sp\u00e9sse v\u00f2tte ri\u00e7erc\u00e6 e b\u00e9n b\u00e9n rapr\u00e9zent\u00e6 inte cole\u00e7io\u00een, s\u00e9gge che e s\u00f2 \u00f2pere s\u00e9ggian p\u00f9blic\u00e6 in Oustr\u00e0lia che a l'\u00e8stero.\nA cole\u00e7i\u00f3n da Bibliot\u00eaca a l'incl\u00f9dde t\u00f9tti i form\u00e2ti de materi\u00e2le, da l\u00ecbbri, giorn\u00e2li, sc\u00eeti d'Intern\u00e9tte e manoscr\u00eeti a qu\u00e0ddri, inm\u00e0gine, m\u00e0ppe, m\u00fbxica e reg\u00ecstra\u00e7io\u00een de st\u00f6ie cont\u00e6, f\u00e9uggi scr\u00eeti a m\u00e0n e ephemera. Ci\u00f9 \u00f2 m\u00eano o 94,1% da cole\u00e7i\u00f3n da Bibliot\u00eaca o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to catalog\u00f2u a-o l\u00f9ggio 2019, pe 'n tot\u00e2le de 5.453.888 \u00f2g\u00e8tti ce se p\u00eauan descrov\u00ee pe m\u00e9zzo do cat\u00e0logo in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6.\nCole\u00e7io\u00een digit\u00e2li.\nA bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00e9 un di leader mondi\u00e2li inte t\u00e9cniche de conserva\u00e7i\u00f3n digit\u00e2le e a mant\u00eagne 'n arch\u00ecvio in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 ciam\u00f2u \"Pandora Archive\", acesc\u00ecbile da l'Intern\u00e9tte pe m\u00e9zzo de \u00e7\u00e8rti sc\u00eeti sele\u00e7ion\u00e6, da-o 1996. L\"'Australian Web Archive\", public\u00f2u into m\u00e0rso do 2019, o m\u00e9tte ins\u00e9mme i d\u00e6ti de PANDORA, de l'\"Australian Government Web Archive\" (AGWA) e de \u00e2tri sc\u00eeti d'Intern\u00e9tte p\u00f9blic\u00e6 in Oustr\u00e0lia. Into bil\u00e0ncio feder\u00e2le do 2019, o gov\u00e8rno o l'\u00e0 m\u00ecsso a dispoxi\u00e7i\u00f3n 10 milio\u00een de d\u00f2lari oustrali\u00e9n pi-\u00e2 bibliot\u00eaca, da distribo\u00ee in qu\u00e0ttro \u00e0nni pi-\u00e2 crea\u00e7i\u00f3n de 'n f\u00f3ndo pi-\u00e2 digitaliza\u00e7i\u00f3n.\nA-o z\u00f9gno do 2019, a Bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00e0 digitaliz\u00f2u \u00e0nche 'n tot\u00e2le de 5.508.008 inm\u00e0gine. Qu\u00e0nde posc\u00ecbile, qu\u00e9ste s\u00f3n c\u00e0reg\u00e6 diretam\u00e9nte in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6.\nSeg\u00f3ndo 'n emendam\u00e9nto a-o \"Copyright Act\" do 2016, t\u00f9tti i contegnu\u00ee cre\u00e6 da s\u00f9bito c\u00f3mme digit\u00e2li d\u00eavan \u00ease dep\u00f2xit\u00e6 inta bibliot\u00eaca asc\u00ec (con v\u00e0rie dispoxi\u00e7io\u00een pe-e bibliot\u00eache di st\u00e2ti feder\u00e2li asc\u00ec). A NLA da-o m\u00e0zzo 2019 a l'\u00f2spita e a gest\u00ecsce o serv\u00ec\u00e7io do \"National edeposit\" (NED). \"Libraries ACT\", \"Libraries Tasmania\", \"Northern Territory Library\", \"State Library of New South Wales\", \"State Library of Queensland\", \"State Library of South Australia\", \"State Library Victoria\" e a \"State Library of Western Australia\" s\u00f3n t\u00f9tte \u00f2rganiza\u00e7io\u00een m\u00e9nbre da colabora\u00e7i\u00f3n.\nCole\u00e7io\u00een azi\u00e0tiche.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00f2spita a ci\u00f9 gr\u00e0nde e a ci\u00f9 ativam\u00e9nte svilup\u00e2 viv\u00e0gna de ri\u00e7\u00e8rca in sce l'\u00c0zia in Oustr\u00e0lia e e ci\u00f9 gr\u00e9nde arecug\u00e9ite de l\u00e9ngoe azi\u00e0tiche inte t\u00f9tto l'emisf\u00earo oustr\u00e2le, con ci\u00f9 de m\u00eazo mili\u00f3n de vol\u00f9mmi inta cole\u00e7i\u00f3n, \u00f3ltre che \u00e0npie viv\u00e0gne in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 e eletr\u00f2niche. A Bibliot\u00eaca a l'arech\u00e9ugge numer\u00f4ze viv\u00e0gne in sc\u00ee v\u00e0rri P\u00e0ixi azi\u00e0tichi scr\u00eete inte l\u00e9ngoe \u00f2cident\u00e2li \u00f2 \u00e0nche in Birm\u00e0n, Cin\u00e9ize, Persi\u00e0n, Indonezi\u00e0n, Giapon\u00e9ize, Khmer, Core\u00e0n, Laoti\u00e0n, Manc\u00e9ize, M\u00f3ngolo, Thailand\u00e9ize, Timor\u00e9ize e Vietnam\u00e9ize.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00e0 acat\u00f2u 'na s\u00e9rie inport\u00e0nte de arecug\u00e9ite in l\u00e9ngoe \u00f2cident\u00e2li e azi\u00e0tiche de ri\u00e7ercato\u00ee e bibliof\u00ecli. Tra de qu\u00e9ste a gh'\u00e9:\nE cole\u00e7io\u00een azi\u00e0tiche se p\u00eauan ri\u00e7erc\u00e2 pe m\u00e9zzo do cat\u00e0logo da Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le.\nQu\u00e0ddri e manoscr\u00eeti.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le a l'\u00f2spita 'n'\u00e0npia cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de qu\u00e0ddri e de manoscr\u00eeti. A cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de manoscr\u00eeti a cont\u00eagne ci\u00f9 de 26 milio\u00een de \u00f2g\u00e8tti separ\u00e6, crov\u00ecndo ci\u00f9 de 10.492 m\u00eatri de sp\u00e0\u00e7io in sc\u00ea sganz\u00eee (\"ACA Australian Archival Statistics\", 1998). A cole\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 pi-\u00e2 ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte in sce l'Oustr\u00e0lia ma a gh'\u00e9 di inport\u00e0nti materi\u00e2li in sce Papoa N\u00eauva Goin\u00eaa, N\u00eauva Zel\u00e0nda e Pac\u00ecfico asc\u00ec. A cole\u00e7i\u00f3n a cont\u00eagne \u00e0nche 'na s\u00e9rie de arecug\u00e9ite de manoscr\u00eeti eorop\u00eai e azi\u00e0tichi \u00f2 di s\u00e9nci \u00f2g\u00e8tti che s\u00f3n st\u00e6ti ri\u00e7ev\u00fbi c\u00f3mme p\u00e0rte d'\u00e2tri gr\u00f9ppi de l\u00ecbbri.\nE cole\u00e7io\u00een de manoscr\u00eeti oustrali\u00e9n rem\u00f3ntan a-o per\u00eeodo de esplora\u00e7i\u00f3n mar\u00ectima e instala\u00e7i\u00f3n de col\u00f2nie, da-o XVIII s\u00e9colo a-a giorn\u00e2 d'ancheu, co-a ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte di materi\u00e2li ch'o l'\u00e9 dat\u00f2u da-o 1890 in p\u00f6i. A cole\u00e7i\u00f3n a conpr\u00e9nde 'n gr\u00e0nde n\u00f9mero de p\u00e9ssi \u00f9nichi ece\u00e7ion\u00e2li, c\u00f3mme o Cartol\u00e2io de Chertsey do XIV s\u00e9colo, o giorn\u00e2le de b\u00f2rdo de James Cook in sce l'HMS \"Endeavour\", inser\u00eeo into Reg\u00ecstro da Mem\u00f6ia do M\u00f3ndo do 2001, i di\u00e2i de Robert O'Hara Burke e William John Wills da spedi\u00e7i\u00f3n de Burke e Wills, e o reg\u00ecstro do vi\u00e2gio de Charles Kingsford Smith e Charles Ulm in sci\u00f4 \"Southern Cross\".\nInta cole\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 raprezent\u00e2 'n'\u00e0npia g\u00e0mma de indiv\u00ecdoi e de fam\u00ecgge, sp\u00e9cce inti c\u00e0npi da pol\u00ectica, da p\u00f9blica aministra\u00e7i\u00f3n, da diploma\u00e7\u00eea, do ti\u00e2tro, de l'\u00e0rte, da letiat\u00fba, da bovinicolt\u00fba e da religi\u00f3n. Ez\u00e9npi de qu\u00e9sti scr\u00eeti s\u00f3n i pap\u00ea de Alfred Deakin, John Latham, Keith Murdoch, Hans Heysen, John Monash, Vance e Nettie Palmer, Alec Derwent Hope, Manning Clark, David Williamson, W.M. Hughes, Robert Menzies, William McMahon, Richard Casey, Geoffrey Dutton, Peter Sculthorpe, Daisy Bates, Jessie Street e qu\u00e9lli de Eddie Mabo e de James Cook, t\u00f9tti do\u00ee inser\u00eei tra i pap\u00ea into Reg\u00ecstro da Mem\u00f6ia do M\u00f3ndo de l'UNESCO into 2001.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00e0 \u00e0nche acat\u00f2u i reg\u00ecstri de v\u00e0rie \u00f2rganiza\u00e7io\u00een na\u00e7ion\u00e2li no governat\u00eeve, tra e qu\u00e6 se p\u00eauan aregord\u00e2 i reg\u00ecstri di Segret\u00e2i Feder\u00e2li do Part\u00eeo Liber\u00e2le, de l'ALP, di Democr\u00e0tichi, do RSL, de l'\"Australian Inland Mission\", de l'\"Australian Union of Students\", de l'\"Australian Ballet\", de l'\"Australian Elizabethan Theatre Trust\", de l'\"Australian Institute of Urban Studies\", de \"Australian Industries Protection League\", de l\"'Australian Conservation Foundation\" e di \"Australian Council of National Trusts\". Pe de ci\u00f9, a Bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00e0 ci\u00f9 \u00f2 m\u00eano 37.000 bob\u00ecnn-e de microfilm de manoscr\u00eeti e pap\u00ea in arch\u00ecvio, pi-\u00e2 ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte di ac\u00e0tti da l'\u00e8stero e de inter\u00e8sse oustrali\u00e0n \u00f2 da z\u00f6na do Pac\u00ecfico.\nA cole\u00e7i\u00f3n de qu\u00e0ddri da Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le a l'incentr\u00e2 in sc\u00ea pers\u00f3nn-e, l\u00eaughi e f\u00e6ti oustrali\u00e9n, da-e pr\u00ecmme esplora\u00e7io\u00een eorop\u00eae into Pac\u00ecfico Meridion\u00e2le a-i f\u00e6ti d'ancheu. Trav\u00e0ggi art\u00ecstichi e fotograf\u00eee s\u00f3n st\u00e6ti ac\u00e0t\u00e6 sorviat\u00f9tto pe-o s\u00f2 val\u00f4 informat\u00eevo, \u00f3ltre che pi-\u00e2 s\u00f2 inport\u00e0nsa c\u00f3mme pap\u00ea st\u00f2richi.\nI t\u00eepi de \u00f2pere raprez\u00e9nt\u00e6 inta cole\u00e7i\u00f3n incl\u00f9ddan inm\u00e0gine, dis\u00e9gni, acquer\u00e9lle, \u00eaui, litograf\u00eee, incixo\u00een, \u00e6goef\u00f3rte e scult\u00fbe/b\u00f9sti.\nServ\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i.\nA Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de Oustr\u00e0lia a l'\u00e0 'n r\u00f2llo de leader na\u00e7ion\u00e2le into svil\u00f9ppo e inta gesti\u00f3n do serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i colaborat\u00eevi in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 co-a comunit\u00e6 de \u00e2tre bibliot\u00eache do p\u00e0ize, rend\u00e9ndo ci\u00f9 f\u00e0\u00e7ile pe-i ut\u00e9nti trov\u00e2 e vixit\u00e2 e viv\u00e0gne informat\u00eeve a liv\u00e9llo na\u00e7ion\u00e2le. A forn\u00ecsce serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i a bibliot\u00eache, edito\u00ee e a-o p\u00f9blico in gener\u00e2le, con l'inscri\u00e7i\u00f3n, dispon\u00ecbile pe-i \u00e7itad\u00ecn oustrali\u00e9n, ch'a da di serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i in ci\u00f9.\nTra i v\u00e0rri conpon\u00e9nti di serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i a gh'\u00e9:\nTrove.\nI serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 minson\u00e6 de d'\u00e2to, e \u00e2tri de ci\u00f9, s\u00f3n acesc\u00ecbili pe m\u00e9zzo do serv\u00ec\u00e7io Trove, o qu\u00e6 o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to avi\u00f2u into 2009. Trove o m\u00e9tte ins\u00e9mme e b\u00e0nche d\u00e6ti de bibliot\u00eache in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6, co-in serv\u00ec\u00e7io na\u00e7ion\u00e2le centraliz\u00f2u ch'o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to realiz\u00f2u co-a colabora\u00e7i\u00f3n de ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte bibliot\u00eache de l'Oustr\u00e0lia. A carater\u00ecstica ci\u00f9 conosci\u00fba de Trove a l'\u00e9 f\u00f2scia l'arecug\u00e9ita digitaliz\u00e2 de giorn\u00e2li oustrali\u00e9n. A ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte di serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i de individoa\u00e7i\u00f3n de viv\u00e0gne NLA s\u00f3n \u00f2ua do t\u00f9tto integr\u00e6 co-o Trove. O serv\u00ec\u00e7io o l'\u00e9 in gr\u00e0ddo de individo\u00e2 viv\u00e0gne in sce l'Oustr\u00e0lia e i oustrali\u00e9n, ariv\u00e0ndo a di materi\u00e2li che de sp\u00e9sso no s\u00f3n dispon\u00ecbili pe-i moto\u00ee de ri\u00e7\u00e8rca est\u00e8rni.\nPublica\u00e7io\u00een.\nA NLA a p\u00f9blica sag\u00ecstica e l\u00ecbbri pe figeu che m\u00f3stran e cole\u00e7io\u00een da bibliot\u00eaca. Qu\u00e9ste publica\u00e7io\u00een rigo\u00e0rdan sorviat\u00f9tto a st\u00f6ia, a st\u00f6ia natur\u00e2le e l'\u00e0rte. A \"NLA Publishing\" a l'\u00e0 goagn\u00f2u div\u00e8rsci \"\".\nAbonam\u00e9nto.\nA registra\u00e7i\u00f3n a-a bibliot\u00eaca a l'\u00e9 de b\u00e0dda pe t\u00f9tti i \u00e7itad\u00ecn oustrali\u00e9n, gr\u00e0\u00e7ie a de t\u00e9sere che v\u00eagnan sped\u00eee a 'n indir\u00ecsso f\u00ecxico pr\u00ecmma che ne s\u00e9gge consent\u00eeo l'\u00fbzo. L'inscri\u00e7i\u00f3n a confer\u00ecsce \u00e7\u00e8rti vant\u00e0ggi in ci\u00f9 pe-i ut\u00e9nti da bibliot\u00eaca, c\u00f3mme o prenot\u00e2 into sc\u00eeto i art\u00eccoli che sai\u00e0n p\u00f6i d\u00eauvi\u00e6 inte s\u00e2le de let\u00fba da bibliot\u00eaca e a poscibilit\u00e6 de v\u00e9dde 'na g\u00e0mma sele\u00e7ion\u00e2 de viv\u00e0gne aotoriz\u00e6, p\u00f9blic\u00e6 da \u00e2tre institu\u00e7io\u00een, c\u00f3mme o t\u00e8sto conpl\u00eato de l\"'Encyclopaedia Britannica\". O l'\u00e9 posc\u00ecbile ordin\u00e2 de c\u00f2pie eletr\u00f2niche de \u00e7\u00e8rti art\u00eccoli e, pe-i m\u00e9nbri che p\u00eauan vixit\u00e2 de pers\u00f3nn-a a Bibliot\u00eaca, o l'\u00e9 posc\u00ecbile \u00f2tegn\u00ee 'n pr\u00e9stito interbibliotec\u00e2io da d\u00eauvi\u00e2 inte s\u00e2le de let\u00fba.\nDireto\u00ee gener\u00e2li.\nI sog\u00e8tti indic\u00e6 inta tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta s\u00f3n st\u00e6ti nomin\u00e6 Diret\u00f4 Gener\u00e2le (\"Director-General\"), \u00f2 co-in t\u00ectolo equival\u00e9nte ma ci\u00f9 v\u00eagio:\nProbl\u00eami.\nInto 2016, co-o r\u00e9izego de t\u00e0ggi a-i finan\u00e7iam\u00e9nti a Trove, 'na canp\u00e0gna p\u00f9blica a l'\u00e0 port\u00f2u o gov\u00e8rno a inpegn\u00e2se a forn\u00ee f\u00f3ndi pe 16,4 milio\u00een de d\u00f2lari oustrali\u00e9n into dex\u00e9nbre do 2016, spart\u00eei in sce 'n per\u00eeodo de qu\u00e0ttro \u00e0nni.\nA l'in\u00ec\u00e7io do 2020, con l'aom\u00e9nto da dom\u00e0nda de t\u00f9tti i t\u00eepi de serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i digit\u00e2li, a Bibliot\u00eaca Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le a l'\u00e0 dov\u00fbo frontez\u00e2 di f\u00f3ndi pe-o s\u00f2 person\u00e2 de l\u00f3ngo ci\u00f9 sc\u00e0rsi pe svilup\u00e2 serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i in sce Trove e o \"National edeposit\", dov\u00e9ndo cosc\u00ec intrapr\u00e9nde 'na ristrutura\u00e7i\u00f3n do s\u00f2 person\u00e2 e de s\u00f2 \u00f2pera\u00e7io\u00een."}
