{"id": "29454", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29454", "title": "Poist\u00e6 da Compagna Communis", "text": "Inta l\u00ecsta di Poist\u00e6 da Compagna Communis, \u00f6 s\u00e6 do L\u00ecbero Com\u00f9n da \u00e7it\u00e6 de Z\u00eana, s\u00f3n incl\u00fbxi i per\u00eeodi inti qu\u00e6 a \u00e7it\u00e6 a l'\u00eaa govern\u00e2 da-i Capit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo, de dedi\u00e7io\u00ecn \u00f2 di governator\u00e2ti.\nA c\u00e0rega a l'\u00eaa de s\u00f2lito de do\u00ee \u00e0nni e de sp\u00e9sso a vegn\u00eeva afid\u00e2 a di foest\u00ea.\nPoist\u00e6 (1191-1256).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i poist\u00e6 el\u00e8tti pr\u00ecmma da n\u00f2mina do Ghig\u00e8rmo B\u00f3ccan\u00e9igra c\u00f3mme Capit\u00e0nio do P\u00f2polo, \u00f6 s\u00e6 qu\u00e9lli tra o 1191 e o 1256.\nPoist\u00e6 (1257-1262).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i poist\u00e6 el\u00e8tti s\u00f3tt'a-o gov\u00e8rno do Capit\u00e0nio do P\u00f2polo Ghig\u00e8rmo B\u00f3ccan\u00e9igra, \u00f6 s\u00e6 qu\u00e9lli tra o 1257 e o 1262.\nPoist\u00e6 (1262-1265).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i poist\u00e6 el\u00e8tti tra o gov\u00e8rno do Capit\u00e0nio do P\u00f2polo Ghig\u00e8rmo B\u00f3ccan\u00e9igra e qu\u00e9llo do Scign\u00f4ro e Capit\u00e0nio \u00d2b\u00e8rto Sp\u00eenoa, \u00f6 s\u00e6 qu\u00e9lli tra o 1262 e o 1265.\nScign\u00f4ro e Capit\u00e0nio (1265).\nGov\u00e8rno do Scign\u00f4ro e Capit\u00e0nio de Z\u00eana \u00d2b\u00e8rto Sp\u00eenoa, into 1265.\nPoist\u00e6 \u00e7itad\u00ecn (1265).\nGov\u00e8rno de do\u00ee poist\u00e6 \u00e7itad\u00ecn, d\u00eeto \"pr\u00ecmma diarch\u00eea D\u00f6ia-Sp\u00eenoa\" asc\u00ec.\nPoist\u00e6 (1266-1270).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i poist\u00e6 el\u00e8tti tra a pr\u00ecmma e a seg\u00f3nda diarch\u00eea D\u00f6ia-Sp\u00eenoa, \u00f6 s\u00e6 qu\u00e9lli tra o 1266 e o 1270.\nCapit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo (1270-1291).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i Capit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo el\u00e8tti inta seg\u00f3nda diarch\u00eea D\u00f6ia-Sp\u00eenoa, d\u00eeta \"Diarch\u00eea di do\u00ee \u00d2b\u00e8rti\" asc\u00ec.\nCapit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo (1291-1295).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i Capit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo el\u00e8tti tra a seg\u00f3nda e a t\u00e8rsa diarch\u00eea D\u00f6ia-Sp\u00eenoa.\nCapit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo \u00e7itad\u00ecn (1296-1299).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i Capit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo el\u00e8tti inta t\u00e8rsa diarch\u00eea D\u00f6ia-Sp\u00eenoa.\nPoist\u00e6 (1300-1306).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i poist\u00e6 el\u00e8tti tra a t\u00e8rsa e a qu\u00e0rta diarch\u00eea D\u00f6ia-Sp\u00eenoa.\nCapit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo \u00e7itad\u00ecn (1306-1310).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i Capit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo el\u00e8tti inta qu\u00e0rta diarch\u00eea D\u00f6ia-Sp\u00eenoa.\nPoist\u00e6 (1311).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i poist\u00e6 el\u00e8tti tra a qu\u00e0rta diarch\u00eea D\u00f6ia-Sp\u00eenoa e a dedi\u00e7i\u00f3n a-o R\u00eccco VIII de Lusenb\u00f9rgo.\nDedi\u00e7i\u00f3n a R\u00eccco VIII de Lusenb\u00f9rgo (1311-1313).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i Vic\u00e2i do S\u00e2cro Rom\u00e2no Inp\u00earo into per\u00eeodo da dedi\u00e7i\u00f3n a-o R\u00eccco VIII de Lusenb\u00f9rgo.\nPoist\u00e6 (1314-1317).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i poist\u00e6 el\u00e8tti tra a dedi\u00e7i\u00f3n a-o R\u00eccco VIII de Lusenb\u00f9rgo e a diarch\u00eea Fi\u00e9schi-Grimaldi.\nCapit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo \u00e7itad\u00ecn (1317-1318).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i Capit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo el\u00e8tti inta diarch\u00eea Fi\u00e9schi-Grimaldi.\nDedi\u00e7i\u00f3n a B\u00e8rto I de N\u00e0poli (1319-13??).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i Vic\u00e2i e i Poist\u00e6 do R\u00e9gno de N\u00e0poli into per\u00eeodo da dedi\u00e7i\u00f3n a-o B\u00e8rto I de N\u00e0poli.\nCapit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo \u00e7itad\u00ecn (1335-1339).\nA tab\u00e9lla chi de s\u00f3tta a fa v\u00e9dde i Capit\u00e0nni do P\u00f2polo el\u00e8tti inta qu\u00ecnta diarch\u00eea D\u00f6ia-Sp\u00eenoa, s\u00f9bito pr\u00ecmma de l'ele\u00e7i\u00f3n do pr\u00ecmmo d\u00fbxe, o Scim\u00f3n B\u00f3ccan\u00e9igra."}
