{"id": "29592", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29592", "title": "Cul\u00f3nne", "text": "Cul\u00f3nne (in itali\u00e0n: \"Colonne\") l'\u00e9 'na frasi\u00f3n id Cantaluvu ch'a gh'\u00f2 28 abitanti. A s'tr\u00f6va inte l'\u00d2ta Val Burb\u00e0ia a 371m d'altit\u00fcdine, int'ei cum\u00fcne 'd Cantaluvu (Cantalovvu). L'\u00e8 'n pa\u00ecze 'd lingua e tradi\u00e7i\u00f3n-i l\u00ecguri inta Prov\u00e9incia 'd Lisandria."}
{"id": "29594", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29594", "title": "Psara (com\u00f9n)", "text": "O com\u00f9n de Psara o l'\u00e9 'n com\u00f9n inta perifer\u00eea de l'Eg\u00eao Setentrion\u00e2le form\u00f2u pi-\u00e2 ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte da l'\u00eezoa de Psara e da \u00e2tri izo\u00f6ti dezabit\u00e6, tra i qu\u00e6 o ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte o l'\u00e9 qu\u00e9llo de Antipsara. O com\u00f9n, o qu\u00e6 a difer\u00e9nsa de qu\u00e9llo de Sc\u00eeo o l'\u00e0 mantegn\u00fbo i s\u00f2 conf\u00ecn \u00f2rigin\u00e2li, o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to sc\u00ecnn-a-o 2010 p\u00e0rte da prefet\u00fba de Sc\u00eeo, pe p\u00f6i pas\u00e2, co-a rif\u00f3rma do cosc\u00ec d\u00eeto progr\u00e0mma \"Kallikratis\", inta n\u00eauva unit\u00e6 perif\u00e9rica de Sc\u00eeo.\nAministra\u00e7i\u00f3n.\nUnit\u00e6 monicip\u00e2li.\nO com\u00f9n de Psara o no l'\u00e9 spart\u00eeo in de unit\u00e6 monicip\u00e2li. \u00d3ltre a-o p\u00e0ize capol\u00eaugo, o qu\u00e6 o l'av\u00e9iva 'na popola\u00e7i\u00f3n de 454 abit\u00e0nti a-o censim\u00e9nto do 2011, a s\u00f4la localit\u00e6 abit\u00e2 a-a giorn\u00e2 d'ancheu a l'\u00e9 in corispond\u00e9nsa do monest\u00ea de l'Ason\u00e7i\u00f3n da V\u00e8rgine, d\u00eaxe chil\u00f2metri a n\u00f2rd do capol\u00eaugo. Seg\u00f3ndo o censim\u00e9nto gh'\u00e9 4 pers\u00f3nn-e che stan in sci\u00e2 pic\u00ecnn-a \u00eezoa de Antipsara asc\u00ec.\nA \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo a popola\u00e7i\u00f3n a peu aoment\u00e2 da-i 458 abit\u00e0nti che st\u00e0n into com\u00f9n pe t\u00f9tto l'\u00e0nno sc\u00ecnn-a-i 1.000 de per\u00eeodo est\u00eevo, qu\u00e0nde a g\u00e9nte de l'\u00eezoa ch'a l'\u00e9 an\u00e6ta a st\u00e2 in \u00e2tre p\u00e0rte da Gr\u00eacia a t\u00f3rna a Psara pe-e vac\u00e0nse."}
{"id": "29596", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29596", "title": "Antipsara", "text": "Antipsara a l'\u00e9 'n'\u00eezoa pic\u00ecnn-a da Gr\u00eacia scito\u00e2 inta p\u00e0rte de lev\u00e0nte do M\u00e2 Eg\u00eao, da-ar\u00e9nte a-a ci\u00f9 gr\u00e0nde \u00eezoa de Psara, da-a qu\u00e6 a n'\u00e0 pigi\u00f2u o n\u00f3mme. Da-o p\u00f3nto de v\u00ecsta aministrat\u00eevo, Antipsara a fa p\u00e0rte do com\u00f9n de Psara e, seg\u00f3ndo o censim\u00e9nto do 2011, in qu\u00e9llo \u00e0nno ghe st\u00e2va qu\u00e0ttro pers\u00f3nn-e.\nGi\u00f6graf\u00eea.\nAntipsara a se tr\u00eauva a pon\u00e9nte de l'estremit\u00e6 s\u00f9d-\u00f2cident\u00e2le de l'\u00eezoa de Psara, a 'na dist\u00e0nsa de 1,3 m\u00ecggia mar\u00ecnn-e, \u00f6 s\u00e6 2,4 km, co-o s\u00f2 c\u00e9ntro ch'o l'\u00e9 a-e cordin\u00e6 38\u00b0 33' N, 25\u00b0 32' E. A superf\u00eccce tot\u00e2le de Antipsara a l'\u00e9 de 4,498 km2, d\u00f3nca a l'\u00e9 d\u00eaxe v\u00f2tte ci\u00f9 pic\u00ecnn-a de Psara. Ci\u00f9 \u00f2 m\u00e8no a-a meit\u00e6 da c\u00f2sta de lev\u00e0nte de l'\u00eezoa a s'\u00e0rve a b\u00e2ia de Limani, riv\u00f2lta v\u00e8rso Psara, m\u00e9ntre o s\u00f2 p\u00f3nto ci\u00f9 \u00e8rto o l'\u00e9 o \"Psili Rachi\", o qu\u00e6 o l'ar\u00eeva a 130 m\u00eatri in sci\u00f4 liv\u00e9llo do m\u00e2.\nO seu de Antipsara o l'\u00e9 pi-\u00e2 ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte arso\u00eeo e roci\u00f4zo e, da-o p\u00f3nto de v\u00ecsta geol\u00f2gico, l'\u00eezoa a l'\u00e9 form\u00e2 sorviat\u00f9tto da pr\u00eee s\u00eami-metam\u00f2rfiche, m\u00e9ntre inta s\u00f2 p\u00e0rte setentrion\u00e2le gh'\u00e9 de pr\u00eee de \u00f2r\u00ecgine vulc\u00e0nica, c\u00f3mme delen\u00ecti oligocl\u00e0stiche.\nD'in g\u00eeo a Antipsara gh'\u00e9 di izo\u00f6ti ci\u00f9 pic\u00ecn asc\u00ec, \u00f6 s\u00e6 qu\u00e9lli de \"K\u00e1tou nis\u00ed\", \"Mesiak\u00f3\" e \"Sk\u00f3gio\". L'\u00eezoa a l'\u00e9 a 51 m\u00ecggia mar\u00ecnn-e (94 km) da-o C\u00e0ppo Kafir\u00e9as, 43 nm (80 km) da l'\u00eezoa de Sc\u00eero, 15 nm (28 km) da-o C\u00e0ppo Melani\u00f3 de Sc\u00eeo e 26 nm (48 km) da-i izo\u00f6ti de Kalogeroi.\nSt\u00f6ia.\nScib\u00e9n che a-a giorn\u00e2 d'ancheu a l'\u00e9 squ\u00e6xi do t\u00f9tto dezabit\u00e2, gr\u00e0\u00e7ie a di sc\u00e2vi archiol\u00f2g\u00eechi f\u00e6ti in sce l'\u00eezoa l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to prov\u00f2u c\u00f3mme a fo\u00eese abit\u00e2 s\u00e9gge a-i t\u00e9npi da Gr\u00eacia ant\u00eega che into per\u00eeodo do dom\u00ecnio rom\u00e2no. Inti s\u00e9coli suces\u00eevi, inte l'\u00eezoa gh'\u00eaa anc\u00f3n 'n p\u00f2rto pic\u00ecn, control\u00f2u inte l'\u00f3rdine da bizant\u00ecn, zen\u00e9ixi e \u00f2tom\u00e0n.\nD'ancheu Antipsara a l'\u00e9, into per\u00eeodo est\u00eevo, coleg\u00e2 a-a vix\u00ecnn-a Psara da inbarca\u00e7io\u00ecn che p\u00f2rtan i tur\u00ecsti a f\u00e2 de g\u00eete in sce l'\u00eezoa.\nP\u00f2sti de inter\u00e8sse.\nAntipsara a l'\u00e9 vixit\u00e2 sorviat\u00f9tto pe-i s\u00f2 paiz\u00e0ggi e-e s\u00f2 spi\u00e2ge, scito\u00e6 s\u00f4lo inta p\u00e0rte s\u00f9d-\u00f2rient\u00e2le de l'\u00eezoa d\u00e6to che o r\u00e8sto de s\u00f2 c\u00f2ste o l'\u00e9 \u00e8rto e roci\u00f4zo. Tra e r\u00eeve ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nti gh'\u00e9 qu\u00e9lla de \"Ag\u00edou Io\u00e1nni\", l\u00f3ngo a c\u00f2sta de lev\u00e0nte, e qu\u00e9lle de \"Sklavolimni\u00f3nas\", \"Papantri\u00e1\", \"Psil\u00ed\" e Stef\u00e1ni, inta p\u00e0rte meridion\u00e2le de l'\u00eezoa. \nIn sce l'\u00eezoa gh'\u00e9 \u00e0nche d\u00f4e pic\u00ecnn-e g\u00eax\u00e9tte, anc\u00f3n abit\u00e6 da m\u00f3neghi e erm\u00ectti, i qu\u00e6 s\u00f3n i s\u00f4li abit\u00e0nti de Antipsara a-a giorn\u00e2 d'ancheu. In particol\u00e2 gh'\u00e9 e d\u00f4e cap\u00e9lle de S\u00e0n Z\u00e2ne Bat\u00ecsta (\"\u00c1gios Io\u00e1nnis o Pr\u00f3dromos\") e de S\u00e0n Z\u00e2ne Evangel\u00ecsta (\"\u00c1gios Io\u00e1nnis o Theol\u00f3gos\"), scito\u00e6 t\u00f9tte d\u00f4e in sc\u00eea c\u00f2sta de lev\u00e0nte de l'\u00eezoa. \nPe de ci\u00f9, Antipsara a l'\u00e9 'n inport\u00e0nte sc\u00eeto pe l'avistam\u00e9nto di \u00f6x\u00e9lli, d\u00e6to che gh'\u00e9 v\u00e0rie sp\u00eace che v\u00eagnan a f\u00e2 o n\u00eeo chi. Prez\u00e9npio gh'\u00e9 o magr\u00f3n da-o s\u00f9ffo (\"Phalacrocorax aristotelis\"), o f\u00e0rco da reg\u00ecnn-a (\"Falco eleonorae\"), a b\u00e8rta magi\u00f4 atl\u00e0ntica (\"Calonectris diomedea\") e a b\u00e8rta min\u00f4 mediter\u00e0nia (\"Puffinus yelkouan\"). "}
{"id": "29597", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29597", "title": "Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de C\u00e2iro", "text": "A sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de C\u00e2iro, (in italian \"Stazione di Cairo Montenotte\") a l'\u00e8 inn-a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n ferovi\u00e0ria italiann-a ch'a se treuva in sci\u00e2 Ferov\u00eea Lisciandria-San Gioxeppe de C\u00e2iro, averta a part\u00ec dao 1874, a l'e ao servi\u00e7io do com\u00f9n de C\u00e2iro, inta Provinsa de Sann-a.\nInpianti.\n\u2022 Segondo a clasc\u00ecfica de RFI a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de\u00a0C\u00e2iro a l'\u00e8 inn-a sta\u00e7ion de categor\u00eea \"bronzo\" perch\u00e8 se ghe ferman s\u00f4lo tr\u00eani region\u00e2li."}
