{"id": "29626", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29626", "title": "Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Ter\u00e7o-Montab\u00f3n", "text": "A sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de T\u00e8r\u00e7o-Montab\u00f3n (in italian \"Terzo-Montabone\"), a l'\u00e8 inn-a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n ferovi\u00e0ria italiann-a ch'a se treuva in sci\u00e2 l\u00ecnia Lisciandria-San Gioxeppe de C\u00e2iro, averta a part\u00ec dao 1874, a l'e ao servi\u00e7io do com\u00f9n de T\u00e8r\u00e7o, inta\u00a0 Provinsa de Lisciandria e de quello de Montab\u00f3n inta Provinsa d'\u00c0sti, l\u00ec vixin.\nInpianti.\n\u2022 Segondo a clasc\u00ecfica de RFI a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de\u00a0T\u00e8r\u00e7o-Montanb\u00f3n a l'\u00e8 inn-a sta\u00e7ion de categor\u00eea \"bronzo\"."}
