{"id": "29633", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29633", "title": "Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Carans\u00e0n-Sant'Andr\u00eca", "text": "A sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Carans\u00e0n-Sant'Andria (in italian \"Stazione di Caranzano-Sant'Andrea\"), a l'\u00e9a inn-a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n ferovi\u00e0ria italiann-a ch'a se treuva in sci\u00e2 Lisciandria-San Gioxeppe de C\u00e2iro, averta a part\u00ec dao 1909, a l'e ao servi\u00e7io do com\u00f9n de Cassine, inta\u00a0 Provinsa de Lisciandria, p\u00e9 e seu fra\u00e7io\u00een de Caransan e Sant'Andria.\nSt\u00f2ia.\nAv\u00e8rta into 1909 p\u00e8 vegn\u00ee inc\u00f3ntro a-e esig\u00eanse da popola\u00e7i\u00f3n loc\u00e2le, l'\u00fbrtima ferm\u00e2 a l'\u00e8 avegn\u00fba into 1985, m\u00e8ntre a l'\u00e8 st\u00e6ta riconosci\u00fba ufi\u00e7ialm\u00e8nte comme dism\u00e9ssa into 2003.\nInpianti.\nA ferm\u00e2ta a l'\u00e9a serv\u00eea t\u00e0nto da tr\u00eani m\u00e8rci qu\u00e0nto da tr\u00eani pi-i paseg\u00eari, con s\u00f4lo 'na banchinn-a dot\u00e2 de marciap\u00e6 ch'a l'an\u00e2va a afianc\u00e2 l'\u00fbnico bin\u00e2io pas\u00e0nte."}
