{"id": "29635", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29635", "title": "Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Gavon\u00e2", "text": "A sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Gavon\u00e2 (in italian \" Stazione di Gavonata\") a l'\u00e9a inn-a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n ferovi\u00e0ria italiann-a ch'a se treuva in sci\u00e2 l\u00ecnia Lisciandria-San Gioxeppe de C\u00e2iro, averta a part\u00ec dao 1923; a l'\u00e9a ao servi\u00e7io do com\u00f9n de Cassine, inta\u00a0Provinsa de Lisciandria, pi-a fra\u00e7i\u00f3n de Gavon\u00e2.\nSt\u00f2ia.\nA sta\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta av\u00e8rta into 1923 pe vegn\u00ee inc\u00f3ntro a-e esig\u00e8nse da popola\u00e7i\u00f3n. A-o mom\u00e9nto i tr\u00eani no se f\u00e8rman chi, donca a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n a riz\u00f3lta desm\u00ecssa.\nInpianti.\nA sta\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e9a serv\u00eea s\u00f4lo da tr\u00eani region\u00e2li e a l'\u00e9a dot\u00e2 de 'n s\u00f4lo bin\u00e2io pass\u00e0nte, afianc\u00f2u da-a banch\u00ecnn-a."}
