{"id": "29996", "revid": "10132", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29996", "title": "Jos\u00e9 Serrato", "text": "Jos\u00e9 Serrato (Muntevideu, 30 de set\u00e9nbre du 1868, 7 de set\u00e9nbre du 1960) u l'\u00e9 st\u00eatu in ecunumista, inzegn\u00ea e puliticu \u00fcruguay\u00e0n, Prescidente Cunstitusiun\u00e2le fra u 1923 e u 1927.\nV\u00ectta.\nA s\u00f6 famiggia a l'\u00eaa urigin\u00e2ia du paize de Gi\u00fcstexine, figgiu de Domingo Serrato (Dumenegu di S\u00e9r\u00e8i) e de Mar\u00eda Berger\u00f3o. L'ax\u00eava frequent\u00f2n a sc\u00f6a Elbio Fern\u00e1ndez, fund\u00e2 da parte de Jos\u00e9 Pedro Varela, p\u00e9 dap\u00f6 laure\u00e2se in-te l'\u00dcniverscit\u00ea di geometri in-tu 1888. De seguitu l'ha st\u00fcdi\u00f2n izegner\u00eea in-ta \u00dcniverscit\u00ea da rep\u00fcblica, laureanduse in-te l'\u00e0nnu 1892, esendu \u00fcn di primmi tr\u00e9i inzegn\u00ea a cunsegu\u00ee u titulu. L'ha travaggi\u00f2n cumme prufes\u00fb e mestru de matematica in-te l'insegnamentu segund\u00e0iu e a livellu ci\u00fc de d'\u00e2tu. Da segnal\u00e2 u matrimoniu cun Josefina Perey.\nAtivit\u00ea pulitica.\nMenbru du part\u00eeu puliticu du Colorado, l'\u00ea st\u00eatu deput\u00f2n, Ministru di Travaggi P\u00fcblici in-tu 1913, de Finanse fra u 1904 e u 1906, de l'Internu in-tu 1911 e di Esteri fra u 1943 e u 1945.Elez\u00fcu Prescidente da Rep\u00fcblica in-tu 1923, l'\u00ea rest\u00f2n in c\u00e0rega fin a-u 1927. In-tu mentre l'ha firm\u00f2n in trat\u00f2n de cunfin cun l'Argentina, istitu\u00ecu a Curte Eletur\u00e2le, inaugur\u00f2n u Pal\u00e0ssu Legislat\u00ecvu, cre\u00f2n i fundi de pensciunamentu e u relat\u00ecvu scistemma a livellu siv\u00ecle, de ansianit\u00ea e p\u00e9 i impiegh\u00ea de b\u00e0nche.\nL'\u00ea st\u00eatu asc\u00ecu primmu prescidente de l'Uruguay a esse elez\u00fcu p\u00e9 vutasi\u00f9n \u00fcnivers\u00e2le, mecanismu previstu daa Custitusiun eman\u00e2 in-tu 1918.\nIncareg\u00f2n p\u00f6i a l'internu du Cunseggiu du Stattu du 1942, cun u sc\u00f2ppu de furmul\u00e2 a Custitusiun du 1942.\nAtivit\u00ea giurnalistica.\nJos\u00e9 Serrato l'ha p\u00fcblic\u00f2n quarche articulu cu-u survanumme \"Engignour\", da-u fransese \"inzegn\u00ea\", u s\u00f6 mest\u00ea. Sutta a stu-chi l'ha p\u00fce intrategn\u00fcu in'inpurtante disc\u00fcsciun finansi\u00e0ria cun Julio Herrera y Obes in-te l'annu 1902 p\u00e9 v\u00eda de 'na s\u00e9rie de art\u00ecculi p\u00fcblich\u00ea in sci giurn\u00e2li de Muntevideu\nAtivit\u00ea pulitica in-tu sport.\nL'\u00ea ricurd\u00f2n p\u00e9 av\u00ea dir\u00e8ttu u \u00abLaudo Serrato\u00bb, ch'u l'ha segn\u00f2n a riunificasiun du bal\u00f9n uruguayan in-tu 1926. U m\u00eaximu l'\u00eaa st\u00eatu divizu in-tu 1922, fra l'\u00abAsociaci\u00f3n Uruguaya de Football\u00bb, capitan\u00e2 da-a squaddra nasiun\u00e2le de bal\u00f9n, e a \u00abFederaci\u00f3n Uruguaya de Football\u00bb, du \u00abClub Atl\u00e9tico Pe\u00f1arol\u00bb. In-tu 1925 sun st\u00eati suspezi i turnei urganiz\u00ea da-e due asuciasiui e, dap\u00f6 ina lunga tratat\u00ecva, s'\u00ea decizu che p\u00e9 1926 se duxeva tegn\u00ee in Turneu du Cunseggiu Pruviz\u00f2riu. A-a fin s'\u00ea riv\u00ea a-a definisiun de in \u00fcnica urganizasi\u00f9n l\"'Asociaci\u00f3n Uruguaya de F\u00fatbol\"."}
{"id": "29997", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29997", "title": "Canpion\u00f2u itali\u00e0n de bal\u00f3n", "text": "O canpion\u00f2u itali\u00e0n de bal\u00f3n (\"campionato italiano di pallapugno\" in itali\u00e0n) o l'\u00e9 l'ins\u00e9mme di v\u00e0rri torn\u00eai de bal\u00f3n, a liv\u00e9llo na\u00e7ion\u00e2le e region\u00e2le, inandi\u00e6 da-a Federa\u00e7i\u00f3n Itali\u00e0nn-a Bal\u00f3n (F.I.P.A.P., \"Federazione Italiana Pallapugno\"). I canpion\u00e6 s\u00f3n spart\u00eei e \u00f2rganiz\u00e6 in sce qu\u00e0ttro liv\u00e9lli, riconosci\u00fbi c\u00f3mme a car\u00e0tere diletant\u00ecstico, ci\u00f9 qu\u00e9lli riserv\u00e6 a-i zugo\u00e9i ci\u00f9 zo\u00eani. T\u00f9tti i liv\u00e9lli, s\u00e9gge inte categor\u00eee \"senior\" che inte qu\u00e9lle di ci\u00f9 zo\u00eani, p\u00f3rtan a l'asegna\u00e7i\u00f3n de 'n scud\u00e9tto e de 'na C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de categor\u00eea.\nE v\u00e0rie socj\u00eat\u00e6 parte\u00e7ipi\u00e0n a-i desp\u00e6gi canpion\u00e6 in sci\u00e2 b\u00e2ze di dir\u00ectti sport\u00eevi go\u00e2gn\u00e6 inta stagi\u00f3n pas\u00e2 e, a difer\u00e9nsa de \u00e2tre discipl\u00ecnn-e, a m\u00e6xima socj\u00eat\u00e6 a peu av\u00e9i di dir\u00ectti sport\u00eevi t\u00e6 da parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 a ci\u00f9 canpion\u00e6.\nS\u00e9rie A.\nA S\u00e9rie A a l'\u00e9 o ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte torn\u00eao na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de bal\u00f3n, es\u00e9ndo a m\u00e0scima categor\u00eea de sto sp\u00f2rt chi, e d'ancheu ghe ne fan p\u00e0rte d\u00eaxe squ\u00e0ddre in tot\u00e2le, spart\u00eee tra a Lig\u00f9ria e o Piem\u00f3nte. A m\u00e0scima s\u00e9rie de bal\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 \u00f2rganiz\u00e2 in sce tr\u00e6 f\u00e2ze, seg\u00f3ndo a cosc\u00ec d\u00eeta \"f\u00f3rmola Bresci\u00e0n\":\nPe de ci\u00f9, e d\u00f4e squ\u00e0ddre inte 'na poxi\u00e7i\u00f3n ci\u00f9 \u00e2ta inti g\u00eeo\u00ecn de and\u00e2ta e de rit\u00f3rno go\u00e2gnan l'intr\u00e2 a-a C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia.\nS\u00e9rie B.\nA S\u00e9rie B a l'\u00e9 o seg\u00f3ndo liv\u00e9llo do canpion\u00f2u itali\u00e0n de bal\u00f3n, form\u00e2 de d\u00f3zze squ\u00e0ddre chi v\u00eagnan t\u00f3rna s\u00e9gge da-o Piem\u00f3nte che da-a Lig\u00f9ria. C\u00f3mme pi-\u00e2 s\u00e9rie magi\u00f4, a S\u00e9rie B a l'\u00e9 div\u00eeza l\u00ea asc\u00ec inte tr\u00e6 f\u00e2ze:\nE squ\u00e0ddre inte pr\u00ecmme \u00e9utto poxi\u00e7io\u00ecn da \"regular season\" go\u00e2gnan l'intr\u00e2 a-a C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de S\u00e9rie B.\nS\u00e9rie C1.\nA S\u00e9rie C1 a l'\u00e9 o t\u00e8rso liv\u00e9llo do canpion\u00f2u itali\u00e0n de bal\u00f3n. D'ancheu, inte sta s\u00e9rie chi ghe z\u00eaugan ch\u00ecnze squ\u00e0ddre, spart\u00eee in sce do\u00ee g\u00eeo\u00ecn: \u00e9utto into g\u00ee\u00f3n A e-e \u00e2tre s\u00e8tte into g\u00ee\u00f3n B. Cosc\u00ec c\u00f3mme e s\u00e9rie magio\u00ee, a l'\u00e9 div\u00eeza inte tr\u00e6 f\u00e2ze:\nE d\u00f4e squ\u00e0ddre clascific\u00e6 a-i pr\u00ecmmi p\u00f3sti da pr\u00ecmma f\u00e2ze a g\u00eeo\u00ecn go\u00e2gnan a partecipa\u00e7i\u00f3n dir\u00e8tta a-a fin\u00e2le de C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de S\u00e9rie C1.\nS\u00e9rie C2.\nA S\u00e9rie C2 a l'\u00e9 o qu\u00e0rto, e \u00f9rtimo, liv\u00e9llo do canpion\u00f2u itali\u00e0n de bal\u00f3n. D'ancheu gh'\u00e9 quat\u00f2rze squ\u00e0ddre che fan p\u00e0rte de sta categor\u00eea chi, s\u00e9gge l\u00ecguri che piemont\u00e9ixi. A l'\u00e9 spart\u00eea inte s\u00f2lite tr\u00e6 f\u00e2ze e d\u00f3nca gh'\u00e9:\nE d\u00f4e squ\u00e0ddre clascific\u00e6 a-i pr\u00ecmmi p\u00f3sti da pr\u00ecmma f\u00e2ze go\u00e2gnan a partecipa\u00e7i\u00f3n dir\u00e8tta a-a fin\u00e2le de C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de S\u00e9rie C2.\nCanpion\u00e6 da zo\u00eani.\nCanpion\u00f2u Under 25.\nA-o canpion\u00f2u Under 25 p\u00eauan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 t\u00f9tti i zugo\u00e9i con m\u00eano de 25 \u00e0nni, s\u00e9nsa a poscibilit\u00e6 de inser\u00eene de ci\u00f9 v\u00eagi inte squ\u00e0ddre. D'ancheu, e squ\u00e0ddre che z\u00eaugan inte sta categor\u00eea s\u00f3n \u00e9utto, m\u00ecsse ins\u00e9mme inte 'n \u00f9nico g\u00ee\u00f3n a l'itali\u00e0nn-a con part\u00eee d'and\u00e2ta e de rit\u00f3rno. T\u00f9tte e squ\u00e0ddre s\u00f3n p\u00f6i am\u00ecsse a-a seg\u00f3nda f\u00e2ze, costito\u00eea da 'n s\u00e9ncio tabel\u00f3n ch'o p\u00e0rte da-i qu\u00e0rti de fin\u00e2le e ch'o fin\u00ecsce con l'asegna\u00e7i\u00f3n do scud\u00e9tto Under 25. A squ\u00e0ddra ch'a go\u00e2gna o t\u00ectolo da categor\u00eea a l'\u00e0 o dir\u00ectto, inta stagi\u00f3n a vegn\u00ee, d'inscr\u00eevise a-o canpion\u00f2u de S\u00e9rie C1.\nPe de ci\u00f9, t\u00f9tte e squ\u00e0ddre inte sta categor\u00eea chi parte\u00e7ipi\u00e0n a-o torn\u00eao da C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia Under 25, co-i abinam\u00e9nti a-i qu\u00e0rti de fin\u00e2le che s\u00f3n stabil\u00eei pe m\u00eazo de 'n sort\u00e9ggio.\nJuniores.\nA-o canpion\u00f2u juniores p\u00eauan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 t\u00f9tti i zugo\u00e9i co-\u00een'et\u00e6 conpr\u00e9iza fra 17 e 18 \u00e0nni, co-a poscibilit\u00e6 pe-e squ\u00e0ddre de inser\u00ee 'n zug\u00f2u ci\u00f9 v\u00eagio, sc\u00ecnn-a-o m\u00e0scimo de 19 \u00e0nni, inta pr\u00f2pio r\u00eauza, ma no into r\u00f2llo de batit\u00f4. Inte sta categor\u00eea gh'\u00e9 'n tot\u00e2le de quat\u00f2rze squ\u00e0ddre, spart\u00eee tra do\u00ee g\u00eeo\u00ecn a car\u00e0tere teritori\u00e2le e \u00f2rganiz\u00e6 seg\u00f3ndo a f\u00f3rmola do g\u00ee\u00f3n a l'itali\u00e0nn-a, con part\u00eee d'and\u00e2ta e de rit\u00f3rno. E pr\u00ecmme qu\u00e0ttro clascifich\u00e6 inti do\u00ee g\u00eeo\u00ecn v\u00eagnan d\u00f3nca ripart\u00eee tra o cosc\u00ec d\u00eeto G\u00ee\u00f3n Bleu e o G\u00ee\u00f3n R\u00f3sso. E pr\u00ecmme d\u00f4e clascifich\u00e6 de ciasched\u00f9n de qu\u00e9sti g\u00eeo\u00ecn intri\u00e0n into tabel\u00f3n, part\u00ecndo da-i qu\u00e0rti de fin\u00e2le, pe l'asegna\u00e7i\u00f3n do scud\u00e9tto juniores de F\u00e0scia A.\nPe c\u00f3ntra, e squ\u00e0ddre che no ariescian a super\u00e2 a seg\u00f3nda f\u00e2ze \u00ecntran inta cosc\u00ec d\u00eeta \"F\u00e0scia B\", d\u00f3nde s\u00f3n div\u00eeze inti g\u00eeo\u00ecn ci\u00e0m\u00e6 G\u00ee\u00f3n V\u00e8rde e G\u00ee\u00f3n Gi\u00e0nco. Scimilm\u00e9nte a-a f\u00e0scia A, e pr\u00ecmme d\u00f4e squ\u00e0ddre de \u00f2gni g\u00ee\u00f3n \u00ecntran into tabel\u00f3n pe l'asegna\u00e7i\u00f3n do scud\u00e9tto juniores de F\u00e0scia B.\nPe de ci\u00f9, e pr\u00ecmme d\u00f4e squ\u00e0ddre inte ciasched\u00f9n di g\u00eeo\u00ecn da pr\u00ecmma f\u00e2ze parte\u00e7ipi\u00e0n a-o torn\u00eao da C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia juniores.\nAli\u00eavi.\nA-o canpion\u00f2u di ali\u00eavi p\u00eauan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 i zugo\u00e9i de 'n'et\u00e6 conpr\u00e9iza tra 15 e 16 \u00e0nni, co-a poscibilit\u00e6 pe-e squ\u00e0ddre de inser\u00ee 'n zug\u00f2u ci\u00f9 v\u00eagio, sc\u00ecnn-a-o m\u00e0scimo de 17 \u00e0nni, inta r\u00eauza da squ\u00e0ddra, ma no into r\u00f2llo de batit\u00f4. E squ\u00e0ddre inte sta categor\u00eea chi s\u00f3n vintis\u00eai, spart\u00eee tra tr\u00e9i g\u00eeo\u00ecn a car\u00e0tere teritori\u00e2le e \u00f2rganiz\u00e6 seg\u00f3ndo a f\u00f3rmola do g\u00ee\u00f3n a l'itali\u00e0nn-a, con part\u00eee d'and\u00e2ta e de rit\u00f3rno. E pr\u00ecmme d\u00f4e clascifich\u00e6 de ciasched\u00f9n g\u00ee\u00f3n, \u00f3ltre che e d\u00f4e t\u00e8rse squ\u00e0ddre inte 'na m\u00eagio poxi\u00e7i\u00f3n tra t\u00f9tti i g\u00eeo\u00ecn da pr\u00ecmma f\u00e2ze, \u00ecntran into tabel\u00f3n da F\u00e0scia A, ch'o l'incom\u00e9nsa da-e part\u00eee di qu\u00e0rti de fin\u00e2le.\nA man\u00eaa pe determin\u00e2 e d\u00f4e t\u00e8rse da \u00e7\u00e8rne a p\u00ecggia in conscidera\u00e7i\u00f3n a m\u00e9dia di p\u00f3nti \u00f2tegn\u00fba da \u00f2gni t\u00e8rsa clasific\u00e2 inti v\u00e0rri g\u00eeo\u00ecn, calcol\u00e2 d\u00f3nca seg\u00f3ndo o rap\u00f2rto tra o n\u00f9mero de part\u00eee disput\u00e6 e o n\u00f9mero de p\u00f3nti go\u00e2gn\u00e6 da qu\u00e9lla squ\u00e0ddra. Into c\u00e2xo de parit\u00e6 da m\u00e9dia di p\u00f3nti, e d\u00f4e squ\u00e0ddre d\u00eavan zug\u00e2 'n spar\u00e9ggio inte 'n c\u00e0npo ne\u00f3tro. In sci\u00e2 f\u00ecn, a squ\u00e0ddra vinc\u00e9nte de sto tabel\u00f3n chi a go\u00e2gna o scud\u00e9tto ali\u00eavi de F\u00e0scia A.\nPe c\u00f3ntra, a squ\u00e0ddra inta ci\u00f9 p\u00eazo poxi\u00e7i\u00f3n tra e t\u00e8rse clasifich\u00e6, e qu\u00e0rte e-e qu\u00ecnte clasifich\u00e6 di tr\u00e9i g\u00eeo\u00ecn e a m\u00eagio s\u00e8sta inta pr\u00ecmma f\u00e2ze intri\u00e0n a-i qu\u00e0rti de fin\u00e2le de F\u00e0scia B. Pe determin\u00e2, a parit\u00e6 de poxi\u00e7i\u00f3n, e squ\u00e0ddre da \u00e7\u00e8rne, se cont\u00ecnoa a calcol\u00e2 a m\u00e9dia di p\u00f3nti conqu\u00ecst\u00e6 e, into c\u00e2xo de parit\u00e6 de m\u00e9dia p\u00f3nti asc\u00ec, o l'\u00e9 da zug\u00e2 'n spar\u00e9ggio inte 'n c\u00e0npo ne\u00f3tro. A squ\u00e0ddra vincitr\u00eexe de sto tabel\u00f3n chi a go\u00e2gna o scud\u00e9tto ali\u00eavi de F\u00e0scia B.\nE tr\u00e6 squ\u00e0ddre a-o pr\u00ecmmo p\u00f3sto inti g\u00eeo\u00ecn da pr\u00ecmma f\u00e2ze, ci\u00f9 a seg\u00f3nda clasific\u00e2 co-a m\u00e9dia p\u00f3nti ci\u00f9 \u00e8rta, zughi\u00e0n asc\u00ec into torn\u00eao pi-\u00e2 C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia ali\u00eavi.\nDebut\u00e0nti.\nA-o canpion\u00f2u di debut\u00e0nti p\u00eauan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 t\u00f9tti i atl\u00eati de 'n'et\u00e6 conpr\u00e9iza tra 13 e 14 \u00e0nni, co-a poscibilit\u00e6 pe-e squ\u00e0ddre de inser\u00ee inta pr\u00f2pia r\u00eauza 'n zug\u00f2u ci\u00f9 gr\u00e0nde, sc\u00ecnn-a-o m\u00e0scimo de 15 \u00e0nni, ma no into r\u00f2llo de batit\u00f4. E squ\u00e0ddre inte sta categor\u00eea chi s\u00f3n vintin\u00eauve, spart\u00eee tra qu\u00e0ttro g\u00eeo\u00ecn a car\u00e0tere teritori\u00e2le e \u00f2rganiz\u00e6 seg\u00f3ndo a f\u00f3rmola do g\u00ee\u00f3n a l'itali\u00e0nn-a, con part\u00eee d'and\u00e2ta e de rit\u00f3rno. E squ\u00e0ddre inte pr\u00ecmme qu\u00e0ttro poxi\u00e7io\u00ecn de \u00f2gni g\u00ee\u00f3n sai\u00e0n inser\u00eee inta tabel\u00f3n fin\u00e2le de F\u00e0scia A, pe c\u00f3ntra t\u00f9tte e \u00e2tre v\u00e0n into tabel\u00f3n de F\u00e0scia B. T\u00f9tti do\u00ee i tabelo\u00ecn p\u00f3rtan a l'asegna\u00e7i\u00f3n de 'n scud\u00e9tto, rispetivam\u00e9nte de F\u00e0scia A \u00f2p\u00fb de F\u00e0scia B.\nE pr\u00ecmme qu\u00e0ttro clasifich\u00e6 de \u00f2gni g\u00ee\u00f3n, \u00f3ltre che parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 a-o tabel\u00f3n de f\u00e0scia superi\u00f4, se sfidi\u00e0n pe go\u00e2gna a C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia debut\u00e0nti asc\u00ec.\nPol\u00ecn.\nA-o canpion\u00f2u di pol\u00ecn p\u00eauan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 t\u00f9tti i atl\u00eati de 'n'et\u00e6 conpr\u00e9iza tra 10 e 12 \u00e0nni, s\u00e9nsa a poscibilit\u00e6 pe-e squ\u00e0ddre de inser\u00ee di zugo\u00e9i ci\u00f9 gr\u00e9ndi inte s\u00f2 r\u00eauze. D'ancheu, inte sta categor\u00eea chi ghe z\u00eaugan 21 squ\u00e0ddre, ripart\u00eee in sce tr\u00e9i g\u00eeo\u00ecn a car\u00e0tere teritori\u00e2le, de l\u00f3ngo \u00f2rganiz\u00e6 seg\u00f3ndo a f\u00f3rmola do g\u00ee\u00f3n a l'itali\u00e0nn-a, con part\u00eee d'and\u00e2ta e de rit\u00f3rno. E squ\u00e0ddre inte pr\u00ecmme qu\u00e0ttro poxi\u00e7io\u00ecn de \u00f2gni g\u00ee\u00f3n sai\u00e0n inser\u00eee inta tabel\u00f3n fin\u00e2le de F\u00e0scia A, pe c\u00f3ntra t\u00f9tte e \u00e2tre v\u00e0n into tabel\u00f3n de F\u00e0scia B. T\u00f9tti do\u00ee i tabelo\u00ecn p\u00f3rtan a l'asegna\u00e7i\u00f3n de 'n scud\u00e9tto, rispetivam\u00e9nte de F\u00e0scia A \u00f2p\u00fb de F\u00e0scia B.\nA squ\u00e0ddra m\u00eagio clasific\u00e2 inta pr\u00ecmma f\u00e2ze a go\u00e2gna o dir\u00ectto de parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 a-a fin\u00e2le de C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia pol\u00ecn, co-o seg\u00f3ndo p\u00f3sto ch'o l'\u00e9 \u00f2tegn\u00fbo da-a squ\u00e0ddra, tra e \u00e2tre d\u00f4e pr\u00ecmme clasifich\u00e6, ch'a v\u00ecn\u00e7e o spar\u00e9ggio.\nPromo\u00e7ion\u00e2li.\nA-o canpion\u00f2u promo\u00e7ion\u00e2li p\u00eauan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 t\u00f9tti i atl\u00eati sc\u00ecnn-a 11 \u00e0nni, conp\u00eei inte l'\u00e0nno sol\u00e2re. D'ancheu gh'\u00e9 31 squ\u00e0ddre che z\u00eaugan inte sta categor\u00eea chi, ripart\u00eee in sce \u00e9utto g\u00eeo\u00ecn de tr\u00e9i \u00f2 qu\u00e0ttro squ\u00e0ddre. E squ\u00e0ddre clasifich\u00e6 inta pr\u00ecmma poxi\u00e7i\u00f3n de \u00f2gni g\u00ee\u00f3n intri\u00e0n a-i qu\u00e0rti de fin\u00e2le de F\u00e0scia A, e \u00e2tre v\u00e0n pe c\u00f3ntra inta F\u00e0scia B.\nCanpion\u00e6 de d\u00f2nne.\nSe\u00e7i\u00f3n senior.\nA-o canpion\u00f2u femin\u00ecn de cl\u00e0sse senior p\u00eauan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 e atl\u00eate co-\u00een'et\u00e6 magi\u00f4 de 14 \u00e0nni, conp\u00eei inte l'\u00e0nno sol\u00e2re. A-a m\u00e0scima categor\u00eea de d\u00f2nne ghe fan p\u00e0rte s\u00eai squ\u00e0ddre che v\u00eagnan ripart\u00eee in sce do\u00ee g\u00eeo\u00ecn. A pr\u00ecmma clasific\u00e2 de ciasched\u00f9n g\u00ee\u00f3n a parte\u00e7ipi\u00e2 d\u00f3nca a-a fin\u00e2le de categor\u00eea.\nSe\u00e7i\u00f3n zo\u00eani.\nA-o canpion\u00f2u femin\u00ecn de cl\u00e0sse zo\u00eani p\u00eauan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 e atl\u00eate co-\u00een'et\u00e6 conpr\u00e9iza tra 10 e 13 \u00e0nni, co-e squ\u00e0ddre che no gh'\u00e0n a poscibilit\u00e6 de inser\u00eene de ci\u00f9 gr\u00e9nde inte s\u00f2 r\u00eauze. D'ancheu gh'\u00e9 tr\u00e6 squ\u00e0ddre che z\u00eaugan inte sta categor\u00eea chi, \u00f2rganiz\u00e2 seg\u00f3ndo 'n g\u00ee\u00f3n a l'itali\u00e0nn-a. E squ\u00e0ddre clasifich\u00e6 inte pr\u00ecmme d\u00f4e poxi\u00e7io\u00ecn zughi\u00e0n d\u00f3nca a fin\u00e2le de categor\u00eea."}
{"id": "29999", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29999", "title": "Diocexi de Arbenga e Impeia", "text": "A diocexi de Arbenga e Impeia (in latin: \"Dioecesis Albingaunensis-Imperiae\") l'\u00e8 ina s\u00eade da G\u00eaxa cat\u00f4lica in Italia, dipendente da l'arcidiocexi de Zena, apartenente aa regi\u00f9n eclexiastica Lig\u00fcria. Intu 2020 a l'ha cunt\u00e0u 157.000 batez\u00e0i in sce 176.000 abitanti. L'\u00e8 rez\u00fca dau v\u00e9scu Guglielmo Borghetti.\nTerit\u00f2iu.\nU terit\u00f2iu da diocexi u cumprende a zona du pun\u00e8nte savunese e a parte du levante da pruvinsa de Impeia. A s\u00eade vescuv\u00ecle a l'\u00e8 a sit\u00e0i d'Arbenga, dund'a se tr\u00f6va a catedr\u00e2le de San Mich\u00ea. A Impeia a bax\u00eelica de San Mau(r)issiu a mantegne l'incaregu de cuncatedr\u00e2le diuces\u00e0na. Inta diocexi se tr\u00f6van asc\u00ec due bax\u00ecliche minuri, quella de San Giu\u00e0nni bat\u00ecsta a Ineja e quella de San Nicol\u00f2 aa Pr\u00eca.\nU terit\u00f2iu da diocexi u l'\u00e8 estesu pe ben 979\u00a0km\u00b2 frasiun\u00e0u poi inte 162 par\u00f2cchie, distribu\u00ece fra:\nSt\u00f2ia.\nA tradisiun luc\u00e2le a cunscide(r)a Arbenga a s\u00eade du marti(r)iu de san calocciu, tradisiunalmente fiss\u00e2 fra i \u00e0nni 121 e 125, u santu u l'\u00e9a in \u00fcfisi\u00e2le bresci\u00e0n aa curte de l'impe(r)at\u00fb ruman Adri\u00e0n; i \u00e0tti du s\u00f2 marti(r)iu e nu sun ben ci\u00e0(r)i, asemme a quelli de san Faustin e Giuv\u00ectta, pe questu van anc\u00f9 ve(r)ific\u00e0e du t\u00fcttu.\nNunustante questu, in sciu pre-sup\u00f2stu scitu de sepurt\u00fca du santu a se ri\u00fcn\u00ecva a primma cum\u00fcnit\u00e0i cristi\u00e0na ing\u00e0una, e dai sc\u00e0vi archeulogici u p\u00e0 che u p\u00f2stu (curispundente au sucesc\u00ecvu munast\u00ea de San Calocciu au Munte), l'\u00e9a z\u00e0 st\u00e0u in postu privuegi\u00e0u inte l'epuca imperi\u00e2le pe sepel\u00ec e s\u00e0rme. D\u00fcante u pruc\u00e8ssu de vangelizasiun d'Arbenga, l'axeva av\u00fcu impurtansa asc\u00ec san Calim\u00eau, v\u00e9scu de Milan, at\u00eevu inta secunda met\u00e0i du III seculu; sta c\u00f4sa a leghe(r)\u00e9va a difux\u00f9n du cristian\u00eaximu inta sit\u00e0i e lungu t\u00fctta a Riv\u00eaa de Punente aa diocexi milanese.\nI st\u00fcddi archeul\u00f2gici mustran cumme za dau V seculu in sit\u00e0i se truvava ina ben dif\u00fcza cum\u00fcnit\u00e0i cristiana, f\u00e0ttu testimuni\u00e0u asc\u00ec daa cuntempuranea custrusi\u00f9n da catedr\u00e2le de San Mich\u00ea e du batist\u00eau luc\u00e2le, ma asc\u00ec dae g\u00eaxe simite(r)i\u00e0li f\u00f6a dae m\u00fcagie sitadine, cumme quelle de San Calocciu e de San Vit\u00fbre.\n\u00c2tru eventu fundament\u00e2le pe a st\u00f2ia religiusa ing\u00e0una l'\u00e8 st\u00e2 a presensa de San Martin vescu de Tours, in sce l'\u00ecsua Gain\u00e2a p\u00f4cu doppu a met\u00e0i du IV seculu ch'u p\u00e0 \u00easse a pr\u00f6va da presensa de in polu religiusu z\u00e0 urganis\u00e0u, ben primma da mensciun du v\u00e9scu \"Quintius:\" propiu a questu sentru u santu l'axeva pusci\u00fcu fa riferimentu .\nL'istitusiun da diocexi riz\u00fclta cumunque ci\u00fct\u00f2stu tarda, in quantu fund\u00e2 seg\u00fcamente d\u00f2ppu a m\u00f2rte de Sant'Ambrogiu. U primmu vescu, Quinsiu, du quale l'emmu nutissa s\u00e8rta, remunta au 451, firmat\u00e0(r)iu da lete(r)a du scinudu de Euzebiu, v\u00e9scu de Mil\u00e0n, invi\u00e2 au pappa Leun I; inta curispundensa a se stabuiva a cund\u00e0nna de Nest\u00f2(r)iu e de Eutiche (M\u00e0nsi); t\u00fcttavia fra e istitusiun religiuse de questu genere, a dux\u00e9a esse a primma in urdine de fundasiun, vistu che nu se tr\u00f6va tr\u00e0ccia di v\u00e9scuvi de Vinim\u00eca e de Savuna armenu fin a l'\u00e0nnu 680, annu da partecipasiun de queste due fig\u00fce a \u00fcn di cuncui de quel'epuca .\nU(r)igina(r)iam\u00e8nte ae dipendense de l'arcidiocexi de Milan, u s\u00f2 terit\u00f2iu u l'\u00e9a limit\u00e0u a setentri\u00f9n dau spartiaiva arp\u00ecn, m\u00e8ntre a levante rivava scin a Fin\u00e2 e a Punente cumprendeva a z\u00f2na sanremasca. \nA scuv\u00e8rta de in edifissiu eclexi\u00e0sticu cun funte batexim\u00e2le intu paise da Riva, cun datasiun curispundente au VI seculu mustran in urganisasiun cristi\u00e0na de campagne e testimonian asc\u00ec in urganisasiun du terit\u00f2iu baz\u00e2 in scia c\u00eave luc\u00e2le.\nInti seculi a vegn\u00ec e nutissie insci vescuvi de Arbenga sun frament\u00e0(r)ie, armenu fin a l'\u00e0nnu Mule. \u00c2tri scavi archeulogici l'han purtau turna aa l\u00fcxe u numme de 'n v\u00e9scu cuntempuraneu a l'et\u00e0i de Quinsiu, stu l\u00ec u se(r)\u00e9va Benedettu. \nAu cunciliu pruvins\u00e2le de Milan du 679, ch'u s'\u00e9a espressu cuntru i ide\u00e2li du munutelismu, l'axeva pi\u00e0u parte asc\u00ec u v\u00e9scu arbenganese: \"Bono\"; pa(r)eggia a partecipasiun au scinudu rum\u00e0n in prepa(r)asiunau seguente cuncuiu ec\u00fcmenicu du 680-681. \u00c2tri dui v\u00e9scuvi, I\u00fcnsiu e Martirian, culuc\u00e0i stu(r)icamente fra a met\u00e0i del VI e a met\u00e0i de l'VIII seculu, sun reciam\u00e0i inti \"Acta Sancti Martiriani episcopi et martiris\". \nDe l'epuca presedente a quella carulingia gh'\u00e8 Dexide(r)iu, che u l'ha cunsacr\u00e0u a g\u00eaxa de l'abas\u00eca de San P\u00ea, inta val\u00e2 du Va(r)atella. Egid\u00fcrfu l'axeva pi\u00e0u parte inv\u00eace au cunciliu milanese a livellu pruvinsale de l'864, cun 'na funsiun de sarvaguardia de l'urdinamentu eclexiasticu e du cuntrollu de l'upe(r)\u00e0u du v\u00e9scu inta gi\u00fc(r)isdisiun diucesana. \nS\u00e8ra u IX seculu u v\u00e9scu Benedettu Revelli, a l'imprensippiu ab\u00e2te du munast\u00eau de l'\u00ccsua epoi elez\u00fcu vescu arbenganese, vene(r)\u00e0u intu Mediuevu e canunis\u00e0u poi intu XVII seculu. \nArbenga, asemme ae sit\u00e0i de Vadu e de Vintim\u00eca, aturnu a l'825, vegne cunscide(r)\u00e2, dandu am\u00e8ntu au capitul\u00e0re de Lut\u00e0(r)iu I, cumme \u00fcna de m\u00eate pe i zueni ch'i v\u00f6nen st\u00fcdi\u00e0, m\u00e8ntre i chierici duxevan and\u00e0 a st\u00fcdi\u00e0 a Turin\nIna presensa de fundamentale impurtansa a l'\u00e9a quella di munast\u00e9(r)i benedet\u00ecn ch'i cuntribu\u00ecvan au rafursamentu religiusu da diocexi. Fra sti chi, particularmente, se distingu\u00e9va quellu de l'\u00ccsua, gi\u00fcstu de frunte aa sit\u00e0i, che intu 1044, grassie a ina particul\u00e2re cuncesci\u00f9n du Pappa Benedettu IX, l'\u00e9a st\u00e0u ezent\u00e0u da l'aministrasi\u00f9n vescuv\u00ecle.\nGrassie a questa particularit\u00e0i u munast\u00ea u l'\u00e9a sciurt\u00ecu a utegn\u00ec diverse prupiet\u00e0i nu sulu in It\u00e0lia, ma asc\u00ec in Catal\u00f2gna, in Pruvensa e in Corsega. Inte l'annu 1064 a c\u00fc(r)ia ing\u00e0una l'\u00e9a anc\u00f9 sutta ae dipendense lumb\u00e0rde, difatti l'\u00e9a in vigure u pagamentu de t\u00e0sce d'in annu in annu.\nU prel\u00e0u diuces\u00e0n Erembertu ax\u00e9va poi partesip\u00e0u au scinudu de Pav\u00eca, ch'u s'\u00e9a svoltu u 25 d'utubre 1046, u sulu fra t\u00fctti i vescuvi lig\u00fc(r)i, incuntrandu u suvr\u00e0n Enr\u00eecu III u Negru, ch'u rapresentava ina reuni\u00f9n de curte aa f\u00ecn de stabu\u00ec a so ca(r)\u00e2 versu Rumma, a testimuni\u00e2 u legamme fra u terit\u00f2iu arbenganese e u Regnu d'Italia.\nSe cumprende inv\u00eace, grassie aa c\u00f2ppi de 'n ducumentu du 29 de z\u00fcgnu du 1076, a cuncesci\u00f9n a l'abas\u00eca de san P\u00ea de Tui(r)\u00e0n de 'n mu(r)\u00ecn intu pa\u00ecse, firm\u00e0u cun u cunsensu de ben 22 can\u00f2nici da cattedr\u00e2le elenc\u00e0i in urdine de dignit\u00e0i e de duzze \"muites Sancti Ioanis\", ( primmu de l'elencu \"Conradus\", avuc\u00e0u de l'episc\u00f2piu).\nU ducumentu u ne mustra ducca cumme a c\u00fc(r)ia a l'\u00e9a gest\u00eca da in alunga s\u00e9(r)ie de can\u00f2nici ch'i fiancavan u v\u00e8scu (a l'epuca Deud\u00e0u), asemme a 'na client\u00eala arm\u00e2, con inc\u00e0reghi ben defin\u00eci e ch'a fa imagin\u00e2 in patrim\u00f4niu vastu, tantu da pa\u00ea puntu de riferimentu asc\u00ec a livellu puliticu.\nDu 1127 u munast\u00ea de San Lu\u00e9nsu a Va(r)ig\u00f2tti vegne cucessu da parte de Bunifassiu du Vastu au vescu ing\u00e0unu, intu stessu periudu sun str\u00e9tti i rap\u00f2rti cu-a sit\u00e0i de Ler\u00ecn. A furt\u00fcna de l'abasia a Tui(r)\u00e0n a munta, grassie p\u00fce a l'asiun du v\u00e9scu Ut\u00f9n, intu 1149, che paralelam\u00e8nte sette \u00e0nni primma l'ax\u00e9va cunferm\u00e0u u cuntr\u00f2llu da parte da g\u00eaxa de San Steva de Zena e g\u00eaxe de San Steva a Sanremmu e de Vuar\u00eagia.\nInte sta fase a prusegue l'uranisasiun cu-e c\u00eavi luc\u00e2li , inta f\u00e0scia cumpr\u00e9sa fra a val\u00e2 de dl'Ar\u00f2scia e u finalese, e (in scia c\u00f2sta) fin au P\u00f2rtu. Au de f\u00f6a de questa sudivixun gh'\u00e9a u gurfu de Di\u00e0n, anc\u00f9 sutta a l'abas\u00eca de San P\u00ea.\nIntu 1169, inv\u00eace, u munast\u00ea da Gain\u00e2a vegne culuc\u00e0u sutta u direttu cuntrollu de l'arcivescuv\u00e0u de Zena; aa fin du 1473, in cuntempuranea aa perdita de prupiet\u00e0i prestigiuse vegne cuncessu in cum\u00eanda. Cu-u 1179 e a paxe in Lateran fra l'Impe(r)u e a Lega di cum\u00fci itali\u00e0ni, l'\u00e9a presente u v\u00e9scu Lanteriu, ch'u rapresent\u00e0va a Marca d'Arbenga. L'annu 1159 pappa Lisciandru III l'axeva asegn\u00e0u a diocexi aa pruvinsa eclexi\u00e0stica de l'arcidiocexi de Zena, ma u pruvedimentu, u nu tr\u00f6va imedi\u00e0u riscuntru, tantu che anc\u00f9a intu 1213 pappa Inucensu III ribad\u00ecsce au v\u00e9scu Enr\u00eecu a sutumisci\u00f9n duv\u00fca a l'auturit\u00e0i diucesana zenesi.\nL'\u00e9a propiu a part\u00ec da-u XIII seculu ch'i s'\u00e8an fai ci\u00fc streiti i rap\u00f4rti cun Zena. F\u00e0ttu ch'u mustra l'avixinamentu de due realt\u00e0i l'\u00e8 u lungu episcop\u00e0u de Lanfrancu de Negru (1255-1288), zenese: vellu u v\u00e0 a elimin\u00e0 serti ben da mensa vescuv\u00ecle a fav\u00fbre de fam\u00ece zenesi, i quali membri vegnivan cusc\u00ec inse(r)\u00eci ad aministr\u00e0 u capitulu da catedr\u00e2le; Au s\u00f2 mand\u00e0u se fan asc\u00ec remunt\u00e0 i primmi urdini mendic\u00e0nti diuces\u00e0i.\nD\u00fcante u 1292 u seggiu vescuv\u00ecle u rez\u00fcltava v\u00f6iu, fin a quande nu munta u sevasch\u00ecn Nicol\u00f2 Guascun (o Vascun di Marchesi de S\u00e9va) da pappa Niccol\u00f2 IV u 29 de zen\u00e0. Vell'u se(r)\u00e0 u priummu de ina s\u00e9(r)ie de sevasch\u00ecn a ucup\u00e0 a cattedra diucesana inta primma met\u00e0i du XIV seculu.\nFede\u00eegu de S\u00e9va, f\u00ecu de Benedettu di Marchesi de Seva, scign\u00fb de Muntezemu(r)u, u l'\u00e9a st\u00e0u elez\u00fcu u 4 dixembre du 1330 a l'et\u00e0i de numma 22 \u00e0nni, pe a quale u l'utegne ina dispensa da parte du pappa Gi\u00f9anni XXII pe a s\u00f2a cunuscensa pe i me(r)iti z\u00e0 utegn\u00fci.\nU 7 d'arv\u00ec du 1334 vegne urdin\u00e0u u scinudu diuces\u00e0n, ai quali a segue a p\u00fcbbricasi\u00f9n di \u00e0tti ai seguenti 2 de m\u00e0zzu. Asc\u00ec pe sta c\u00f4sa chi u pappa Benedettu XII cu'ina l\u00e9tera du 27 mazzu 1336 u inc\u00e0rrega de infurm\u00e2se e de furn\u00ec 'na scistemasi\u00f9n ai prublemi nasci\u00fci fra u marchese du Carettu de Savuna e u v\u00e9scu de N\u00f4li, Teud\u00f4xiu.\nAi 31 de l\u00fciu du 1337 u l'ax\u00e9va apruv\u00e0u i stat\u00fci capitul\u00e0(r)i di canonici da s\u00f2 catedr\u00e2le. U m\u00f6(r)e 1349 e u 18 de frev\u00e2 du m\u00e8ximu \u00e0nnu u p\u00eca u tr\u00f4nu u prubabue n\u00e9vu Giuanni di marchesi de S\u00e9va, cunscign\u00fb de Pri\u00e9ru e S\u00e2le. Dau 1380 au 1419 u v\u00e9scu in c\u00e0rega l'\u00e8 st\u00e0u Girbertu Fieschi, ch'u l'aminist\u00e0va a diocexi grassie a 'na s\u00e9(r)ie de vic\u00e0ri, mustrandu ina scarsa presensa.\nDoppu se vegghe Ant\u00f4gnu Da Punte, prel\u00e0u atentu a l'ambitu artisticu, ch'u porta aa fin i travaji pe u n\u00f6vu c\u00f4(r)u da catedr\u00e2le asc\u00ec grassie aa puscibuit\u00e0i d\u00e2 dau p\u00e0ppa Martin Vpe pu\u00ea vende e indurgense d\u00fc(r)\u00e0nte a festivit\u00e0i \"conluant ad eandem ecclesiam et ad eius conservationem seu fabricam manus prompte porrigant adiutrices\". Intu 1427 u r\u00f2llu vegne ricuv\u00e8rtu da Mat\u00eau du Carettu, che partecipandu au Cuncuiu de Baxu\u00eaa u cuntrasta furtemente a linea de Rumma, pe poi turn\u00e2 in der\u00ea a paxific\u00e2se primma ch'u fusse tr\u00f2ppu tardi.\nFra i seculi XV e XVI se fa stradda a fig\u00fca de Leunardu Marchese (1476-1513), ricurd\u00e0u pe a c\u00fca du terit\u00f2iu diuces\u00e0n, a riurganisasi\u00f9n di ben pused\u00fci e a fundasiun de n\u00f6ve par\u00f2cchie. Carlu Siga(r)a (1554-1572), doppu av\u00ea pi\u00e0u parte au Cuncuilu de Trentu, rez\u00fclta \u00easse \u00fcn di pr\u00ecmmi a aplic\u00e2 efetivamente e n\u00f6ve nurmat\u00ecve. L'8 de m\u00e0zzu du 1564 u fa cunvuc\u00e0 u primmu scinudu diuces\u00e0n.\nAi 21 d'arv\u00ec du1569 istitu\u00ecsce u semin\u00e0(r)iu vescuv\u00ecle intu ci\u00f2stru da catedr\u00e2le, ch'u l'ha utegn\u00fcu in n\u00f6vu edifissiu primma intu 1622 e poi 1929, qund'u s'\u00e8 spust\u00e0u inta s\u00eade de anc\u00f6i. U n\u00fcme(r)u de scinudi va multiplicanduse cu-i vescuvi ch\u00eci vegnen: fra t\u00fctti Luca Fieschi n'ax\u00e9va cunvuc\u00e0u trei, m\u00e8ntre Vincensu Landiintuli e Pier Fransescu Costa dui pe \u00fcn.\nA st'\u00fcrtimu se d\u00eave asc\u00ec a redasi\u00f9n, atu\u00e2 dau can\u00f4nicu Gio Ant\u00f4gnu Pani\u00eari, da munument\u00e2le \u00f2pe(r)a, rest\u00e2 scr\u00ecta a m\u00e0n e cunserv\u00e2 inti archivi diuces\u00e0i, cu-u titulu \"Sacro, e vago Giardiintulo\", fundament\u00e2le pe a cunuscensa du st\u00e0ttu da diocexi d'Arbenga inta primma met\u00e0i du XVII seculu.\nAa fin du XVI seculu u se reg\u00f2rda u vescuv\u00e0u de Luca Fieschi, membru de 'na ricca fam\u00eca zenese, ch'u mette(r)\u00e0 a dispusisiun ina gr\u00f2ssa parte du so patrim\u00f4niu intu rifasimentu da catedr\u00e2le arbenganese, adat\u00e2 cusc\u00ec ai canuni fiss\u00e0i dau Cuncuiu trent\u00ecn.\nSciben st'impurtante \u00f2pe(r)a de restr\u00fctt\u00fc(r)asi\u00f9n, u nu l'ha av\u00fcu vitta fasue, tantu che a v\u00eexita aa fin du seculu, cumpi\u00fcu dau munscign\u00fb Masc\u00e0rdi, se(r)\u00e9va st\u00e2 vusci\u00fca dau pap\u00e0u pe meju cuntrul\u00e2 u mand\u00e0u du v\u00e9scu, lud\u00e0u cumunque pe u so upe(r)\u00e0u inta magiuransa de g\u00eaxe sutta aa diocexi. U marcuntentu di \u00e2tri eclexiastici e de serti sitad\u00ecn uustri se(r)\u00e9va st\u00e0u racoltu e messu in evidensa cun in ducumentu (nu 'riv\u00e0u aa giurn\u00e2 d'anc\u00f6i) du 1600: i \"mugugni\" i vegnivan survat\u00fcttu dai ci\u00fc cunservat\u00f9i, ch'i cuntestavan e \u00f2pe(r) da vellu f\u00e0e e dumandavan asc\u00ec a v\u00eexita in diocexi de 'n cumis\u00e2iu e a cunvucasiun a Rumma du prel\u00e0u pe r\u00eande c\u00f9ntu da s\u00f2 aministrasiun.\nIn \u00e2tru pap\u00ea, invi\u00e0u dau cum\u00fcn aa Santa S\u00eade, dumanda a presensa du vescu in sit\u00e0i d\u00fc(r)ante u periudu de Qua(r)\u00e9xima de l'\u00e0nnu du Giubu\u00eau, in m\u00f2ddu ch'i possen fin\u00ec asc\u00ec i travaji entru a fin de l'\u00e0nnu santu. U Fieschi u m\u00f6(r)e in Arbenga intu 1610, sepurtu inta cap\u00e9lla de San Ric\u00e0rdu, dund'u s\u00f2 suces\u00fb P\u00ea Fransescu C\u00f2sta u fa(r)\u00e0 custru\u00eci in b\u00fcstu e mete(r)\u00e0 ina t\u00e0rga a mem\u00f4ia du v\u00e9scu, poi spust\u00e2 inta sacrest\u00eca.\nD\u00f2ppu san Benedettu, v\u00e9scu du IX seculu, intu Setesentu a diocexi l'ha purt\u00e0u aa G\u00eaxa cat\u00f4lica in \u00e2tru s\u00e0ntu, Leunardu dau P\u00f2rtu, fr\u00e0tte di Min\u00fbi rifurm\u00e0i, predicat\u00fb de rui\u00eavu in t\u00fctta It\u00e0lia, ma survat\u00fcttu a Rumma, dunde u l'\u00e8 ina fig\u00fca sentr\u00e2le du grande giubu\u00eau de l'\u00e0nnu 1750, ricurd\u00e0u asc\u00ec cumme prumut\u00fb da pr\u00e0tica da Via Cr\u00fbci, che pe primmu pr\u00eadica au Culuss\u00eau, propiu d\u00fc(r)\u00e0nte l'Annu S\u00e0ntu inandi\u00e0u da pappa Benedettu XIV.\nInta primma parte de l'Utusentu a diocexi a vegghe in ridimensciunamentu da s\u00f2 sf\u00e9(r)a de influ\u00e8nsa teritui\u00e2le. Vegnen difatti sed\u00fce fra u 1803 e u 1804 quattru par\u00f2cchie de l'entrut\u00e8ra arbenganese, in sciu crin\u00e2le arp\u00ecn: sun quella de Ci(r)ix\u00f6a (frasiun de Gar\u00e9sce) inta val\u00e2 du N\u00e9va e quelle de Autu, Crava\u00fcna e naxin, inta val\u00e2 du Pennavaire.\nT\u00fctte queste e passan sutta aa diocexi de Munduv\u00ec. De suguitu, intu 1831, \u00e2tre vintisinque parocchie da parte ci\u00fc a punente vegnen pas\u00e0e aa diocexi de Vintim\u00eca, fra ste chi: Sanremmu, T\u00e0ggia, B\u00e2\u00fcccu, Munt\u00e2utu Carp\u00e0xe, Tri\u00f6a, Bajardu, Se(r)i\u00e0na, A C\u00f2lla de Sanremmu, Castel\u00e0(r)u, Ters\u00f4iu, Pomp\u00eai\u00e0na, A Riva, San St\u00eava au M\u00e2, Cipr\u00e8ssa, Lenguejetta, A C\u00f2sta, San Luensu au M\u00e2, Priabr\u00fcna (numma e frasiui de B\u00f2scum\u00e2 e da T\u00fbre), I Mu(r)in de Tri\u00f6a e Uspedaletti.\nFra i v\u00e9scuvi ch'i fig\u00fc(r)an intu XIX seculu, gh'\u00e8 st\u00e0u Raffaele Biale (1840-1870) ch'u l'ax\u00e9va favu(r)\u00ecu i st\u00fcddi teulogici du cl\u00earu e l'in\u00ecu de 'na misci\u00f9n de sacerd\u00f2tti diuces\u00e0i. \nZ\u00e0 intu 1816 in sacer\u00f2tte de Tri\u00f6a, Giu\u00e0nni dai Mu(r)\u00ecn, l'\u00e9a m\u00f2rtu mart\u00ec(r)e in C\u00eena. mor\u00ec martire in Cina. I primmi dui patri\u00e0rchi da restaur\u00e2 s\u00eade da Geruxal\u00e8mme di lat\u00ecn l'\u00e9an u(r)igin\u00e0i da diocexi: Gi\u00fcseppe Valerga de L\u00f6a e Vincenso Br\u00e0cco da Tur\u00e0ssa.\nSempre intu m\u00e8ximu periudu gh'\u00e8 st\u00e2 a n\u00e0scita de arc\u00fcne ciungregasiun religiuse femin\u00ecli: intu 1836 Te(r)esa Munardu l'ax\u00e9va fund\u00e0u a L\u00f6a e muneghe da Vixitasi\u00f9n, anc\u00f9 a L\u00f6a, intu 1885, Ma(r)ia Fransesca de Ges\u00f9 R\u00fcb\u00e0ttu l'ax\u00e9va fund\u00e0u e Tersi\u00e0rie Capuc\u00eene. Anc\u00f9 du 1848 Ma(r)\u00eca Leunarda Ran\u00ecxe l'ha istitu\u00ecu e Cla(r)\u00ecsse da Sant\u00ecscima Nunsi\u00e2.\nIntu N\u00f6vesentu, pe diversci \u00e0nni u v\u00e9scu d'Arbenga l'\u00e8 st\u00e0u Ange(r)u Cambi\u00e2xu, ch'u v\u00ecve i \u00e0nni d\u00fc(r)\u00ecscimi de due gu\u00e8re, intervenendu asc\u00ec persunalmente inti cunfrunti du cumandu tedescu, fin au 1945. In particul\u00e2re ufrenduse intu 1942, u 29 de setembre, cumme ust\u00e0ggiu au p\u00f2stu de ci\u00fc de sentusinquanta pixun\u00e9(r)i siv\u00ecli.\nL'8 de l\u00fciu du 1949, cu-a let\u00e9(r)a apust\u00f4lica \"Qua Augustus Imperator\", u pappa Piu XII u l'ha pruclam\u00e0u a Be\u00e2ta Ma(r)\u00eca V\u00e8rgine, cunusci\u00fca cu-u titulu de \"Mad\u00f2nna de Puntelungu\", prutetrixe prinsip\u00e2le da sit\u00e0i d'Arbenga e da diocexi. Ai 2 de frev\u00e2 du 1965 a diocexi asci\u00f2rbe intu s\u00f2 terit\u00f2iu a par\u00f2cchia de Naxin, ch'a l'\u00e9a apartegn\u00fca aa diocexi de Munduv\u00ec dau 1804. Vista l'impurtansa da sit\u00e0i de Impeia, u numme da diocexi u l'\u00e8 st\u00e0u cangi\u00e0u in diocexi de Arbenga-Impeia a part\u00ec dau 1\u00ba de dixembre du 1973, m\u00e8ntre a bax\u00eclica de San Mau(r)\u00ecssiu au Portu, l'\u00e8 st\u00e0 elev\u00e2 a cuncatedr\u00e2le da diocexi.\nVescuvi.\nSun chi de sutta inse(r)\u00eci i vescuvi da diocei scin daa so fundasiun, umetendu i periudi de s\u00eade vac\u00e0nte ch'i nu s\u00fcpe(r)an i dui anni o nu sun acert\u00e0i.\nStatistighe.\nA diocexi a cuntava intu 2020 157.000 battezzati in sce na pupulasi\u00f9n de 176.000 persune,ch'i curispunde a l'89,2% du tut\u00e2le."}
{"id": "30000", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30000", "title": "S\u00e9rie A (bal\u00f3n)", "text": "A S\u00e9rie A a l'\u00e9 a m\u00e0scima categor\u00eea e ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte conpeti\u00e7i\u00f3n itali\u00e0nn-a de bal\u00f3n, \u00f2rganiz\u00e2 a part\u00ee da-o 1912 e d'ancheu ariv\u00e2 a-a s\u00f2 \u00e7ent\u00eaxima edi\u00e7i\u00f3n. \nFon\u00e7ionam\u00e9nto.\nA S\u00e9rie A a l'\u00e9 o ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte torn\u00eao do canpion\u00f2u na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de bal\u00f3n, es\u00e9ndo a m\u00e0scima categor\u00eea de sto sp\u00f2rt chi, e d'ancheu ghe ne fan p\u00e0rte d\u00eaxe squ\u00e0ddre in tot\u00e2le che v\u00eagnan s\u00e9gge da-a Lig\u00f9ria che da-o Piem\u00f3nte. A S\u00e9rie A a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta \u00f2rganiz\u00e2 in sce tr\u00e6 f\u00e2ze difer\u00e9nti, seg\u00f3ndo a cosc\u00ec d\u00eeta \"f\u00f3rmola Bresci\u00e0n\".\nA pr\u00ecmma p\u00e0rte do canpion\u00f2u, de l\u00f3ngo qu\u00e9lla ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte, a l'\u00e9 a \"\"regular season\". Inte sta f\u00e2ze chi gh'\u00e9 i sc\u00f3ntri dir\u00e9tti tra t\u00f9tte e squ\u00e0ddre do canpion\u00f2u, into form\u00e2to conosci\u00fbo c\u00f3mme g\u00ee\u00f3n a l'itali\u00e0nn-a, pe 'n tot\u00e2le de 18 giorn\u00e6, incl\u00fbze s\u00e9gge e part\u00eee d'and\u00e2ta che qu\u00e9lle de rit\u00f3rno. In sci\u00e2 b\u00e2ze di rizult\u00e2ti de sta f\u00e2ze chi, sai\u00e0n decret\u00e6 i n\u00f3mmi de s\u00eai squ\u00e0ddre che parte\u00e7ipi\u00e0n a-i \"play-off\" e de qu\u00e0ttro che sai\u00e0n pe c\u00f3ntra costr\u00e9ite a zug\u00e2 i \"play-out\".\nS\u00e9gge i \"play-off\" che i \"play-out\" s\u00f3n disput\u00e6 l\u00ea asc\u00ec con di g\u00eeo\u00ecn a l'itali\u00e0nn-a, rispetivam\u00e9nte de s\u00eai e de qu\u00e0ttro squ\u00e0ddre, co-e pr\u00ecmme tr\u00e6 squ\u00e0ddre a-i \"play-off\" ch'ani\u00e0n de dir\u00ectto a-e semifin\u00e2le p\u00f2-u scud\u00e9tto; pe c\u00f3ntra e \u00f9rtime tr\u00e6 e a pr\u00ecmma di \"play-out\" zughi\u00e0n 'n spar\u00e9ggio pe l'\u00f9rtimo p\u00f3sto dispon\u00ecbile. L'\u00f9rtima squ\u00e0ddra inti \"play-out\" a l'\u00e9 pe c\u00f3ntra qu\u00e9lla a \u00ease retroc\u00e8ssa inta S\u00e9rie B.\nO canpion\u00f2u de S\u00e9rie A o se concl\u00f9dde co-e part\u00eee de semifin\u00e2le e da fin\u00e2le do scud\u00e9tto, co-e qu\u00e0ttro squ\u00e0ddre qualifich\u00e6 a l'\u00f9rtima f\u00e2ze che zughi\u00e0n di d\u00f3ggi inc\u00f3ntri (con and\u00e2ta e rit\u00f3rno) ci\u00f9 'na part\u00eea de spar\u00e9ggio, se neces\u00e2ia.\nPe de ci\u00f9, e d\u00f4e squ\u00e0ddre inte 'na poxi\u00e7i\u00f3n ci\u00f9 \u00e2ta inti g\u00eeo\u00ecn de and\u00e2ta e inte qu\u00e9lli de rit\u00f3rno go\u00e2gnan a pr\u00f2pia parte\u00e7ipa\u00e7i\u00f3n a-a C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia da m\u00e0scima s\u00e9rie.\nSt\u00f6ia.\nScib\u00e9n che i pr\u00ecmmi torn\u00eai de bal\u00f3n rem\u00f3ntan a-a f\u00ecn do s\u00e9colo XIX, a l'\u00e9poca de zugo\u00e9i lezend\u00e2i c\u00f3mme o Giuseppe Filippa \"Ghindo\"\" de Cravans\u00e0nn-a, o pr\u00ecmmo canpion\u00f2u regol\u00e2re de sta discipl\u00ecnn-a chi o s'\u00e9 dispot\u00f2u s\u00f4lo into 1912. Tra i atl\u00eati ci\u00f9 avox\u00e6 de qu\u00e9lli \u00e0nni, se p\u00eauan aregord\u00e2 o Riccardo Fuseri, canpi\u00f3n pe qu\u00e0ttro \u00e0nni de f\u00eea, o Pierino Bonsignore e o Maggiorino Bistolfi, con do\u00ee scud\u00e9tti ciasched\u00f9n, e o Raffaele Ricca, ch'o l'\u00e0 go\u00e2gn\u00f2u qu\u00e0ttro canpion\u00e6. Into c\u00f3rso de 'n part\u00eea a \u00c0sti into 1920, o sanrem\u00e0sco Milin Panizzi o l'\u00e0 ti\u00f2u 'n bal\u00f3n de 180\u00a0gr\u00e0mmi a 'na dist\u00e0nsa de 87,5\u00a0m\u00eatri, stabil\u00ecndo un di ci\u00f9 ant\u00eeghi rec\u00f2rd da discipl\u00ecnn-a. Inte sto per\u00eeodo chi o canpion\u00f2u de bal\u00f3n o l'\u00eaa as\u00e6 conosci\u00fbo o l'\u00e0iva b\u00e9n b\u00e9n de tif\u00f4xi, rivalez\u00e0ndo co-o n\u00eauvo z\u00eaugo do bal\u00f3n. Pe de ci\u00f9, se peu aregord\u00e2 c\u00f3mme o Vittorio Pozzo, comis\u00e2io t\u00e9cnico da na\u00e7ion\u00e2le itali\u00e0nn-a de bal\u00f3n ch'a l'\u00e0 go\u00e2gn\u00f2u do\u00ee mondi\u00e2li, o Carlo Parola, o Renato Cesarini e t\u00e0nti \u00e2tri zugo\u00e9i da bal\u00f3n, av\u00e9ssan zug\u00f2u a qu\u00e9sta discipl\u00ecnn-a asc\u00ec.\nInti \u00e0nni tr\u00e9nta o bal\u00f3n o p\u00e0ssa sott'a l'\u00f2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n sport\u00eeva de l'\u00d2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le D\u00f2ppo lav\u00f4ro (OND), ch'a gest\u00eeva t\u00f9tte e ativit\u00e6 de l'\u00e9poca, ma o p\u00eegia p\u00f6chi finan\u00e7iam\u00e9nti tr\u00eauv\u00e0ndose inte 'n per\u00eeodo de f\u00f3rte cr\u00eexi e vegn\u00ecndo emargin\u00f2u da-o r\u00e8sto do panor\u00e0mma sport\u00eevo na\u00e7ion\u00e2le. O canpion\u00f2u de l'\u00e9poca o l'\u00e0iva poch\u00ecscima inport\u00e0nsa, con 'n n\u00f9mero as\u00e6 contegn\u00fbo de squ\u00e0ddre; adreit\u00fba, into 1937, a-o canpi\u00f3n Paolo Rossi o no l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to posc\u00ecbile dif\u00e9nde o s\u00f2 t\u00ectolo apr\u00eauvo a-o f\u00e6to che i \u00f2rganizato\u00ee no l'\u00e0ivan avis\u00f2u in t\u00e9npo de l'in\u00ec\u00e7io da conpeti\u00e7i\u00f3n. Into m\u00e0zzo do 1946 gh'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta 'na riuni\u00f3n de v\u00e0rri tif\u00f4xi e ecs dirig\u00e9nti a Tor\u00ecn con l'\u00f2biet\u00eevo de \u00f2rganiz\u00e2se inte 'na federa\u00e7i\u00f3n ma i trav\u00e0ggi s\u00f3n st\u00e6ti as\u00e6 l\u00f3nghi e, into m\u00e9ize de dex\u00e9nbre de qu\u00e9llo \u00e0nno, o bal\u00f3n o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to inglob\u00f2u inta federa\u00e7i\u00f3n de tanbo\u00eato.\nInti m\u00e6ximi \u00e0nni, s\u00f9bito d\u00f2ppo a f\u00ecn da go\u00e6ra, o l'\u00eaa arest\u00f2u s\u00f4lo qu\u00e0rche sferist\u00eaio anc\u00f3n in fon\u00e7i\u00f3n, con l'intr\u00eaga discipl\u00ecnn-a ch'a vegn\u00eeva in pr\u00e0tica gest\u00eea da-i tr\u00e9i inpi\u00e0nti de Tor\u00ecn, \u00c0rba e \u00c0cqui inte 'na man\u00eaa fortem\u00e9nte specolat\u00eeva. Pe de ci\u00f9, o canpion\u00f2u o l'\u00eaa zug\u00f2u a set\u00e9nbre, a-a f\u00ecn da stagi\u00f3n sport\u00eeva dedic\u00e2 sorviat\u00f9tto a-i torn\u00eai, f\u00e6to ch'o port\u00e2va i zugo\u00e9i a no trov\u00e2se inte m\u00eagio condi\u00e7io\u00ecn p\u00f2-u scud\u00e9tto. O canpion\u00f2u da m\u00e0scima s\u00e9rie o v\u00eagne t\u00f3rna inandi\u00f2u a part\u00ee da-o 1947 (s\u00e9nsa \u00e2tre interu\u00e7io\u00ecn sc\u00ecnn-a qu\u00e9lla do 2020, caxon\u00e2 da-a pandem\u00eea COVID-19), co-e p\u00f6che squ\u00e0ddre de l'\u00e9poca e co-a sf\u00ecdda ritrov\u00e2 tra l'Augusto Manzo, conscider\u00f2u un di ci\u00f9 f\u00f3rti zugo\u00e9i da st\u00f6ia do bal\u00f3n, e o s\u00f2 gr\u00e0nde riv\u00e2le Francesco Gioetti. Def\u00e6ti, tra o 1947 e o 1951, o canpion\u00f2u o v\u00eagne go\u00e2gn\u00f2u pe \u00e7\u00ecnque v\u00f2tte de f\u00eea da-o Manzo, co-\u00een'inpr\u00e9iza ch'a no l'\u00e9 ci\u00f9 st\u00e6ta ripet\u00fba. Pe de ci\u00f9, into 1942, o Manzo o l'\u00e0iva parte\u00e7ip\u00f2u asc\u00ec a-o canpion\u00f2u de bal\u00f3n co-o bras\u00e0llo, vin\u00e7\u00e9ndo c\u00f3ntra i ci\u00f9 avox\u00e6 special\u00ecsti de qu\u00e9lla discipl\u00ecnn-a.\nCo-o prin\u00e7\u00ecpio di \u00e0nni '50 o bal\u00f3n o l'incom\u00e9nsa t\u00f3rna a svilup\u00e2se apr\u00eauvo a-i sf\u00f2rsci de \u00e7\u00e8rti direto\u00ee, c\u00f3mme qu\u00e9llo do sferist\u00eaio de \u00c0rba, o Romualdo Isnardi, e do giornal\u00ecsta da \"Gazzetta d'Alba\" Remo Gianuzzi, con l'\u00f2biet\u00eevo de liber\u00e2 o bal\u00f3n da-e scom\u00ecsse, avr\u00ecndolo a-i zo\u00eani e fax\u00e9ndolo con\u00f3sce in sc\u00ee giorn\u00e2li. Into 1951, a Tor\u00ecn, a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta d\u00f3nca cre\u00e2 l'Uni\u00f3n Itali\u00e0nn-a Bal\u00f3n El\u00e0stico (UIPE, \"Unione Italiana Pallone Elastico\"), co-a prez\u00e9nsa, tra i \u00e2tri, de l'Isnardi, de Gianuzzi e de Manzo.\nSta discipl\u00ecnn-a chi a l'incom\u00e9nsa cosc\u00ec a atir\u00e2 l'inter\u00e9sse di giorn\u00e2li: inte qu\u00e9sto per\u00eeodo publica\u00e7io\u00ecn c\u00f3mme \"La Stampa\", \"Il Popolo Nuovo\", \"Tuttosport\", a \"Gazzetta del Popolo\", \"Il Secolo XIX\" e il \"Corriere del Popolo\" com\u00e9nsan a riport\u00e2 inte 'n m\u00f2ddo regol\u00e2re a cr\u00f2naca di f\u00e6ti da-o m\u00f3ndo do bal\u00f3n. S\u00f3n inougur\u00e6 i n\u00eauvi sferist\u00eai de C\u00f2rcre, S\u00e0n St\u00eava B\u00e9lbo, Inp\u00eaia, C\u00eava, C\u00f9nio e Bra, m\u00e9ntre t\u00f3rnan in ativit\u00e6 qu\u00e9lli de \u00c0sti, B\u00eane Viag\u00e9nn-a e L\u00eaua. Into 1951 a fin\u00e2le do torn\u00eao de Tor\u00ecn tra l'Augusto Manzo e o Franco Balestra, in contenpor\u00e0nia a-o derby da \u00e7it\u00e6 de z\u00eaugo do bal\u00f3n, a l'\u00e0 ci\u00f9 de 5.000 spetato\u00ee. Into m\u00e6ximo per\u00eeodo o sp\u00f2rt o se svil\u00f9ppa inte 'n m\u00f2ddo ci\u00f9 profescion\u00ecstico: into 1953 o canpi\u00f2n de Prel\u00e0 Franco Balestra o p\u00e0ssa a-a \"Sapet Torino\" co-in contr\u00e0tto de 500.000 fr\u00e0nchi a l'\u00e0nno, 'n p\u00f6 m\u00eano de qu\u00e0nte o vegn\u00eeva pag\u00f2u a-i zugo\u00e9i da bal\u00f3n ma a \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo as\u00e6 conscider\u00e9vole. Apr\u00eauvo a-o f\u00e6to che i torn\u00eai garant\u00eevan di gr\u00f2sci go\u00e2gni a-i s\u00f2 \u00f2rganizato\u00ee, lev\u00e0ndo de inter\u00e9sse a-o canpion\u00f2u, into 1959 a federa\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e0 stabil\u00eeo che t\u00f9tte e squ\u00e0ddre de pr\u00ecmma e seg\u00f3nda categor\u00eea dov\u00e9ssan ripoz\u00e2 pe f\u00f2rsa a-o m\u00eano o gi\u00f3rno pr\u00ecmma de part\u00eee de canpion\u00f2u.\nIn sci\u00e2 f\u00ecn, co-i \u00e0nni '60, o canpion\u00f2u o l'\u00e9 t\u00f3rna divent\u00f2u l'ev\u00e9nto sport\u00eevo ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte da stagi\u00f3n, co-i torn\u00eai che s\u00f3n amerm\u00e6 de n\u00f9mero e frequ\u00e9nsa. Sto chi o l'\u00e9 'n per\u00eeodo de gr\u00e0n popolarit\u00e6 pe-o bal\u00f3n, con migi\u00e6a de tif\u00f4xi a asc\u00ecste a-e part\u00eee de gr\u00e9ndi canpio\u00ecn c\u00f3mme Piero Alemanni, Aurelio Defilippi, Donato Feliciano, Beppe Corino e Guido Galliano. A f\u00ecn de st'\u00e9poca chi a l'\u00e9 segn\u00e2, into 1964, da-o ret\u00eeo de l'Augusto Manzo e, into 1967, da-a demoli\u00e7i\u00f3n do gr\u00e0nde sferist\u00eaio de Tor\u00ecn, l\"'Edmondo De Amicis\". A l'\u00e9 p\u00f6i incomens\u00e2 a rivalit\u00e6 tra o Felice Bertola e o Massimo Berruti, che se contendi\u00e0n o t\u00ectolo pe squ\u00e6xi v\u00ecnt'\u00e0nni.\nInto 1983 o v\u00eagne zug\u00f2u pi-\u00e2 pr\u00ecmma v\u00f2tta o torn\u00eao da C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia e, a part\u00ee da-o 1992, s\u00f3n \u00f2rganiz\u00e6 e pr\u00ecmme conpeti\u00e7io\u00ecn interna\u00e7ion\u00e2li. Da qu\u00e9ste o s'\u00e9 p\u00f6i svilup\u00f2u o canpion\u00f2u mondi\u00e2le di sp\u00f2rt sfer\u00ecstichi, zug\u00f2u in It\u00e0lia asc\u00ec inte l'\u00e0nno 2004.\n\u00c0lbo d'\u00f6o.\nChi de s\u00f3tta gh'\u00e9 'n estr\u00e6to de l'\u00e0lbo d'\u00f6o do canpion\u00f2u itali\u00e0n de bal\u00f3n. A part\u00ee da-a s\u00f2 pr\u00ecmma edi\u00e7i\u00f3n, zug\u00e2 inte l'\u00e0nno 1912, o t\u00ectolo o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to go\u00e2gn\u00f2u da squ\u00e0ddre de vint\u00e9utto \u00e7it\u00e6 difer\u00e9nti."}
{"id": "30001", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30001", "title": "S\u00e9rie B (bal\u00f3n)", "text": "A S\u00e9rie B a l'\u00e9 a seg\u00f3nda ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte conpeti\u00e7i\u00f3n itali\u00e0nn-a de bal\u00f3n, \u00f2rganiz\u00e2 a part\u00ee da-o 1949 e d'ancheu ariv\u00e2 a-a s\u00f2 setantun\u00eaxima edi\u00e7i\u00f3n. Inandi\u00e2 e dir\u00e9tta da-a Federa\u00e7i\u00f3n Itali\u00e0nn-a Bal\u00f3n (F.I.P.A.P., \"Federazione Italiana Pallapugno\"), \u00f3ltre che a-o s\u00f2 scud\u00e9tto a fa goagn\u00e2 a promo\u00e7i\u00f3n a-a categor\u00eea superi\u00f4re, a S\u00e9rie A. \n\u00d3ltre a-a promo\u00e7i\u00f3n pi-\u00e2 pr\u00ecmma clasific\u00e2 gh'\u00e9 asc\u00ec a retrocesci\u00f3n, prev\u00ecsta pe-e \u00f9rtime d\u00f4e squ\u00e0ddre. Pe de ci\u00f9, a part\u00ee da-o 2012, e m\u00eagio squ\u00e0ddre do canpion\u00f2u p\u00eauan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 a-o torn\u00eao pe l'asegna\u00e7i\u00f3n de 'na C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia a l\u00f4 dedic\u00e2, m\u00e9ntre into pas\u00f2u dov\u00e9ivan zug\u00e2 inte qu\u00e9lla da m\u00e0scima s\u00e9rie. \nFon\u00e7ionam\u00e9nto.\nA S\u00e9rie B a l'\u00e9 o seg\u00f3ndo liv\u00e9llo do canpion\u00f2u na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de bal\u00f3n e, d'ancheu, ghe ne fan p\u00e0rte d\u00f3zze squ\u00e0ddre che v\u00eagnan s\u00e9gge da-o Piem\u00f3nte che da-a Lig\u00f9ria.\nA S\u00e9rie B, scimilm\u00e9nte a-a categor\u00eea superi\u00f4re, a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta \u00f2rganiz\u00e2 in sce tr\u00e6 f\u00e2ze difer\u00e9nti comens\u00e0ndo da-a cosc\u00ec d\u00eeta \"regular season\". Sta chi a consc\u00ecste inte 'n g\u00ee\u00f3n a l'itali\u00e0nn-a de 22 giorn\u00e6, cont\u00e0ndo s\u00e9gge e part\u00eee de and\u00e2ta che qu\u00e9lle de rit\u00f3rno. In sci\u00e2 b\u00e2ze di rizult\u00e2ti do g\u00ee\u00f3n, se avi\u00e0n e pr\u00ecmme s\u00eai squ\u00e0ddre, qualifich\u00e6 a-i \"play-off\", e-e s\u00eai che pe c\u00f3ntra duvi\u00e0n zug\u00e2 i \"play-out\".\nInta seg\u00f3nda f\u00e2ze v\u00e0n diretam\u00e9nte a-e semifin\u00e2le di \"play-off\" e pr\u00ecmme tr\u00e6 qualifich\u00e6 do g\u00ee\u00f3n, a-e qu\u00e6 a l'\u00e9 da az\u00f3nze a vincitr\u00eexe di spar\u00e9ggi zugh\u00e6 tra e \u00e2tre tr\u00e6 squ\u00e0ddre di \"play-off\" (d\u00f3nca inte poxi\u00e7io\u00ecn 4\u00b0 - 5\u00b0 - 6\u00b0 da clas\u00ecfica) e a pr\u00ecmma di \"play-out\", \u00f6 s\u00e6 a s\u00e8tima. Pe c\u00f3ntra, tra e squ\u00e0ddre a-i \"play-out\", e \u00f9rtime d\u00f4e d\u00f2ppo i spar\u00e9ggi sai\u00e0n retroc\u00e8sse inta S\u00e9rie C1.\nL'\u00f9rtima f\u00e2ze, p\u00e6gia a-a s\u00e9rie A, a consc\u00ecste inte 'na semifin\u00e2le e inta fin\u00e2le do scud\u00e9tto, co-e qu\u00e0ttro squ\u00e0ddre qualifich\u00e6 che se sc\u00f3ntran inte de part\u00eee de and\u00e2ta e de rit\u00f3rno, ci\u00f9 'n'evento\u00e2le part\u00eea de spar\u00e9ggio into c\u00e2xo a fo\u00eese neces\u00e2ia.\nPe qu\u00e0nte o rigo\u00e0rda i p\u00f3nti, inta pr\u00ecmma f\u00e2ze \u00f2gni vit\u00f6ia a l'\u00e0 'n val\u00f4 de 'n p\u00f3nto in clas\u00ecfica m\u00e9ntre, inta seg\u00f3nda f\u00e2ze, o val\u00f4 de 'na vit\u00f6ia o l'\u00e9 aoment\u00f2u a do\u00ee p\u00f3nti.\nE squ\u00e0ddre inte pr\u00ecmme \u00e9utto poxi\u00e7io\u00ecn da \"regular season\" go\u00e2gnan l'intr\u00e2 a-o torn\u00eao pi-\u00e2 C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de S\u00e9rie B asc\u00ec."}
{"id": "30003", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30003", "title": "\u00c0lbo d'\u00f6o do canpion\u00f2u itali\u00e0n de bal\u00f3n", "text": "L'\u00e0lbo d'\u00f6o do canpion\u00f2u itali\u00e0n de bal\u00f3n o l'incl\u00f9dde i 99 canpion\u00e6 da m\u00e0scima s\u00e9rie itali\u00e0nn-a disput\u00e6 sc\u00ecnn-a-a giorn\u00e2 d'ancheu."}
{"id": "30004", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30004", "title": "C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de bal\u00f3n", "text": "A C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de bal\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 'na conpeti\u00e7i\u00f3n itali\u00e0nn-a de bal\u00f3n, \u00f2rganiz\u00e2 da-a Federa\u00e7i\u00f3n Itali\u00e0nn-a Bal\u00f3n (F.I.P.A.P, \"Federazione Italiana Pallapugno\") a part\u00ee da-o 1983 e ch'a se z\u00eauga co-ina cad\u00e9nsa ano\u00e2le. A squ\u00e0ddra ch'a go\u00e2gna sto torn\u00eao chi a l'\u00f2t\u00eagne asc\u00ec l'\u00f2cax\u00f3n de parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 a-a Superc\u00f3ppa itali\u00e0nn-a de bal\u00f3n.\nSt\u00f6ia.\nO torn\u00eao da C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to inandi\u00f2u pi-\u00e2 pr\u00ecmma v\u00f2tta into c\u00f3rso da stagi\u00f3n do 1983. In prin\u00e7\u00ecpio o coinvolg\u00e9iva s\u00e9gge de squ\u00e0ddre da-a S\u00e9rie A che da-a S\u00e9rie B ma, co-a crea\u00e7I\u00f3n do torn\u00eao de C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de S\u00e9rie B, \u00f2ua \u00f2gni categor\u00eea a l'\u00e0 'n pr\u00f2pio torn\u00eao pi-\u00e2 c\u00f3ppa.\nD\u00f2ppo o 1983, a C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia a no l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta asegn\u00e2 inte stagio\u00ecn 1996, 1997 e 2004, \u00f3ltre che inte qu\u00e9lla do 2020, co-o canpion\u00f2u ch'o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to scancel\u00f2u apr\u00eauvo a-o scc\u00e9uppo da pandem\u00eea de COVID-19. In particol\u00e2, inte l'edi\u00e7i\u00f2n do 1996, l'\u00eaa acapit\u00f2u ch'a fo\u00eese zug\u00e2 s\u00f4lo a pr\u00ecmma de d\u00f4e semifin\u00e2le, co-e seg\u00f3nda ch'a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta rimand\u00e2 a l'\u00e0nno a vegn\u00ee. A \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo, apr\u00eauvo a di c\u00e0ngi de squ\u00e0ddra di zugo\u00e9i, a v\u00e0rri infortun\u00e6 e pe 'n ric\u00f3rso da Subalcuneo c\u00f3ntra a man\u00eaa no go\u00e6i regol\u00e2re de ricuper\u00e2 a part\u00eea, a C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia 1996 a l'\u00e9 rest\u00e2 s\u00e9nsa 'n vincit\u00f4.\nPe c\u00f2ntra, inte l'\u00e0nno d\u00f2ppo, a C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia a no l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta asegn\u00e2 d\u00e6to apr\u00eauvo a-a decix\u00f3n de tent\u00e2 'n n\u00eauvo scist\u00eama pe l'asegna\u00e7i\u00f3n da c\u00f3ppa, inandi\u00e2 c\u00f3mme 'n torn\u00eao a-o cord\u00ecn con zugo\u00e9i da t\u00f9tte d\u00f4e e s\u00e9rie magio\u00ee e con part\u00eee a-i 15 z\u00eaughi. A \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo sta f\u00f3rmola chi a l'\u00e0 av\u00fbo cosc\u00ec p\u00f6co suc\u00e8sso da \u00ease f\u00eeto abandon\u00e2, s\u00e9nsa asegn\u00e2 d\u00f3nca o trof\u00eao de qu\u00e9llo \u00e0nno. In sci\u00e2 f\u00ecn, l'edi\u00e7i\u00f3n do 2004 a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta anul\u00e2 apr\u00eauvo a-a prez\u00e9nsa do canpion\u00f2u mondi\u00e2le di sp\u00f2rt sfer\u00ecstichi in It\u00e0lia, d\u00f3nde gh'\u00eaa v\u00e0rie part\u00eee de bal\u00f3n asc\u00ec.\nFon\u00e7ionam\u00e9nto.\nO regolam\u00e9nto da C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia o l'\u00e9 b\u00e9n b\u00e9n cangi\u00f2u co-o pas\u00e2 di \u00e0nni; seg\u00f3ndo a s\u00f2 f\u00f3rmola d'ancheu, pe qualific\u00e2se a-o torn\u00eao da C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia, 'na squ\u00e0ddra da m\u00e0scima s\u00e9rie a se d\u00eave trov\u00e2 inte unn-a de pr\u00ecmme \u00e9utto poxi\u00e7io\u00ecn da clasc\u00ecfica a-a f\u00ecn do g\u00ee\u00f3n d'and\u00e2ta da \"regular season\".\nE squ\u00e0ddre cosc\u00ec sele\u00e7ion\u00e6 v\u00eagnan d\u00f3nca inser\u00eee inte 'n tabel\u00f3n con part\u00eee a elimina\u00e7i\u00f3n dir\u00e9tta. I qu\u00e0rti de fin\u00e2le e-e d\u00f4e semifin\u00e2le s\u00f3n da zug\u00e2 into c\u00e0npo da squ\u00e0ddra m\u00eagio clasific\u00e2, pe c\u00f3ntra a fin\u00e2le a se d\u00eave tegn\u00ee inte 'n c\u00e0npo ne\u00f3tro."}
{"id": "30005", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30005", "title": "C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de S\u00e9rie B de bal\u00f3n", "text": "A C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de S\u00e9rie B de bal\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 'na conpeti\u00e7i\u00f3n itali\u00e0nn-a de bal\u00f3n, \u00f2rganiz\u00e2 da-a Federa\u00e7i\u00f3n Itali\u00e0nn-a Bal\u00f3n (F.I.P.A.P, \"Federazione Italiana Pallapugno\") a part\u00ee da-o 2012 e ch'a se z\u00eauga co-ina cad\u00e9nsa ano\u00e2le.\nSt\u00f6ia.\nO torn\u00eao da C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de bal\u00f3n, introd\u00fbto pi-\u00e2 pr\u00ecmma v\u00f2tta inte l'\u00e0nno 1983, o l'\u00eaa in prin\u00e7\u00ecpio \u00f9nico tra i canpion\u00e6 de d\u00f4e s\u00e9rie magio\u00ee, pigi\u00e0ndo de squ\u00e0ddre s\u00e9gge da-a s\u00e9rie A che da-a S\u00e9rie B. A \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo, da-o 2012, s'\u00e9 dec\u00eezo d'inandi\u00e2 'n torn\u00eao spec\u00ecfico pe \u00f2gni categor\u00eea, separ\u00e0ndo i trof\u00eai, \u00e0nche se za inte l'\u00e0nno 2006 o l'\u00eaa st\u00e6to \u00f2rganiz\u00f2u 'n torn\u00eao de c\u00f3ppa dedic\u00f2u a-a S\u00e9rie B.\nInti \u00e0nni de as\u00e9nsa do torn\u00eao spec\u00ecfico pi-\u00e2 seg\u00f3nda s\u00e9rie e s\u00f2 squ\u00e0ddre po\u00e9ivan parte\u00e7ip\u00e2 a qu\u00e9llo de l'\u00f9nica C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia e, a desp\u00e6to da prez\u00e9nsa de forma\u00e7io\u00ecn da S\u00e9rie magi\u00f4, s\u00f3n ariv\u00e6 a-e fin\u00e2le pe b\u00e9n \u00e7\u00ecnque v\u00f2tte: \u00f6 s\u00e6 inti \u00e0nni 1990, 1994, 1998, 2005 e 2009.\nFon\u00e7ionam\u00e9nto.\nA C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia de S\u00e9rie B a l'\u00e9 'n torn\u00eao a elimina\u00e7i\u00f3n dir\u00e9tta zug\u00f2u da qu\u00e0ttro squ\u00e0ddre. E pr\u00ecmme d\u00f4e v\u00eagnan sele\u00e7ion\u00e6 a-a f\u00ecn do g\u00ee\u00f3n d'and\u00e2ta da \"regolar season\" da S\u00e9rie B, pigi\u00e0ndo qu\u00e9lle inta m\u00eagio poxi\u00e7i\u00f3n. Ci\u00f9 t\u00e0rdi, a-a f\u00ecn do g\u00ee\u00f3n de rit\u00f3rno, se p\u00ecggian e \u00e2tre d\u00f4e m\u00eagio squ\u00e0ddre che parte\u00e7ipi\u00e0n a-e semifin\u00e2le.\nT\u00f9tte e part\u00eee do torn\u00eao, d\u00f3nca s\u00e9gge e semifin\u00e2le che a fin\u00e2le, se d\u00eavan zug\u00e2 inte 'n c\u00e0npo ne\u00f3tro."}
{"id": "30006", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30006", "title": "Superc\u00f3ppa itali\u00e0nn-a de bal\u00f3n", "text": "A Superc\u00f3ppa itali\u00e0nn-a a l'\u00e9 'na conpeti\u00e7i\u00f3n itali\u00e0nn-a de bal\u00f3n, \u00f2rganiz\u00e2 da-a Federa\u00e7i\u00f3n Itali\u00e0nn-a Bal\u00f3n (F.I.P.A.P, \"Federazione Italiana Pallapugno\") a part\u00ee da-o 1994 e ch'a se z\u00eauga co-ina cad\u00e9nsa ano\u00e2le.\nSt\u00f6ia.\nO trof\u00eao da Superc\u00f3ppa o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to zug\u00f2u pi-\u00e2 pr\u00ecmma v\u00f2tta into 1994 ma o l'\u00e0 av\u00fbo cosc\u00ec p\u00f6co suc\u00e8sso da \u00ease inandi\u00f2u t\u00f3rna s\u00f4lo v\u00e0rri \u00e0nni d\u00f2ppo. Def\u00e6ti, a part\u00eea tra a vincitr\u00eexe da m\u00e0scima s\u00e9rie e qu\u00e9lla da C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta zug\u00e2 a-i 8 d'arv\u00ee a R\u00f3mma, inte 'n c\u00e0npo da z\u00eaugo do bal\u00f3n e l\u00f3nxi da-o p\u00f9blico apascion\u00f2u de sta discipl\u00ecnn-a chi.\nPe de ci\u00f9, a Superc\u00f3ppa a no l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta zug\u00e2 inte l'\u00e0nno 2020 apr\u00eauvo a-o scc\u00e9uppo da pandem\u00eea de COVID-19 e, p\u00ee-a m\u00e6xima rax\u00f3n, a no l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta inandi\u00e2 m\u00e0nco inte l'\u00e0nno a vegn\u00ee, d\u00e6to ch\u00f2-u canpion\u00f2u e a C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia \u00eaan st\u00e6ti scancel\u00e6 asc\u00ec.\nFon\u00e7ionam\u00e9nto.\nO trof\u00eao o v\u00eagne de s\u00f2lito asegn\u00f2u a-o prin\u00e7\u00ecpio da stagi\u00f3n, qu\u00e0rche gi\u00f3rno pr\u00ecmma ch'a com\u00e9nse a \"regular season\", co-ina g\u00e2ra \u00f9nica tra e squ\u00e0ddre ch'\u00e0n go\u00e2gn\u00f2u o canpion\u00f2u de S\u00e9rie A e a C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia into c\u00f3rso da stagi\u00f3n pas\u00e2. O c\u00e0npo de z\u00eaugo pe sta part\u00eea chi o l'\u00e9 de s\u00f2lito qu\u00e9llo di canpio\u00ecn d'It\u00e0lia.\nInto c\u00e2xo a m\u00e6xima squ\u00e0ddra a l'\u00e0gge go\u00e2gn\u00f2u s\u00e9gge o t\u00ectolo chi-\u00e2 c\u00f3ppa, a s\u00f2 sfid\u00e0nte a sai\u00e2 l'\u00e2tra final\u00ecsta da C\u00f3ppa It\u00e0lia. A Superc\u00f3ppa a l'\u00ecntra do t\u00f9tto in pos\u00e9sso de 'na socj\u00eat\u00e6 s\u00f4lo d\u00f2ppo av\u00e9il\u00e0 go\u00e2gn\u00e2 pe tr\u00e9i v\u00f2tte, inpr\u00e9iza che pe \u00f2ua a l'\u00e9 ariesc\u00eea s\u00f4lo a-a Subalcuneo, a-a Canalese e a l'Albese."}
{"id": "30010", "revid": "10132", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30010", "title": "Izoa Genovesa", "text": "L\u2019\u00cezoa Genovesa (in spagn\u00f2llo \"Isla Genovesa\", in ingl\u00e9ize \"Tower Island\") a l\u2019\u00e9 \u2019n vulc\u00e0n a sc\u00f9ddo inte \u00cezoe Gal\u00e0pagos (Ecuad\u00f2r), inte l\u2019\u00d2c\u00e8ano Pac\u00ecfico de lev\u00e0nte. L\u2019\u00eezoa a l\u2019\u00e9 grande qu\u00e6xi 14 chil\u00f2metri quadr\u00e2ti e a s\u00f2 alt\u00e9ssa m\u00e0scima a l\u2019\u00e9 de 64 m\u00eatri. L\u2019\u00eezoa, a f\u00f3rma de f\u00e6ro de cav\u00e0llo, a gh\u2019\u00e0 \u2019na caldera vulc\u00e0nica (\u2019na c\u00f3nca \u00f2cup\u00e2 da \u2019n l\u00e2go) \u2019na mi\u00e2gia da qu\u00e6 a l\u2019\u00e9 deru\u00e2 e a l\u2019\u00e0 form\u00f2u a Grande B\u00e2ia de Darwin, con de scug\u00eae t\u00f9tto in g\u00eeo. Into c\u00e9ntro gh\u2019\u00e9 o l\u00e2go d\u2019\u00e6goa s\u00e2 Arcturus, a qu\u00e6 z\u00f3tta a gh\u2019\u00e0 \u2019n pit\u00ecn m\u00eano de 6.000 \u00e0nni. Scib\u00e9n che no s\u2019areg\u00f2rdan eru\u00e7io\u00ecn st\u00f2riche in sce l\u2019\u00eezoa Genovesa, in sc\u00ee fi\u00e0nchi do vulc\u00e0n gh\u2019\u00e9 de co\u00ea de l\u00e2va as\u00e6 rec\u00e9nti.\nO n\u00f3mme spagn\u00f2llo ofi\u00e7i\u00e2 de Genovesa o ne v\u00e9n da-a \u00e7it\u00e6 de Z\u00eana, in \u00f6n\u00f4 do Crist\u00f2ffa Col\u00f3nbo. O n\u00f3mme ingl\u00e9ize \u201cTower\u201d o l\u2019\u00e9 qu\u00e6xi de seg\u00fbo l\u2019altera\u00e7i\u00f3n de \u201cDownes\u201d. A poxi\u00e7i\u00f3n de l\u2019\u00eezoa a l\u2019\u00e9 st\u00e6ta segnal\u00e2 da-o John Downes capit\u00e0nio do b\u00e0rco USS Essex inte l\u2019\u00e0nno 1813, inta go\u00e6ra do 1812. e o n\u00f3mme \u201cDowers\u2019s\u201d o l\u2019\u00e9 conp\u00e0rso into 1815, de seg\u00fbo scriv\u00e9ndo m\u00e2 o n\u00f3mme Downes. Pas\u00e0ndo da \u201cDowers\u2019s\u201d, \u201cDowers\u201d, e \u201cTower\u2019s\u201d, in sci\u00e2 f\u00ecn da-o 1841 l\u2019\u00e9 st\u00e6to scr\u00eeto \u201cTower\u201d in sc\u00ea c\u00e0rte gi\u00f6gr\u00e0fiche de l\u2019Amirali\u00e2to Brit\u00e0nico.\nF\u00e0ona\nSt\u2019\u00eezoa chi a l\u2019\u00e9 conosci\u00fba c\u00f3mme L\u2019\u00cezoa di \u00d6x\u00e9lli, perch\u00e9 a l\u2019\u00e9 p\u00ecnn-a de \u2019na gr\u00e0n quantit\u00e6 d\u2019\u00f6x\u00e9lli de t\u00f9tte e r\u00e0zze. Gh\u2019\u00e9 \u2019n m\u00f9ggio de freg\u00e0dde e o l\u2019\u00e9 o m\u00eagio p\u00f2sto de l\u2019arcip\u00e9lago pe v\u00e9dde a S\u00f4la da-i p\u00ea r\u00f3sci (Sula Sula), a S\u00f4la de Nazca (Sula granti), l\u2019\u00d6chin c\u00f4a de rondan\u00ecnn-a (Creagrus furcatus), l\u2019\u00d6x\u00e9llo de tenp\u00e8ste (Hydro bates pelagicus), o Frengu\u00e9llo de Darwin (Fring\u00eclla Darwin) e o T\u00f3rdo pic\u00ecn (Mimus parvulus).\nO P\u00e0sso Prince Philip o l\u2019\u00e9 \u2019n sent\u00ea straorden\u00e2io into m\u00eazo da col\u00f2nia di \u00f6x\u00e9lli de m\u00e2 p\u00ecn de v\u00ectta, s\u00f3rvia \u2019na scug\u00eaa \u00e8rta 25 m\u00eatri. In \u00e7\u00ecmma a p\u00ecsta a cont\u00ecnoa inte l\u2019entrot\u00e6ra in m\u00eazo a \u00e2tre col\u00f2nie d\u2019\u00f6x\u00e9lli inte \u2019n b\u00f2sco pic\u00ecn d\u2019\u00e8rboi de l\u00e9gno s\u00e0nto. A p\u00ecsta a proc\u00fba asc\u00ec \u2019na v\u00ecsta da cian\u00fba p\u00ecnn-a de r\u00f2cce. I \u00d6x\u00e9lli de tenp\u00e8ste chi s\u00f3n \u2019na r\u00e0zza do t\u00f9tto desp\u00e6gia da \u00f2gni \u00e2tra into m\u00f3ndo perch\u00e9 s\u00f3n b\u00e9n b\u00e9n at\u00eeve into gi\u00f3rno. Pe sghind\u00e2 i predato\u00ee, l\u00f4 t\u00f3rnan inti s\u00f2 n\u00eei s\u00f4lo de n\u00e9utte.\nAnche e iguane de m\u00e2 ci\u00f9 pic\u00ecnn-e v\u00eevan chi.\nDem\u00f4e\nInta B\u00e2ia de Darwin l\u2019\u00e9 posc\u00ecbile inm\u00e8rzise l\u00f3ngo a mi\u00e2gia int\u00e8rna \u00f2 l\u00f3ngo qu\u00e9lla est\u00e8rna meno prot\u00e8tta. \u2019N\u2019\u00e2tra poscibilit\u00e6 a l\u2019\u00e9 qu\u00e9lla de inm\u00e8rzise a-o de f\u00eaua do vulc\u00e2n atrav\u00e8rso e can\u00e6 da Caldera."}
{"id": "30011", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30011", "title": "Par\u00f2cchie da diocexi de Arbenga e Impeia", "text": "E parocchie da Diocexi d'Arbenga-Impeia sun 163 distribu\u00ece int'ina z\u00f2na ch'a cumprende i cum\u00fci da parte ci\u00fc a punente da pruvinsa de Savuna e da parte ci\u00fc a levante de quella de Impeia in sce 'na superficcie de 979 km qu\u00e0ddri, cun 173.000 abitanti. A magiur\u00e0nsa de queste (86), se tr\u00f6va inta parte imperi\u00e9se, m\u00e8ntre e restanti 77 inte quella savunese."}
