{"id": "30019", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30019", "title": "SpongeBob SquarePants", "text": "SpongeBob SquarePants (\u00f6 s\u00e6 SpongeBob Br\u00e2ghe Quadr\u00e2te, ciam\u00e2 s\u00f4lo SpongeBob asc\u00ec) a l'\u00e9 'na s\u00e9rie de carto\u00ecn anim\u00e6 americ\u00e0nn-a ch'a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta cre\u00e2 da l'animat\u00f4 e divulgat\u00f4 scent\u00ecfico Stephen Hillenburg pi-\u00e2 socj\u00eat\u00e6 Nickelodeon. A s\u00e9rie a c\u00f3nta e avent\u00fbe do protagon\u00ecsta, 'na sp\u00f3nzia, e di s\u00f2 am\u00eexi, abit\u00e0nti de 'na \u00e7it\u00e6 sotomar\u00ecnn-a de fantax\u00eea ciam\u00e2 Bikini Bottom.\nTra e s\u00e9rie anim\u00e6 americ\u00e0nn-e a l'\u00e9 a qu\u00ecnta ci\u00f9 v\u00eagia e, apr\u00eauvo a-o s\u00f2 gr\u00e0nde suc\u00e8sso, s'\u00e9 svilup\u00f2u 'n inport\u00e0nte \"franchise\" a l\u00ea lig\u00f2u. Tra i carto\u00ecn trasm\u00ecssi in sce Nickelodeon, a l'\u00e9 qu\u00e9lla co-o ci\u00f9 \u00e8rto \u00ecndice de asc\u00f3lto; pe de ci\u00f9, co-i 13 mili\u00e0rdi de d\u00f2lari de ric\u00e2vi ch'a l'\u00e0 gener\u00f2u inte l'\u00e0nno 2019, a l'\u00e9 in asol\u00fbto a propi\u00eat\u00e6 ci\u00f9 redit\u00ec\u00e7ia pi-\u00e2 Paramount Consumer Products."}
